name: Nike Air Max 90 'Black Gum'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 'Black Gum' is a timeless silhouette that seamlessly blends classic design and urban style. The sneaker's upper offers breathability and durability through high-quality materials. Its all-black construction allows the brown rubber outsole to stand out from the monochromatic vibe. Air Max cushioning ensures a responsive stride, while the universal colour combination makes these sneakers a versatile addition to any wardrobe.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8 'Cool Grey'
text_content: With its clean and neutral design, the 'Cool Grey' Air Force 1 '07 LV8 (DZ4514-002) offers exceptional versatility, easily complementing a wide range of outfits and occasions. The grey tones provide a modern and sleek aesthetic that's suitable for both casual wear and more dressed-up settings. Soft suede overlays pair with era-echoing '80s construction and reflective-design Swoosh logos to elevate the design while hidden full-length Air units add the legendary comfort the AF 1 model offers. Details such as the mini Swooshes in the main side Swoosh make the pair unique and add up to the authenticity of the design.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Medium Olive'
text_content: 2021 was the year of the Nike Dunk, which is still wildly popular and has been released in a lot of cool colorways, including the Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Medium Olive'. This sneaker features a two-tone colour palette, pairing a white leather base with olive green overlays. The outsole and laces can also be seen in Olive Green, completing the look of the subtle colorway.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Wild WMNS 'Black'
text_content: As a variation of the classic Air Force 1 silhouette, the Nike Air Force 1 Wild WMNS is designed especially for women, featuring a boot-like look for comfort during outdoor activities. With inspiration from the Air Force 1 Boot, this is a great alternative version of the iconic shoe.The AF1 Wild WMNS 'Black' features an outdoor-friendly sole unit. For comfort and durability, the upper combines nubuck and mesh materials, and an extra cushion is added to the heel. Additionally, the sneaker features a double lacing system and a double collar to ensure a secure fit.A unique twist on the classic Air Force 1 design, the Air Force 1 Wild WMNS is designed for style and versatility. With a 2023 launch, it will cater to the fashion-forward tastes of female sneaker enthusiasts.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Luxe 'Summit White'
text_content: The design of this sturdy Nike Air Force 1 Luxe 'Summit White' features a white leather upper with a soft mesh collar, wavy eyelets and a perforated toe box. Furthermore, references to the Light Bone are visible on the rubber outsole, heel tab and the Air logo on the midsole. The Nike Swoosh logo can be found on both sides of the trainers and on the heel. Furthermore, this Air Force 1 has a padded tongue, a round toe cap and sturdy soles. There are also full-length Air units. The finishing touch to the design are the jagged edges of the outsole that give the sneaker a mysterious look.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Wild WMNS 'Sail'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Wild WMNS 'Sail' sneaker cleverly blends fashion and utility to produce a diverse line of women's shoes.This shoe's upper has a simple and classic sail colorway, giving it a sophisticated and neutral appearance that goes well with many different outfits. The Nike Swoosh logo in cream sail hue blends into the upper, while premium leather overlays and perforations add texture and depth to the design.The Air Force 1 Wild WMNS 'Sail' was created with comfort in mind and has a cushioned midsole that offers excellent impact absorption and support. On various surfaces, the rubber outsole's solid traction ensures stability. The traditional Air Force 1 silhouette has a low-top profile that promotes easy movement and a contemporary look.The Nike Air Force 1 Wild WMNS 'Sail' is a go-to sneaker that combines classic style with unrivalled comfort, whether you're exploring the city streets or hanging out with friends. With this iconic silhouette that celebrates both fashion and function, up your footwear game.

name: Nike Air Max 90 PRM 'Flax'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 PRM 'Flax' has the appropriate colour combination for autumn. The Air Max 90 has an all-brown finish, with the upper being a combination of suede and nubuck. The branding elements are in the same shade of brown as the upper, as are the Swoosh and laces. In contrast, the shoe is rounded off with a sole in a custom brown shade, with the signature Air unit visible.

name: Nike Air Max 1 87 LX 'Light Smoke Grey'
text_content: Honouring the legacy of the Nike Air Max 1, a symbol of innovation and style since its debut in 1987, Nike is set to release the Nike Air Max 1 '87 LX 'Light Smoke Grey' exclusively for women during the 2023 holiday season. This premium version features a plush white corduroy base layer, creating a perfect canvas for the sophisticated grey tumbled leather and suede overlays. The design combines darker grey accents on the suede mudguard with lighter grey elements on the tumbled leather vamp, midfoot, and heel. The iconic white Swoosh seamlessly integrates into the overall aesthetic, drawing attention to the shoe's legendary silhouette. Notably, the tongue tag boasts a 3D black Swoosh, while the heel tab showcases a revamped Nike text design in a contrasting black hue, reminiscent of previous designs. To complete the look, the sneaker is equipped with a classic white foam midsole and a durable grey rubber outsole.

name: NOCTA x Nike Air Force 1 'Certified Lover Boy'
text_content: The Drake x Nike Air Force 1 'Certified Lover Boy' (CZ8065-100) is a collab between the Toronto rapper and Nike that has been a long time coming. After being teased with images several times, Nike revealed the official images of the sneaker in 2022. The simplistic design is all-white and features details on the midsole that hint at Drake. The shoe has been given the same name as the album Drake dropped in 2021. The sneaker is coloured all-white and has a leather upper. The midsole features 'Love You Forever' in cursive letters. The Swoosh appears on the middle panel and the Nike Air logo on the heel completes the look.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Shadow 'Atmosphere'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Shadow 'Atmosphere' CI0919-117 has a fresh look and combines different pastel colours. The silhouette takes its inspiration from the classic Air Force 1 model and adds different elements to the design. The upper has double overlays on the nose, heel and tongue. The sneaker has an off-white colouring. The overlays on the lace-up are light pink, as are the details on the Swoosh. The 'Atmosphere' has a double Swoosh and the 'Air' logo on the heel is also printed twice. The tongue turns light green, as does the heel tab.

name: Nike Air Max 1 'University Gold'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 'University Gold' is an iconic silhouette that takes a bold leap with a carefully chosen colour scheme.The sneaker's white mesh base is complemented by black and grey overlays. 'University Gold' colours the Swoosh, tongue tag and Air Bubble, offering harmonious detail to the tonal upper. The result is an eye-catching masterpiece. Embrace colour and design with the Nike Air Max 1 'University Gold', where every step becomes a statement of artistic expression and refined taste.

name: Nike Air Max 1 'Clear Jade'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 'Clear Jade' sneaker, is a vibrant and stylish iteration of the iconic Air Max 1 silhouette. The energizing 'Clear Jade' colorway features a combination of light green and white tones to produce an alluring and striking shoe. The visible Air Max unit in the heel offers superior cushioning and impact protection, while the premium suede and mesh upper offer comfort and breathability.The Nike Air Max 1 'Clear Jade' is a stylish and functional shoe that provides a smooth ride. It is appropriate for any activity because the rubber outsole provides dependable traction on a variety of surfaces. With this timeless silhouette, you can enter the world of boldness and elegance because it skillfully fuses classic style with vibrant colours.Take advantage of the vibrant colour scheme and unrivalled comfort of the Air Max cushioning to make each step a statement of self-assured style.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Panda'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Low is a popular trainer from the Nike brand. The colourway is inspired by the panda, an endangered species best known for its black and white fur. The trainer has a white base with black overlays. The inner lining is also black in colour. The Air Force 1 Low 'Panda' has a comfortable fit and is made of high-quality leather. This makes the trainer durable and suitable for daily use. The Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Panda' is a versatile trainer that goes well with different outfits, making it great for everyday use.

name: Nike Air Max 1 Crepe 'Soft Grey'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 Premium 'Soft Grey' features a crepe midsole like its popular predecessor Air Max 1 'Crepe Hemp'. The upper is constructed of a ‘Soft Grey’ mesh base with ‘Thunder Grey’ and ‘Neutral Grey’ suede overlays. The monochromatic aspect of the design is disrupted by the white leather Swoosh. The grey Air Unit and light brown rubber outsole complete the design.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'Light Iron Ore'
text_content: As the transition to Fall/Winter approaches, Nike embraces neutral tones for the Air Max 90, presenting a new ‘Light Iron Ore’ colorway. The quarter panel and several branded elements adopt this subtle hue, setting the tone for the design. Meanwhile, the upper predominantly features the understated ‘Photon Dust’ shade. However, the focal point emerges through rich dark brown leather enveloping both the lateral and medial sides, adding depth and character. Complementing the palette, accents in cream are strategically placed, including on the vamp and lining, providing a balanced and harmonious contrast.

name: Nike Air Force 1 'Anthracite'
text_content: In a subtle anticipation of the colder seasons, the Nike Air Force 1 Low adopts a muted grey and ‘Anthracite’ color palette, blending suede and leather across its upper. Overlays utilize suede while darker grey panels grace the toe, tongue, and heel, creating contrast against the lighter base and swooshes. The sole unit follows an all-dark arrangement, allowing the upper's grayscale tones to take the spotlight.The Air Force 1 Low combines style and functionality in advance of the coming months, providing a versatile option for those considering their winter wardrobes as summer approaches.

name: Nike Air Max 1 'Bronze'
text_content: Featuring an alluring colour scheme, the Nike Air Max 1 'Bronze' exudes class and sophistication. With its rich and opulent colour palette, this shoe commands attention and adds luxury to your shoe collection. The sneaker is constructed with a breathable white mesh base and 'Light Orewood Brown' suede overlays around the lacing system and medial and heel. The smooth beige hue is nicely complemented by the 'Magma Orange' mudguard constructed in tumbled leather. The eye-catching hue colours the Swoosh and branding elements. Black accents on the outsole add elegance to the overall design. With its patented Air Max cushioning, the shoe offers plush cushioning and responsive support, ensuring all-day comfort.A precisely made, meticulously detailed Nike Air Max 1, the 'Bronze' provides both fashion and comfort on a daily basis.

name: Nike Air Max 1 'Mica Green'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 'Mica Green' features the classic design of Air Max 1 in a mix of textures that made the design so successful. The silhouette is constructed with a white mesh base on the upper, 'Photon Dust' suede overlays and stylish 'Mica Green' leather mudguard and Swoosh. The branding elements on the heel and tongue tag come in a green hue, matching the eyestays on the front. The white midsole sits atop a rubber outsole which features a mix of green, grey and black tones.

name: Nike Air Max 1 'Deep Royal Blue'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 'Deep Royal Blue' is a stylish, contemporary shoe in a classic colour scheme that is sure to turn heads. Premium materials that provide breathability and durability, like leather and mesh, are combined to create the upper. On a white mesh base, 'Deep Royal Blue' is used in the construction of the mudguard. Black used in the depiction of the Swoosh together with accents throughout the sneaker adds to the contrast. Its colour scheme is ideal for those who want a daring appearance that can still be worn with a variety of outfits.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 'Reflective Swoosh' - Nike App Release
Nike Dunk Low 'Grey Fog'
text_content: The Nike Dunk is a unique model. In fact, the Dunk is a blend of the best of two iconic Nike basketball silhouettes: the Nike Terminator and the Air Jordan 1. This Nike Dunk Low 'Grey Fog' (DD1391-103) features a white base with 'Grey Fog' overlays and Swoosh. The sneaker is completed with a white midsole and a 'Grey Fog' outsole.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX WMNS 'Grain'
text_content: As a trend-setting and iconic sneaker, the Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX WMNS 'Grain' effortlessly blends style with comfort. The women's exclusive 'Grain' colorway gives a fresh and contemporary look to any outfit. A luxurious hairy suede upper in 'Grain' hue provides style through its texture. 'Deep Royal Blue' heel tab disrupts the sneaker's monochromatic look while adding to its stunning aesthetic. With its signature Nike Air cushioning and rubber outsole, this sneaker provides incredible support and comfort throughout the day. With the Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX WMNS 'Grain', you can elevate your sneaker game, whether you're hitting the streets or stepping out casually.

name: Nike Air Max 1 WMNS 'Tan Multi-Color'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 'Tan Multi-Color' sneaker is a captivating and vibrant shoe that combines classic design with a one-of-a-kind twist. This iconic shape has a versatile tan colour as the foundation, which is elevated by a fun and vibrant multi-colour palette, creating a vibrant and eye-catching appearance.The upper of the Nike Air Max 1 'Tan Multi-Color' features a tan leather base. The heel of the sneaker is accessorised with colourful accents against sophisticated and adaptable black Swoosh and branding elements. In addition to providing outstanding impact absorption and cushioning, the recognizable Air Max unit in the heel also gives the overall style a vintage feel.This sneaker offers a cosy and supportive ride and is designed for both style and performance. The rubber outsole provides reliable traction on a variety of surfaces, and the cushioned insole and padded collar provide plush comfort. The Nike Air Max 1 'Tan Multi-Color' is ideal for those who want to make a bold statement with their footwear thanks to its timeless design and vibrant colour scheme.

name: Nike WMNS Dunk Low Next Nature 'Pale Coral'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low is a popular silhouette that goes with many different outfits. Nike is working hard on their sustainability project and have released the Next Nature line. The kicks under this name are produced with recycled and sustainable materials. The upper of this Dunk Low is not made of leather, but it does have the same look and feel. The toebox, side panel and collar are in white on this pair, as is the tongue. On the overlays is a coral-like colour. This light colour can also be seen on the Swoosh, heeltab and laces. The midsole is also in white. In contrast to the other colours, the outsole is light grey.

name: Nike Wmns Dunk Low Next Nature 'Floral Tapestry'
Nike Air Force 1 Low PRM 'Ale Brown and Midnight Navy'
text_content: Nike has launched a new version of its legendary Air Force 1, inspired by the world of bespoke tailoring. Tweed, suede, corduroy, and houndstooth are interwoven intricately in this one-of-a-kind pattern to give the shoe a distinctive, hand-crafted appearance. The design of the shoe is aesthetically interesting since each panel is made of a different fabric. Notably, chestnut-treated corduroy adds an autumnal touch to the vamp and profile swooshes, while tweed graces the mudguards, and houndstooth patterns adorn the quarter panels. Dark navy hues are prominent, especially on the eye stay, collar, ribbed tongue construction, and inner lining, providing a suede-like appearance. Complementing this intricate design, the shoe features 'Sail' accents on the laces, stitched tongue tabs, and the sole unit underfoot.

name: Nike Air Max 95 'Reverse Neon'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 95 'Reverse Neon' consists of leather combined with a mesh upper. The tipped overlays create the Air Max 95's signature wavy lines. These waves transition from the colour black to light grey, which is supported by a black midsole with a dark yellow Air unit. Eye-catching details include the lace eyelets and the small Swoosh on the heel, which come in 'Neon' colour. The shoe is rounded off with a black rubber sole, featuring the Nike logo.

name: Nike Air Max 1 WMNS 'Black & White'
text_content: Nike Air Max 1 'Black & White' is an iconic shoe that embodies timeless style and cutting-edge comfort. Featuring a timeless, refined look, this shoe comes in a stylish and functional black and white colour scheme. In a unified and sophisticated design highlighted by the contrast of the neutral colours, this shoe exudes effortless elegance without feeling out of place. The white mesh base provides breathability while the black leather mudguard ensures the sneaker's durability. The Swoosh and branding elements reference the iconic sportswear brand. With its recognizable Air Max cushioning technology, the Nike Air Max 1 'Black & White' offers responsive support and padded comfort for all-day comfort.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Midnight Navy and Baroque Brown'
text_content: Featuring classic design and premium materials, this Nike Dunk Low 'Midnight Navy Ale Brown' is the perfect shoe for any occasion. It has a sophisticated colour scheme featuring midnight navy, ale brown, and pale ivory. Constructed with a variety of materials, evoking quality and craftsmanship that makes it stand out from the rest.Its 'Midnight Navy' corduroy base is layered with brown materials featuring different patterns. The Swoosh adorns the lateral in brown corduroy, matching the outsole colour. Its white laces and branding elements seen on the upper smoothly align with the sneaker's midsole, creating a cohesive look. Enjoy the elegance and sophistication of the timeless brown and blue combination with the Nike Dunk Low 'Midnight Navy Ale Brown'.

name: Nike Air Max 1 '87 QS WMNS 'Obsidian'
text_content: One of the nicest Nike Air Max 1 from 2022? Quite possibly, as the Nike Air Max 1 '87' QS WMNS 'Obsidian' (DV3887-400) has great details and materials.The upper of the sneaker consists of the colours dark blue and green. The branding on the heel and on the nose have the classic college style and are colored dark purple. The whole is finished with a white midsole with a gum outsole.

name: Nike Air Max 1 WMNS 'Sanddrift'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 WMNS 'White Tan' is an elegant edition of the Air Max 1. The sneaker is a WMNS exclusive, meaning the model is available in sizes 35.5 to 44.5. The Nike Air Max WMNS 'White Tan' combines several neutral toned colours. For instance, the sneaker's base consists of white-coloured mesh. The overlays come in bone nubuck and the sleek upper is finished off with a beige Swoosh and mudguard. The midsole colours white with a beige-coloured air unit. Finally, the beige outsole brings the look together.

name: Nike Air Max 1 Premium 'Shima Shima III' - 2023
text_content: Twenty years after the original release of the 'Shima Shima' pack, composed of the Nike Air Trainer 1, Nike Air Max 1 and Nike Dunk High, the Nike Air Max 1 Premium 'Shima Shima III' made its debut to the public in a celebratory spirit. The Air Max 1 silhouette completes the modern adaptation of the pack as part of the 'Shima Shima' collection together with Nike Air Trainer 1 'Shima Shima' and Nike Nike Dunk High Shima, featuring the earthy 'Wolf Grey' and 'Plum Eclipse'. On a 'Summit White' leather base, the sneaker is complemented by the grey overlays and brown mudguard and Swoosh. The laces and font of the tongue tag come in the 'Plum Eclipse' tone while the writing on the tongue tag depicts Japanese symbols in red for a pop of colour. The inner lining consists of a stripped pattern featuring the primary colours of the silhouette. The design is completed by a white midsole with a brown airbag which sits atop a rubber outsole consisting of a mix of brown and grey alternating patches.

name: LeBron x Liverpool x Nike Air Max 1
text_content: Nike brings forward an iconic Air Max 1 silhouette for all sports fans out there. The LeBron x Liverpool x Nike Air Max 1features a colour palette inspired by the signature colours of Liverpool F.C., the club where LeBron James owns shares since 2011. White mesh sets the base of the black and tail leather overlays where the black Swoosh atop the tail quarter panel offers an eye-catching contrast.  The air unit matches the sock liner in a red tone, adding a pop of colour to the shoe. The insole and the heel feature branding details such as logos and the famous 'YNWA' ( You'll Never Walk Alone).

name: Drake x Nike Hot Step Air Terra 'Triple Black' - Nocta
text_content: In addition to the Drake x Nike Hot Step Air Terra 'White' release, American rapper Drake has also created 'Triple Black' version of the Nike Hot Step Air Terra (DH4692-001). This Nike Hot Step Air Terra comes in black and chrome with a premium pebbled leather upper, 3M reflective accents, co-branded insoles and G-Tek traction technology on the outsole.

name: Nike Air Force 1 LV8 'Sail'
text_content: An elegant sneaker that epitomizes timeless elegance is the Nike Air Force 1 LV8 'Sail'. Its clean and crisp colour scheme with an off-white leather base and 'Pure Platinum' suede overlays exudes sophistication and flexibility. 'Sail' Swoosh matching the laces and outsole blend seamlessly into the tonal design. Elevate your style with the subtle allure of the 'Sail' colorway and make a powerful statement wherever you step.

name: Nike Air Max 1 '86 'Blue Safari'
text_content: With the Nike Air Max 1 '86 'Blue Safari' sneaker step into timeless fashion in a striking combination of blue hues.Breathable 'Light Smoke Grey' mesh base features 'Indigo Haze' smooth suede leather overlays. Energizing 'Diffused Blue' hue colours the Swoosh, sock liner and outsole, offering unity to the design. The mudguard and heel embellishments in safari print lend a dash of wildness to the design, making it stand out as special and daring. The sneaker delivers comfort and durability thanks to its quality construction. A responsive cushioning system is provided by the visible Air Max unit in the heel, offering a pleasant and easy stride.The Nike Air Max 1 '86 'Blue Safari' is a must-have sneaker that blends traditional style with modern flare, whether you're hitting the streets or putting a fashionable touch on your regular outfits.

name: Nike Air Max 1 '87 WMNS 'Tiger Swoosh'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 '87 WMNS 'Tiger Swoosh' is a women's shoe that combines the classic style of the original Nike Air Max 1 with eye-catching accents.The sneaker has a leather upper with various animal prints. The mudguard features a cow print, giving the shoe a playful twist. The toebox has a floral print the heel cap colours red and has been given a paisley print. The eyestays of the sneaker are light blue, as is the outsole. The tiger print on the Swoosh of the Nike Air Max 1 '87 WMNS 'Tiger Swoosh' gives the shoe an eye-catching and unique accent, setting this shoe apart from other Nike Air Max 1 models.

name: Nike Air Max 1 SC 'Noise Aqua'
text_content: Air Max 1 SC 'Noise Aqua' fuses iconic design with a captivating colorway. Featuring photon dust, white, cool grey, and noise aqua, the sneaker offers a visually stunning aesthetic.Featuring a white mesh base, the silhouette is accessorised with 'Cool Grey' suede overlays. Smoothing 'Noise Aqua' accents highlight the wavy mudguards and mesh inner lining contributing to the sophisticated look of the sneaker. The white Swoosh decorates the upper sides while branding elements are displayed on the tongue tag and heel. Aside from looking stylish, the shoe provides exceptional comfort thanks to the Air Max unit in the midsole. Take your sneaker collection to the next level with the striking and vibrant Nike Air Max 1 SC 'Noise Aqua'.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Photon Dust'
text_content: The Nike Dunk silhouette debuted in 1985 as a basketball trainer, over three decades later, the Dunk is still being released. The WMNS exclusive 'Photon Dust' is part of the 2021 releases.  The base of the Nike WMNS Dunk Low 'Photon Dust' comes in smooth leather. The trainer uses two colours, white and grey. The grey colour is also known as Photon Dust within Nike hence this colourway name. The original basketball trainer is finished off by a white midsole and a grey outsole.

name: Nike Air Max 1 Premium 'Pecan' - Ugly Duckling
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 Premium 'Pecan' (DZ0482-200) is from the latest AM1 which is expected in 2022.This version will be characterised by the use of natural colours such as Pecan and Yellow Ochre. Besides these colours there will be a darker shade to be found on the sneaker namely the Nike colour Baroque Brown.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Cacao Wow'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Cacao Wow' is a delicious and fashionable sneaker. The colour scheme of this unique shoe combines chocolate and deep brown tones for a mouthwatering look. The leather-constructed upper features a 'Coconut Milk' base and 'Cacao Wow' overlays. The 'Sail' midsole paired with a dark brown outsole completes the design. The Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Cacao Wow' exudes luxury and sophistication.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Diffused Taupe'
text_content: A sleek and stylish women's exclusive, the Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Diffused Taupe' features a minimalistic and clean design that exudes timeless elegance. The upper is crafted with premium Sail leather, while a contrasting pop of colour is provided by 'Diffused Taupe' overlays. 'Plum Eclipse' depicts the Swoosh and branding elements, making this design a tonal masterpiece.  Enjoy a perfect blend of fashion and functionality with the sophisticated Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Diffused Taupe'.

name: Nike Air Max 90 GTX 'Medium Olive'
text_content: An autumn sneaker, the Air Max 90 GTX 'Medium Olive' combines iconic style with weatherproof functionality. As leaves change colour and temperatures drop, Nike and GORE-TEX collaborate to keep your feet dry and comfortable.Covered in earthy hues, the sneaker features GORE-TEX technology, providing a reliable barrier against rain, snow, and wind. Neutral and Medium Olive green compose the majority of the upper, while the 'Burgundy Crush' and 'Cargo Khaki' details enhance the overall appearance of the silhouette. The sneaker offers superior comfort and impact absorption with each step, and the rubber outsole ensures stability on slippery surfaces.You can take on outdoor adventures or navigate city streets with ease in the Nike Air Max 90 GTX 'Medium Olive'. This winterized version of a legendary sneaker keeps you dry, stylish, and comfortable during the colder months. Embrace any terrain with confidence and elevate your footwear game.

name: Nike Air Max 1 WMNS 'Magma Orange' - Patch Work
text_content: The Air Max is a special model, based on a building where elements were visible that you normally do not see. Thus came the unusual idea of making the Air Unit visible. The rest is history!The Nike Air Max 1 'Light Bone' (DZ4709-001) receives a light colorway consisting of 'Light Bone' and 'Neutral Grey'. A bright contrast colour on the sneaker is 'Magma Orange' this colour was also previously seen on the Nike Air Max 1 OG 'Magma Orange'.

name: Nike Air Max 1 'Urawa' - 2023
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 'Urawa' is a remarkable trainer known for its unique and exclusive design. This special edition is named after the Japanese football club Urawa Red Diamonds. The Nike Air Max 1 "Urawa" was first released in 2004 as a tribute to the Japanese football club. After a period of 19 years, this trainer is finally getting a sequel with its upcoming release in 2023.The trainer's upper is made of high-quality materials, such as premium suede and breathable mesh. The trainer has black mesh underlays as a base, contrasting with grey suede overlays. Eye-catching red accents can be found on the eyestays, while gold details adorn the "Nike Air" branding on the tongue tag. To complete the trainer, the signature element, the embroidered Urawa dragon logo, is on the heel of the trainer.The Nike Air Max 1 'Urawa' is valuable to any trainer collection. Its unique design and high-quality construction make this trainer a must-have for fans of exclusive and stylish trainers.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Light Bone'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low Light Bone is the latest release from Nike. It features a leather upper and a midsole with a vintage-style look. The colour scheme includes shades of eggshell, gray, and cream, which give the sneaker a charming appearance. This understated colour palette will surely appeal to those who appreciate the beauty in simplicity.

name: Nike Air Max 1 'Volt Suede'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 'Volt Suede' is a vibrant and eye-catching take on the classic sneaker.  The toe box has a delicate diamond perforated pattern for ventilation. The upper's mudguard, Swoosh and heel branding are all coated in a striking volt-green suede material. The clean white leather utilized for the overlays provides a good contrast to the vibrant volt colour. The visible Air cushioning unit in the heel provides responsive cushioning and impact protection.For sneaker enthusiasts looking to add something bold and distinctive to their collection, the Nike Air Max 1 'Volt Suede' is a must-have.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8 'Black Light Crimson'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8 'Black Light Crimson' combines a timeless silhouette with a fresh colour scheme for a unique design. Designed in sleek black, the upper creates a sharp and sophisticated look. Featuring vibrant accents of 'Light Crimson' red, these sneakers feature a bold and vibrant pop of colour in the mini Swoosh logo, branding elements, and outsole. Their premium leather construction ensures durability and comfort, so they are suitable for everyday use. Make a statement every time you step out wearing the Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8 'Black Light Crimson,' whether you're strolling the streets or hitting the basketball court.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Vintage Navy'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Vintage Navy' sneaker expertly fuses contemporary style with nostalgic vibes to produce truly captivating footwear.The low top profile and blue hue give the design elegance and adaptability by taking inspiration from bygone eras. Its smooth white leather upper is elegantly accessorised by 'Midnight Navy' overlays that rock a satin-like look. 'Coconut Milk' midsole offers a vintage look to the sneaker while matching the laces in the same calming hue. Navy blue rubber outsole and branding elements throughout the upper complete the design. Bring a touch of classic elegance to your shoe collection with the Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Vintage Navy'.

name: Nike Terminator Low 'Black Croc'
text_content: A vintage-inspired sneaker, the Nike Terminator Low 'Black Croc' exudes timeless style. Constructed with a white leather base, the distinctive black crocodile-textured overlays add luxury and sophistication to your footwear collection. Its low-top silhouette and lace-up design make it durable and comfortable.The Nike Terminator Low 'Black Croc' is a versatile and iconic sneaker that will add style to any casual look with its white and black colour palette.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'Black University Blue'
text_content: The Air Max 90 has seen many different colourways and materials over the years and is a classic in sneaker culture. The midsole which is equipped with a visible Nike Air cushioning unit and offers soft cushioning and shock absorption is its trademark. Today, it is still a popular shoe for everyday wear and sports activities. With the Nike Air Max 90 'Black University Blue', we see the model in a simple colorway in black with blue details in the Swoosh and the logo on the tongue and side.

name: Nike Air Max 90 WMNS 'White Metallic Silver'
Nike Air Max 1 '87 WMNS 'Aura'
text_content: Featuring a harmonious blend of rich denim hues and sleek neutrals, the Nike Air Max 1 87 Denim 'Aura' elevates your sneaker game. With its intricate denim textures covering the upper in different hues of blue and beige the 'Aura' colorway adds depth and character to the timeless Air Max 1. A dark mustard hue on the tongue and sticking across the 'Sail' mudguard creates a striking contrast against the denim blues on the base and overlays. Infusing an urban edge, the meticulous material and colour selections make a lasting impression. Nike Air Max 1 87 Denim 'Aura', an embodiment of artistic expression and distinctive style, combines colours and materials with confidence.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Polar Blue'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low 'Polar Blue' is a cool and refreshing sneaker silhouette that effortlessly combines classic design with contemporary flair.The two-toned sneaker features a crisp white leather base with 'Polar Blue' overlays. Branding elements on the tongue tag and heel tab reference the Nike brand while the lateral is dressed in the brand's iconic Swoosh. To complete the design, the white midsole paired with the blue outsole mirrors the upper. Its harmonious colour combination makes the Nike Dunk Low 'Polar Blue' a versatile addition to your wardrobe, whether you're hitting the streets or making a stylish statement.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 WB 'Flax'
text_content: This Air Force 1 '07 WB has been given a 'Flax' colorway. Nike brings back the 'Flax' colorway every year on the Air Force 1, which is no surprise as it is the perfect colorway for Autumn. In addition, the model the Air Force 1 is a big must-have. The sneaker has a nubuck leather upper. A nice detail of the shoe are the round laces that give the sneaker a distinctive look. The upper of the shoe sits on the Air midsole, which ensures optimal comfort. With this sneaker, you know for sure that you are ready for the wet and cold!

name: Nike Air Max 1 WMNS 'Safety Orange'
text_content: A striking and vibrant sneaker, the Nike Air Max 1 WMNS 'Safety Orange' seamlessly combines style and comfort. With its bold 'Safety Orange' colorway, this women's exclusive makes a bold statement with every step. Providing both breathability and durability, the upper features a white mesh base and sail suede overlays. The stunning 'Safety Orange' hue enhances the style and personality of the mudguard, branding elements, and the Swoosh. The visible Air Max unit in the heel provides cushioning and impact absorption. With the Nike Air Max 1 WMNS 'Safety Orange', you can express your vibrant personality whether you're hitting the gym, running errands, or simply enhancing your street style.

name: Travis Scott x Nike Air Trainer 1 SP 'Ashen Slate'
text_content: Travis Scott has a lot of collaborations with Nike to his name. In May 2022, he released several pairs. This release, the Air Trainer 1 and Air Max 1, was first due in December 2021, but was postponed due to the circumstances surrounding Astroworld festival. The Travis Scott x Nike Air Trainer 1 SP 'Wheat' (DR7515-200) features a dark colour scheme. The upper of the pair is made primarily of corduroy. If you look closely you can see several snaps across the upper. When you buy the pair, there is a kind of protection layer attached to the upper with these buttons. You can choose to rock the pair with the protection or without.

name: Nike Air Max 1 ’86 OG 'Obsidian'
text_content: In celebration of Air Max Day earlier in 2023, Nike unveiled a reimagined Air Max 1. This return comes in the classic ‘Obsidian’ colourway, a nod to the shoe's roots. The Nike Air Max 1 '86 OG ‘Obsidian’ faithfully recreates the iconic look with its blue accents on the Swoosh and mudguard, complemented by the customary light grey suedes. White is used for the mesh inserts, midsole, and lace unit, providing a contrasting backdrop for the touches of red that can be spotted on both the outsole and various branding elements.

name: Nike Air Force 1 High Utility 2.0 'Black Gum'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 High Utility 2.0 Black Gum is a sneaker without any concessions. The sneaker has a high silhouette that is adapted to defy winter conditions with ease. The outsole is a lot firmer than the original sole that is normally under the model. The upper is also adapted to these conditions. The upper is also adjusted for these conditions, with a black leather upper and an extra strap at the ankle.

name: Nike Air Max 1 'Crepe Hemp' - 2022
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 'Hemp' is a classic AM1 that got a retro release in 2022. This time not a 1 on 1 retro but a new release with some differences.One of the most annoying aspects of the original Air Max 1 was the material on the nose, it wore out very fast and broke. On the '22 version, we see a different kind of material, which is quite similar. The overlays are made of leather and the small piece on the forefoot is made of canvas. The mudguard is dark brown and is made of suede. Just like the '04 original, this sneaker also has a crepe outsole. The Nike Air Max 1 'Crepe Hemp 2022' has slightly different colours than the '04 version, this is just refreshing and leaves the original in its value.

name: Nike Air Max 1 Safari  'Summit White'
text_content: With a design influenced by the ever so popular 'Safari' print and inspiration from the looks of the snow leopard comes the Air Max 1 'Summit White' FB5059-100. The tonal colorway features a white tumbled leather base, smooth white leather overlays on the upper part and light grey safari print overlays all around the middle of the shoe. The Swoosh also comes in a light grey safari print offering unity to the design. Baby Blue details on the upper eyelets and parts of the outsole diversify the colour palette while keeping the design clean.

name: Nike Air Max Plus '25th Anniversary'
text_content: The Nike Air Max Plus, introduced to the public in 1998, holds a special place in sneaker history. As a tribute to its 25th anniversary, Nike is set to unveil the Nike Air Max Plus 25th Anniversary edition. The shoe's design, crafted by Sean McDowell, draws inspiration from his vacation in Florida, where he was captivated by the swaying palm trees. Notable features of this special edition include its unique gradient design and a pattern reminiscent of crinkled paper. The Air Max Plus also stands out with wavy TPU overlays, mirroring the gentle sway of palm trees. The release incorporates the signature yellow from the TN logo on the visible Air unit, with black accents on various elements, including TPU overlays, laces, lining, midsole, and leather overlays.

name: Nike Dunk High WMNS 'Aluminium'
text_content: Although similar in style to the ‘University Blue’ colour scheme, the ‘Aluminum’ is a WMNS exclusive Nike Dunk High that stands out on its own merit. The two-tone colorway sets light blue ‘Aluminum’ mudguard, lace, Swoosh, and heel overlays on a smooth white leather base. The laces and tongue are white to add more contrast, and a white midsole and light blue outsole round off the look.

name: Social Status x Nike Mac Attack SP 'Summit White'
text_content: This summer saw the Nike Mac Attack undergo a timely revitalization in its OG form, gaining renewed attention through collaborations with James Whitaker's Social Status brand. Now, entering its fourth iteration within the collaboration, the Nike Mac Attack is set to release a 'Summit White' version as part of Social Status' bodega-inspired collection. The upper boasts cracked suede overlays in a bright 'Summit White' tint, while reflective white finishes accentuate the mesh underlays, profile swoosh, and inner lining. Contrast elements come in the form of a jet-black collar, heel counter, and tread. A pre-aged midsole, characteristic of the brand's collaborative series, is complemented by Social Status' typical embellishments, referencing the inner-city currency. Notably, 'Pine Green' accents on the mid-top trim illuminate the tongue tabs and the heel's Nike lettering, adding a vibrant touch to this neutral-coated effort.

name: Nike Air Footscape Woven WMNS 'Black Croc'
text_content: Originally designed by Tory Orzeck, the Nike Air Footscape Woven WMNS ‘Black Croc’ (FQ8129-010) is a modern take on the classic Nike’s Air Footscape Woven design from the late 90s. This ‘Black Croc’ edition features a sophisticated design with an all-black leather upper which is inspired by the crocodile skin texture. The pair features the signature design details such as the asymmetrical lacing system and woven stripe detail on the upper which makes it truly authentic. More details include the pale ivory (‘Sail’) branding on the embroidered tongues and heels, a Swoosh imprinted on the Black insoles, an off-white midsole and a Black waffle-patterned rubber outsole for extra grip.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Rose Whisper'
text_content: The classic colour blocking on the Nike Dunk Low is doing super well on the beloved model. This 'Rose Whisper' colorway confirms this again.The classic composition is that the underlays are a solid colour, in this case white. The overlays, in this case 'Rose Whisper', are also given a solid colour that contrasts with the underlays. The whole thing sits on a white midsole and an outsole in the pink colour.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Mini Swoosh Grey'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low 'Mini Swoosh Grey' is the latest colorway for the Dunk Low model. A padded tongue and collar provide additional comfort to the low-top silhouette. The upper is made of durable leather in white and grey colour enhancements, complemented by a white mid and outer sole, as well as a perforated toe box for ventilation. There is a double swoosh on the sides of the sneakers in grey, and a single mini swoosh on the upper in a light blue colour. Finally, the Nike logo can be found on the pull tab embroidered in a bright red color.

name: Nike Dunk Low Retro WMNS 'Panda'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low 'Panda' is a classic for a reason. It is a sneaker that completes every look and therefore should not be missing in your collection. Clean and simple but still just that little bit extra to the outfit. All the classic features are present, from the nose with perforation to the recognizable swoosh. The name of this colorway says it all. The 'Panda' is a black and white Dunk Low that goes with every outfit. The upper is made of white leather, the overlays and swoosh of black leather. White branding on the tongue and heel finish the design.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 WMNS 'Dusted Clay'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 '07 WMNS 'Dusted Clay' is a women's exclusive sneaker designed to elevate your autumn looks.Constructed with a white leather base and 'Pale Ivory' suede overlays, the design integrates seamlessly into any casual outfit. Swoosh and heel tabs are crafted in 'Dusted Clay' brown to elevate the silhouette. Branding elements on the upper complete the design while the white outsole offers a clean aesthetic. Its clean design and versatile colour make the Nike Air Force 1 '07 WMNS 'Dusted Clay' a must-have among sneaker enthusiasts.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'Neutral Olive'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 Premium is a shoe filled with the brand's technology, offering superior comfort and style. Featuring Nike's iconic swoosh branding throughout the textile uppers, these sneakers feature a tonal design in the ‘Neutral Olive’ colorway. The shoes are made with suede and leather overlays for durability and luxury. In the midsole, a visible Air unit provides enhanced cushioning, while the foam midsole provides exceptional air cushioning. Durable traction on challenging terrain is provided by the rubber outsole. An Air Max 90 Premium boasts a distinctive and high-quality design featuring moulded rubber details and embossed branding.

name: NOCTA x Nike Air Force 1 Low GS 'Love You Forever'
text_content: NOCTA x Nike Air Force 1 Low GS 'Love You Forever', is a highly anticipated collaboration that blends style with sentiment. The Air Force 1 Low gets a unique touch with this special edition sneaker, created in collaboration with the Canadian sensation Drake NOCTA. Constructed with a premium all white leather upper with a perforated toe panel the design has visual appeal and breathability. Its moulded outsole adorned with miniature hearts evokes the theme of eternal love. Synthetic leather lining and an embroidered North Star on the left heel tab give this sneaker that special touch. Embrace a symbol of style and affection with the NOCTA x Nike Air Force 1 Low GS 'Love You Forever'.

name: Nike Air Max 90 SE WMNS 'Lace Toggle'
text_content: The latest ensemble of Nike Air Max 90 features a combination of lace toggles and outdoors-ready tooling. Its design includes houndstooth laces, autumn-friendly tones, hazelnut-treated eye stays and cream-stamped tongue tabs. The sneaker also has dark olive ballistic mesh on the base layer and tongue. Meanwhile, chocolate brown suede overlays dominate the mid-foot section, and army green profile swooshes introduce a layered aesthetic.

name: Nike Air Max 1 WMNS LX 'Obsidian'
text_content: With its timeless charm and modern flair, the Nike Air Max 1 WMNS LX 'Obsidian' is a classic and sophisticated sneaker. The women's exclusive 'Obsidian' colorway blends deep navy blue with subtle red hints. The smooth white mesh base is complemented by the rich blue hue that covers the mudguard and Swoosh. 'Off-white' overlays around the laces, midsole and medial blend into the design while accessorised by red details. Air Max cushioning for excellent responsiveness makes it ideal for all-day activities.A refined design and subtle detailing set this Nike Air Max 1 WMNS LX 'Obsidian' apart from the rest.

name: Nike Air Max 1 '87 SE WMNS 'Hangul Day'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 '87 SE WMNS 'Sail Khaki' (FQ8150-133) is a women’s exclusive model which is part of Nike’s celebration of Korea’s Hangul Day. This commemorative product was created in honour of the Korean holiday celebrating the creation of their alphabet during the 15th century.  The Air Max 1 Sail Khaki features a clean colour scheme, crafted with a white mesh base and suede overlays in a Orewood Brown shade. The tongues, Swooshes, and laces come in a pale coconut milk shade of white. Some special design features are the Hangul characters on the insoles, heels and the hangtag, all placed on the sole with a slight yellow finish that delivers an “aged” aesthetic onto the Air Max 1.

name: Nike Air Max 1 PRM 'Slate Blue'
text_content: A traditional silhouette and contemporary design cues come together in the Nike Air Max 1 PRM 'Slate Blue' creating a versatile and fashionable sneaker. 'Slate blue' colouring and a quality combination of materials, including suede, leather, and textile, make up the upper. White highlights on the midsole, laces, and Nike branding contrast with the hue.The intricately detailed design on the shoe's heel depicting trees shadows in black lends a distinctive touch and a subtle but eye-catching detail. The gum outsole completes the shoe's vintage look, and Air Max technology provides every step in comfort and cushioning. For sneaker enthusiasts wishing to add a versatile, warm, and stylish shoe to their collection, the Nike Air Max 1 PRM 'Slate Blue' is a great choice.

name: Nike Dunk Low Hemp WMNS 'Coconut Milk'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low Hemp WMNS 'Coconut Milk' is a fashionable sneaker with natural beauty thanks to its creamy colour scheme.Hemp, a sustainable and long-lasting material, is used to make the upper of the Nike Dunk Low Hemp WMNS 'Coconut Milk'. The shoe's hemp construction gives it a distinctive feel and aesthetic appeal, and the creamy coconut milk hue gives it a classic, timeless look that goes well with many different ensembles.  The padded collar and cushioned insole offer superb all-day comfort. The distinctive Swoosh design is delicately interwoven into the Nike insignia, highlighting the quality and style of the shoe. For people who value both style and sustainability, the Nike Dunk Low Hemp WMNS 'Coconut Milk' is a must-have shoe. It is an adaptable option for numerous events thanks to the hemp material it is made of, the simple colour scheme, and the cosy style.

name: Nike Dunk Low Retro 'Panda'
text_content: A lot of colour schemes of the Nike Dunk Low only consist of two colours. This 'Panda' colorway also uses this scheme. The upper of the low model is completely made of leather, except for the tongue. The tongue is made of textile.  As the name of the colorway suggests, the pair is made up of the colours of a panda. The tongue, side and collar are in white. The overlays, heeltab, Swoosh and laces are in black. To complete the colour scheme, Nike has made the midsole white and the outsole black. The 'Panda' colorway is a common sight on sneakers from the American sports brand and is extremely popular.

name: Nike Air Max 1 'Chili 2.0'
text_content: Nike has revived several AM1 models from the archive in 2023, one example being the Nike Air Max 1 'Chili 2023'. The Chili first came out in 2003, now, some 20 years later, the colorway is back. Some differences can be seen between the 2023 version and the original model. For instance, the upper of the updated version is of a lighter shade of grey. The branding on the heel is black on the 2023 version and, finally, the tongue label is predominantly white instead of red. Broadly speaking, the original colour scheme has remained pretty much intact. The Swoosh is still of sheet red colour that the air unit also adopts. The Nike Air Max 1 'Chili 2023' is finished off by a white sole with black accents.

name: Nike Dunk Low PRM WMNS 'Vintage Panda'
text_content: The iconic 'Panda' colorway comes in a nostalgic iteration in the Nike Dunk Low PRM WMNS 'Vintage Panda'.One of the most popular Nike Dunk Low colorways, the 'Panda' features a white leather base accessorised with black overlays. The twist of the 'Vintage Panda' stands in its 'Sail' midsole which gives the design an aged look. Paired with the classic black rubber outsole and matching laces, the design is set to stand out from the crowd. Extend your sneaker collection with a classic colorway with a stylish twist in the Nike Dunk Low PRM WMNS 'Vintage Panda'.

name: Nike Air Max 90 SE WMNS 'Animal'
text_content: Show your wild side with this Nike Air Max 90 SE WMNS 'Multi Animal' (DH5075-100). The iconic Nike Air Max 90 features a white mesh and leather base. This is the perfect canvas for a detailed mix of various safari prints used on the overlays. These prints include leopard, faux fur, safari, and suede. White Swooshes, laces, and midsole on a tri-colour rubber outsole complete the design.

name: Nike Shox TL WMNS 'White'
text_content: The Nike Shox TL is set to make a return in a women's-exclusive 'White' iteration in 2023. This anticipated release follows its previous availability in 2019. The shoe features a classic 'White/White-Metallic Silver-Max Orange' colour scheme and is constructed with a combination of open and ballistic mesh materials, complemented by glossy TPU overlays. Notably, 3M reflective accents enhance its design. The sneaker is completed with a tonal white Shox tooling that defines its profile.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Fresh 'Triple White'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Fresh 'Triple White' was first released in 1982. it was designed by designer Bruce Kilgore and was originally intended as a basketball shoe. The name of the shoe comes from the plane that transports the US president and was chosen by Nike as a symbol of the shoe's strength and quality. The shoe lives up to its name and is completely white. features a leather upper and a thick rubber sole with air cushioning. The Air Force 1 is an iconic model from Nike and has been released in various colour combinations and variations over the years. Since the colorway has a timeless design that can be combined at will, it has always inspired sneaker fans all over the world.

name: Nike Air Max 1 Premium 'Michigan'
text_content: The Air Max 1 PRM 'Varsity Maize' takes its inspiration from the state of Michigan, with a colour palette including Midnight Navy, Varsity Maize and Natural. This version of the Air Max 1 uses a base of buttery leather, tongues of nylon and embroidered mini-Swooshes on the forefoot. The Swooshes have a snake print, which pairs well with the crocodile print on the mudguards. A premium leather lining on top of the Sail midsole and yellow rubber outsoles complete the sneaker's design.

name: Nike Air Max 1 Premium 'Honeydew' - Ugly Duckling
text_content: A sleek and timeless design which has been loved since 1987, that can only be the Nike Air Max 1!In 2022, the model is back on Nike's radar. There will be a Premium version of the model in Anthracite. Besides this colour, the Nike Air Max 1 Premium 'Anthracite' (DZ0482-001) also features the colours Honeydew, Black and Kumquat.

name: Nike Dunk High WMNS 'Panda'
text_content: The Nike Dunk received a lot of attention in 2021. Both the high silhouette and the low silhouette were released in different colorways. Nike saw the popularity of the model rise and decided to release a bunch of new colorways in the following year as well. The Nike WMNS Dunk High 'Black & White' has a simple colour scheme. The upper is made of leather. The toebox, side panel and collar are in white. The overlays are black. Because of the black and white colour scheme, this shoe is also referred to as 'Panda'. This shoe is easy to style with a lot of different outfits.

name: Nike Air Max 1 Premium 'Dirty Denim' - 2022
text_content: An unprecedented classic and all-time favourite of the Dutch sneaker lovers; the Nike Air Max 1. From Atmos to Patta collabs, they always do it right!This time around, the Nike Air Max 1 got a 'premium' makeover. This often results in a combination of nice materials and details on the sneakers. The Nike Air Max 1 Premium 'Mineral Slate' (DV3050-300) also comes in different colours like Deep Royal Blue and Lemon Wash.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Light Orewood Brown' - Next Nature
text_content: Through their ‘Move To Zero’ Campaign, Nike have made many positive changes to their production methods and company ethos, and part of that is through releasing sustainable and eco-conscious sneakers. ‘Next Nature’ is a collection that is crafted with at least 20% recycled material by weight and is tagged with a Swoosh-wheel logo on the tongue and/or sockliner.  The Nike Dunk Low ‘Light Orewood Brown’ – Next Nature has simple white underlays that are covered by creamy light brown panels. The Swoosh has been crafted from cracked leather for a hint of texture. The white midsole sits on a grey outsole that has been created from Nike Grind material (made apparent by the faint speckles throughout).

name: Nike Air Max Plus Black University Blue (2022)
Nike Dunk High Retro 'Panda'
text_content: The Nike Dunk High Retro 'Panda' (DD1399-105) brings a two-tone colorway to the iconic silhouette. The colorway and materials are true to the original 1985 release, culminating in a leather upper in sharply contrasting black and white tones. The smooth leather overlays, laces and Swoosh of this versatile pair are fully immersed in black, while the toebox, tongue and collar balance the yin and yang look with white. Atop the lightly padded nylon tongue, a woven label with crimson Nike branding provides some colour.

name: Nike Air Max 1 SC 'Light Bone'
text_content: Tinker Hatfield's Air Max 1 SC model has become an iconic silhouette in the sneaker scene since its debut in 1987. Among a plethora of Air Max 1 colorways, Nike surprises us with the 'Light Bone' colorway. This version stands out for its material choices, with a cream-colored leather base instead of the typical mesh.The canvas mudguards, which contribute to both the appearance and composition of the 'Light Bone' version, add to its uniqueness; plus, the outsole is shared with the Air Max 1 Crepe model, ensuring continuity. Nike's regular release of new colorways reflects the Air Max 1's enduring popularity. Cream-colored leather and canvas are combined with a familiar outsole in the unexpected 'Light Bone' version.

name: Nike Air Max 1 WMNS 'Tour Yellow'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 ‘Tour Yellow’ (DX2954-001) is a bright, summery pair, built from tumbled leather and mesh. The premium tumbled leather overlays on the heel and quarter are a shade of pristine white, matching the mesh on the toe and nylon at the ankle, while the tumbled leather on the mudguard and on the Swoosh have been given a zesty yellow colour to match the Air Unit in the heel. A light grey rubber outsole and white midsole round off the look.

name: Nike Air Max 90 WMNS 'United in Victory'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 WMNS 'United in Victory' sneaker is a strong, empowering shoe that celebrates cohesion and conquest. This women's exclusive creates a visual representation of strength and solidarity by paying homage to the idea of banding together and accomplishing greatness.The upper of the Nike Air Max 90 WMNS 'United in Victory' is made of a mix of high-quality leather and mesh materials, providing both durability and breathability. The eye-catching colour scheme uses a combination of hemp, strong black, and clean white to represent the unwavering determination and teamwork necessary for success. Every step is comfortable thanks to the legendary Air Max unit in the heel, which offers outstanding cushioning and impact absorption.The Nike Air Max 90 WMNS 'United in Victory' is a statement-making shoe that uplifts and inspires thanks to its distinctive design and meaningful concept. The 'United in Victory' colorway is also featured on the AF-1, Court Legacy Lift and Victori One Slide designs.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 '07 (DR0155-001) has a tough look. The Air Force 1 is one of the most famous colorways of Nike and has been a staple in the sneaker world since 1982. Especially the low version, which was introduced later, is a favourite with many. This colorway of the Nike Air Force 1 '07 has a blue grey upper. This gives the sneaker a fresh look. The Swoosh on the middle panel seems to be cut-out. The orange details contrast nicely with the grey-blue upper. The midsole is dark grey. The upper is made of leather. There are perforation holes on the toe cap. In short, a fresh colorway that is appropriate for all four seasons.

name: Nike Air Max 95 'Anatomy of Air'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 95 has received a very special makeover, namely an anatomical one! The sneaker has been given the characteristic colours of anatomical dolls and drawings. The Nike Air Max 95 'Anatomy of Air' (DM0012-600) is a very unique pair!The upper still has the famous gradient, only this time it runs from white, to pink and ends with dark red. The nose of the sneaker is coloured light grey. All these panels are extra stitched. The sole and lace come in an off-white colour that again matches the colour of bones! A nice detail can be found on the sole, here is a small anatomical drawing.

name: Nike Air Jordan 1 Mid 'Obsidian'
text_content: Maintaining its iconic look in a lower profile, the Nike Air Jordan 1 Mid ‘Obsidian’ (554724-174) comes in a classically clean navy blue and white colorway, constructed from a premium leather upper on top of a cushioned midsole and rubber sole. Navy panels overlay the white base on the heel, ankle, and around the toe. The Wings logo cuts through the navy ankle strap in clean white, while the Swoosh is a dark slash across the white midfoot. Metallic gold labelling adorns the light grey nylon tongue for a finishing detail.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'Diffused Blue'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 'Diffused Blue' is a stylish and comfortable trainer that continues Nike's classic Air Max 90 line. The trainer features an upper made of different materials, such as leather, mesh and suede, in a beautiful 'Diffused Blue' colour. This is complemented by black accents and a white midsole with a visible Air Max unit for excellent cushioning and comfort.The Air Max 90 'Diffused Blue' has a timeless and versatile design that fits perfectly with different outfits and occasions. The trainer has a lightweight construction and a padded collar and tongue for extra comfort while wearing. In addition, the rubber outsole and grip pattern ensure excellent grip and durability.With its striking 'Diffused Blue' colour and the iconic design of the Air Max 90, this trainer is a great choice for anyone looking for a comfortable and stylish trainer for everyday wear or sports activities. Whether you go running, hiking or just want to wear it casually, this trainer offers the perfect combination of style and functionality.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8 'White Multi-Etch Swoosh'
text_content: Featuring a classic all-white leather upper and a multi-etch Swoosh design, the Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8 'White Multi-Etch Swoosh' brings a modern twist to the classic black and white combination. The design features a black Swoosh on the lateral, paired with a mini Swoosh on the mudguard that adds dynamism to the design. The etched pattern adds texture and depth to the iconic Nike logo, creating a striking visual effect. Featuring Nike Air cushioning, the Air Force 1 '07 LV8 offers unparalleled comfort and support, making it the perfect choice for everyday use. Make a bold statement wherever you go with the Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8 'White Multi-Etch Swoosh'.

name: Billie Eilish x Nike Air Force 1 'White'
text_content: Following the debut of the 'Mushroom' and 'Sequoia' colorways, the Billie Eilish Air Force 1 now also gets a 'White' colorway. As with the previous designs, the white version features fragmented patchwork uppers made from recycled textiles. The nylon base features leather cutouts, nylon wrapguards and stitching accents. To complete the design of the sneaker, there are additional details on the tongue and lacing. Pineapple fibre insoles decorated with the joint brand and classic sole finished off the look.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Metallic Silver'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low WMNS ‘Metallic Silver’ sneakers are a stylish addition to any outfit, adding a touch of glamour with their clean white mesh upper and metallic silver leather overlays and on the classic Nike Swoosh. The white branding on the tongue and the heel, gives the sneakers a sleek and modern look. The classic white midsole and grey outsole provide a comfortable and durable foundation for these sneakers.

name: Nike Air Trainer 1 SP 'Dark Smoke Grey'
text_content: In 2022, Nike released a new version of the Air Trainer. This SP version is a heavily modified version of the original.There is a lot going on with this sneaker, with multiple panels decorated with reflective contrast pieces. The middle panel, around the Swoosh, has a light gradient pattern. On the upper, multiple shades of grey are used, the outsole with its yellow colour provides contrast.

name: Off-White x Nike Air Force 1 Mid 'Varsity Maize'
text_content: The Off-White x Nike Air Force 1 Mid 'Varsity Maize' fuses the classic AF-1 design with the avant-garde vision of Off-White. White and yellow hues give the Air Force 1 Mid a bold look. Featuring a full leather construction with perforations on the toe, breathable mesh tongue, and a clean white backdrop, this shoe is set to make a statement. Its two-toned design stands out as 'Varsity Maize' yellow accents on the overlays, ankle straps, laces, and tongue add to the striking look. Embroidered details as well as classic Off-White elements contribute to the authenticity of the sneaker. Off-White x Nike Air Force 1 Mid 'Varsity Maize' embodies the perfect blend of style and innovation.

name: Nike V2K Run WMNS 'Summit White'
text_content: The model is a new casual sneaker with a cool Y2K look for women whose release we can expect in July 2023. The design is reminiscent of the models we know from the 2000s. It has a chunky rubber sole, and the upper is covered with a coarse mesh fabric. The colorway 'Summit White' brings a futuristic look with the silver Swoosh in combination with the contrast of black and white.

name: Patta x FC Barcelona x Nike Air Max Plus
text_content: The special edition release Patta x FC Barcelona x Nike Air Max Plus brings together the distinctive style of Patta, the iconic FC Barcelona football club, and the legendary Nike Air Max Plus silhouette. The Amsterdam-based streetwear pioneer Patta has teamed up with FC Barcelona to create a stylish streetwear interpretation of the Air Max Plus.The sneaker features an eye-catching gradient in fuchsia and deep blue, the football club's iconic colours, paired with black details. The two Swooshes decorate the lateral in the same legendary hues and bold branding, making it a true collector's item. Nike branding, FC Barcelona's emblem, and Patta's signature touch make this sneaker the perfect fusion of fashion and sport.Embrace the rich heritage of football and sneaker culture with this exclusive Patta x FC Barcelona x Nike Air Max Plus collaboration.

name: Nike Dunk Low SP 'University Red'
text_content: Stylish and comfortable, the Nike Dunk Low SP 'University Red' makes a great statement piece. Featuring one of the most popular colours in the Nike collection, 'University Red' adds an edgy and iconic touch to the classic Dunk Low design. Constructed with a white leather base, the red overlays shine bright on the silhouette's upper. The two-toned colorway features branding elements on the tongue tag and heel tab as well as the iconic Swoosh on the side. White midsole paired with a red rubber outsole complete the design. Add the Nike Dunk Low SP 'University Red' to your collection. Whether you're dressed up or down, these shoes will elevate your style.

name: Premium Goods x Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Tan'
Nike Air Force 1 Low WMNS 'Vintage Gorge Green'
Nike Air Force 1 '07 'University Blue'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 '07 'University Blue' is a subtle colorway of the legendary Nike Air Force 1 model, known for its timeless style and iconic design. This colourway features a fresh and vibrant colorway with the signature 'University Blue', making it a trendy choice for sneaker lovers.The upper of the 'University Blue' is made of premium leather. The sneaker is all white with bright 'University Blue' accents, reminiscent of classic Carolina Blue. The shoe has a clean and minimalist design, with subtle branding, emphasising the bright colour on the upper and outsole.

name: Nike Air Force 1 LX WMNS 'United in Victory'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 LX WMNS 'United in Victory' sneaker is a strong, empowering shoe that celebrates cohesion and conquest. With a remarkable design that combines style and meaning, this women's exclusive pays homage to the idea of banding together and achieving greatness.The premium leather upper of the Nike Air Force 1 LX WMNS 'United in Victory' offers durability and a hint of luxury. The striking colour combination of hemp, bright white, and sharp black accents represents the unwavering resolve and teamwork that are essential for success. The 'United in Victory' graphic on the Swoosh and heel tab add a special touch to the iconic Air Force 1 silhouette and sends a strong message of unity and strength. The rubber outsole ensures dependable traction on a variety of surfaces, while the cushioned insole and padded collar provide support and plush cushioning. The Nike Air Force 1 LX WMNS 'United in Victory' is more than just a pair of shoes; it's a declaration of empowerment and unity thanks to its exceptional design and meaningful message. The 'United in Victory' colorway is also featured on the Air Max 90, Court Legacy Lift and Victori One Slide designs.

name: Nike Air Max 1 '87 WMNS 'Burgundy Crush'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 '87 NBHD 'Burgundy Crush' (DV3888-600) is one of the sneakers that is being looked forward to in 2022. The beloved model gets a colorway consisting of the colour Burgundy Crush. Burgundy always does well on the model, the Patta x Parra x Nike Air Max 1 'Cherrywood' being the perfect example.

name: Nike P-6000 'Coconut Milk'
text_content: The Nike P-6000 'Coconut Milk' is made of mesh covered with overlays of synthetic leather and suede. The P-6000's main colours are 'Metallic Silver' and 'Coconut Milk' which are complemented by black and white. On the tongue is the text "Bowerman Series" referring to Nike co-founder Bill Bowerman. The shoe is finished with a midsole in white and black, backed by a rubber outsole.

name: Nike Air Max Plus TN
text_content: The Nike Air Max Plus TN ‘Triple Black’ was released ahead of the 20th Anniversary of the Air Max Plus. The all-black colorway features a synthetic upper with breathable mesh inserts and bold TPU ribs, and a lightweight midsole with Tuned Air technology and a Max Air sole unit.

name: Nike Air Force 1 07 WMNS 'Triple White'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 07 in triple white has been one of the most popular and best selling sneakers for some time now. The Air Force 1 silhouette designed by Bruce Kilgore came in a high version in 1982, the low version only appeared in 1986. After all this time, the Nike Air Force 1 as a model is still leading in the sneaker world and even beyond. The popularity of this classic white version proves that a classic design in a subtle white version is still unbeatable. The silver lace dubrae is the only contrast to the all-white version of this sneaker. The upper is made of white leather. The upper is made of white leather, as are the laces, the lining, the midsole and the outsole. A sneaker that cannot be missed in any shoe collection.

name: NOCTA x Nike Glide 'White'
text_content: The NOCTA x Nike Glide 'White' features a striking silhouette constructed from honeycomb mesh, TPU Swooshes and a leather upper. The NOCTA signature appears on several parts of the shoe, namely the tongue, the insole and on one of the silver bug eyes in the midsole. The Nike NOCTA Glide White has reflective details on the lace eyelets and the pull tab on the heel. The shoe is finished with a rubber sole that features G-TEK grip technology.

name: Nike Air Max Plus 3 'Spider-Man'
text_content: In addition to a collaborative Air Jordan 1, the brand has introduced several inline colourways that bear a resemblance to the superhero. One of these offerings is the Nike Air Max Plus 3, unofficially honouring Miles Morales' signature suit. The shoe predominantly features a black colour scheme, mirroring Morales' hero attire. Black is applied across the mesh base, TPU detailing, and sole unit. Red and blue accents are strategically placed on the side and heel, replicating the shading and decals seen on-screen when the young Spider-Man swings into action. Featuring the comfort and style of the Nike Air Max Plus 3 silhouette, the Nike Air Max Plus 3 tribute to Miles Morales offers a unique and stylish option.

name: Nike Air Max 90 Reflective 'Olive'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 Reflective in the 'Olive/Black' colourway (DZ4504-300) is a distinctive iteration that enhances the classic Air Max 90 design. The upper features reflective details on the mudguards for improved visibility in low-light conditions. Crafted from a blend of materials, including mesh for the base, sturdy tumbled leather for the overlays, and reflective elements, the shoe offers a textured and eye-catching appearance. The olive and black hues dominate the upper, creating a versatile and modern aesthetic. With meticulous attention to detail and the added reflective elements, the Air Max 90 Reflective in 'Olive/Black' offers a stylish and functional option for those seeking visibility and flair in their footwear.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 'Triple White'
text_content: There are classics and then there is the Nike Air Force 1 'Triple White'.  The nickname gives it away, the sneaker has an all white colorway. This sneaker also has a leather upper for that classic Nike sports look. The silhouette of the Air Force is characterized by the simple flat design that rests on a sturdy sole.

name: Nike Dunk Low Retro PRM 'Mica Green'
text_content: Fresh and colourful, the Nike Dunk Low Retro PRM 'Mica Green' is the ideal sneaker for spring and summer. Constructed with a pale colour palette, the premium leather and canvas used on the upper offer comfort and style. 'Photon Dust' canvas upper ensures the sneaker's breathability while the 'Mica Green' leather overlays increase the shoe's durability. 'Sail' tumbled leather Swoosh and branded heel tab adds to the style of the sneaker and its material mix. Branding elements on the tongue tag and heel depict the renowned Nike logo. The pale green tongue and laces nicely contrast the sail outsole of the sneaker, providing unity to the design. Its colour scheme is ideal for those looking for a vibrant and fun look that is still adaptable to a variety of outfits. The colorway also comes available in the Air Force 1 design.

name: Gore-Tex x Nike ACG Air Zoom Gaiadome 'Black'
Nike Air Force 1 Shadow 'White'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Shadow 'White' takes inspiration from the classic Air Force 1 and adds different elements to its silhouette. The sneaker features an all-white colorway. The double overlays on the upper give the pair a playful twist. The Shadow also has a raised midsole. On the middle panel of the Nike Air Force 1 Shadow 'White' is the Swoosh. Like the upper, the Swoosh is white. On the midsole, the Air logo is put. This logo is put on the midsole twice and runs over the heel. There are perforation holes on the nose. These help the sneaker to breathe.

name: Nike Air Max 1 Corduroy PRM 'Coral Stardust'
text_content: A modern take on a timeless silhouette, the Nike Air Max 1 Corduroy PRM 'Coral Stardust' combines premium materials and distinctive design elements to produce a shoe that is both fashionable and cosy. Coral pink corduroy that constructs the upper offers the sneaker a bold look. Nike's iconic Swoosh in 'Bright Coral' corduroy gives the shoe a splash of colour. The iconic Air Max unit is located in the heel of the midsole's white foam construction, offering responsive cushioning for all-day comfort. 'Oxen Brown' used on the sock liner and rubber outsole completes the design while diversifying the colour palette. Branding elements on the heel and tongue tag come in the same soft brown hue, matching the vibe of the sneaker. With its distinctive and fashionable design, the Nike Air Max 1 Corduroy PRM 'Coral Stardust' is a versatile shoe that is ideal for both casual and athletic wear.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Blue Tint' - Next Nature
text_content: Women's-exclusive Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Blue Tint' - Next Nature, is part of Nike's "Next Nature" pack, which emphasizes sustainability without compromising on style. With a tropical-inspired palette and rich texture, this sneaker features an eye-catching colour combination. 'Cobalt Bliss' overlays and lacing system stand out against a white base, creating a striking contrast. Branding elements, Swoosh and outsole in 'Blue Tint' create a cohesive look.Enjoy the perfect blend of style, comfort, and eco-conscious construction with the Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Blue Tint' - Next Nature.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Triple White'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Triple White' is a release especially for the ladies and has an all-white colorway. This makes the sneaker the ideal pair to combine with different outfits. The pair was released in 2021 and is still a must in the shoe closet. The sneaker has a leather upper and is white from head to toe. The Nike logo is in black on the tongue and on the heel in white.

name: Parris Goebel x Nike Dunk Low 'Playful Pink'
text_content: The highly anticipated Parris Goebel x Nike Dunk Low 'Playful Pink' is a vibrant and stunning collaboration that will surely turn heads. Nike created this exclusive sneaker with Parris Goebel as a tribute to her unique artistic vision as a choreographer and dancer. Incorporating pink patent overlays and Bronzine leather underlays creates an eye-catching and playful aesthetic for this design. Every detail is meticulously crafted, from the Clear Jade patent leather Swooshes to the raised "Nike" lettering on the heels. Gold Nike dubrae, upside-down Nike branding on the tongue tags, to the Parris Goebel branding on the insoles, add uniqueness to the sneakers. The design is completed by an aged midsole that adds character. Get a pair of the Parris Goebel x Nike Dunk Low 'Playful Pink' for some stylish and creative footwear.

name: Nike Air Max 1 '86 OG Golf 'Sea Glass'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 '86 OG 'Sea Glass' features 'Sea Glass', 'Sequoia', 'Mica Green' and 'Lime Blast' colours combined with breathable mesh, comfortable suede and a nylon tongue. Eye-catching details include Lime Blast accents on the upper lace eyelets and insoles, and the Nike-Air logo on the heel. The speckled midsole features a large Air bubble, providing comfort and support.

name: Nike Air Max 1 '86 OG 'University Red'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 '86 OG 'University Red' mostly known by sneakerheads by the 'Big Bubble' nickname brings back to the public the original design that made Nike the iconic brand that is today. The revolutionary design of Tinker Hatfield took over the footwear industry in a way nobody could have predicted. With an architectural background, Hatfield designed the sneaker with a visible air bubble, which was highly criticized as it was considered too innovative and eccentric. Luckily, Nike believed in innovative thinking and from there on the rest is history. The '86 OG silhouette features a white mesh base with grey suede overlays around the lacing system and heel. The guard is constructed with intense 'University Red' suede together with the Swoosh. The branding elements on the heel tab and tongue tag also come written in the same red hue as well as the insole and upper eyestays. A white midsole supports the upper while the outsole is constructed of a mix of white red and black patches. The element that makes this shoe truly authentic is the enlarged air bubble which at the time was a manufacturing mistake, thus the newer models feature a significantly smaller one.The colorway also comes in WMNS and GS Sizing.

name: A-COLD-WALL x Nike Air Max Plus 'Black'
text_content: A-COLD-WALL has joined forces with Nike for Fall 2023, introducing two stylish monochromatic versions of the Air Max Plus. These editions come in ‘Black’ and ‘Platinum Tint’ colourways, offering a sleek and understated aesthetic. The sneakers depart from the traditional mesh build, featuring an all-black premium leather for the upper, while the mesh is used for the inner lining, ensuring both style and breathability. Skillfully moulded plastic TPU overlays add a premium touch.
