Subtle "ACW" branding is placed on the tongues, shank plate, insoles, and heels, while the iconic "TN" branding remains intact. Available in men's sizing, these special editions will be presented in co-branded packaging, enhancing their overall appeal.

name: Nike ACG Mountain Fly Low GORE-TEX 'Dark Smoke Grey'
text_content: Nike's outdoor sub-brand ACG also releases shoes focused on different activities in nature. ACG stands for All Conditions Gear. The items are designed for different weather conditions, like the Nike ACG Mountain Fly. The Nike ACG Mountain Fly GORE-TEX 'Dark Smoke Grey' (DD2861-002) matches all your hike-outfits. The upper is extra protected by the use of GORE-TEX, which makes the material extra waterproof. The upper is finished in a dark grey colour. This colour is also found on the midsole. To spice up the colour scheme, there are several black accents around the shoe. The outsole ensures that you have enough grip during your hike through the mountains.

name: Nike Air Max 1 LX WMNS 'Rugged Orange'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 WMNS LX 'Rugged Orange' shoe will help you make a statement. This sneaker's upper features an eye-catching combination of hues in tones of Rugged Orange, Sail, Orewood and Brown-Sundial. The 'Sail' mesh base ensures breathability while dressed with 'Orewood' tumbled leather overlays. 'Rugged Orange' mudguard smoothly complements the design of the upper. The same orange hue is used in depicting the Swoosh and Branding elements on the heel and tongue tag. Details around the eyelets and outsole in 'Brown-Sundial' offer the design a chic touch. The Nike Air Max 1 WMNS LX 'Rugged Orange' is a must-have addition to your collection, whether you're hitting the streets or making a fashion statement. Take a bold stance while wearing this striking sneaker as you walk down the street.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Industrial Blue'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low 'Industrial Blue' delivers classic design and modern aesthetics, featuring a striking blue, white and black colour scheme. A stylish and functional sneaker with attention to detail, the low silhouette boasts premium materials. Its white leather base is smoothly complemented by black overlays, tongue and lacing system. Added to these two tones, the eye-catching 'Industrial Blue' covers the collar and Swoosh. The gradient effect of combining blue and black in the creation of the Swoosh gives an iconic touch to the design. A world of bold self-expression and urban sophistication awaits you with the Nike Dunk Low 'Industrial Blue'. The colorway is also available in GS, PS and TD sizes.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'Phantom Neutral Olive'
text_content: Nike has extended its summer collection with a fresh colour palette for the Air Max 90. This new ‘Phantom Neutral Olive’ colourway is designed for both summer and the transition into autumn. The shoe boasts a blend of materials, including mesh, leather, ripstop, and suede, and features a phantom base with light bone accents on the upper. To highlight the Swoosh and parts of the midsole, neutral olive is used, while muted red tones add emphasis to the Nike Air Max branding throughout the shoe, creating a well-rounded and appealing design.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'Ironstone Stardust'
text_content: Embracing the transition from summer to autumn, Nike introduces a fresh take on the Air Max 90, paying respect to its rich heritage. The new colourway ’Ironstone Stardust’ captures the essence of the changing seasons. The upper is adorned with Ironstone-hued suede overlays that evoke the imagery of autumn leaves, creating an earthy backdrop for the contrasting design elements. The striking accents on the profile Swooshes and TPU components inject vibrant energy into the look, while the dark Black mudguard pays homage to the iconic "Infrared" release of 1990, infusing nostalgia and depth. The inner lining consistently follows the "Red Stardust" theme, contributing to a cohesive overall ensemble. Completing the design is a sole unit that harmoniously blends Summit White, Ironstone, Black, and Red Stardust, creating an aesthetically compelling and seasonally appropriate balance.

name: Nike Shox TL WMNS 'Triple Black'
text_content: The Nike Shox TL Triple Black is a sleek sneaker known for its striking all-black design. Its upper is crafted from premium black leather and showcases bold Nike Swoosh logos on the lateral sides. To ensure a secure fit, it features a black lacing system. The upper also incorporates Nike Shox branding at the top of the tongue and breathable mesh detailing that extends to the lower toe cap. Adding to its style, tonal webbing contrasts with an embroidered Swoosh. A black Shox midsole that provides both necessary stability and comfort is what keeps the sneaker in place below. For improved traction and grip on a variety of surfaces, the outsole is fashioned with a patterned tread. In an all-black hue, the Nike Shox TL Triple Black is the pinnacle of a classic and adaptable sneaker.

name: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 'Oatmeal'
text_content: Few Vomero 5 models were released in 2020. After the drop of this beige-coloured Nike Zoom Vomero 5 'Oatmeal' from 2022, the model appeared more and more often.  In 2011, the Vomero+ 5 was launched as a comfortable running sneaker that you could connect to your IPod. After a long period of a world without Vomero, the model made its debut as a lifestyle sneaker in 2018, and since 2022 the model has become more popular.  The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 'Oatmeal' colour palette includes shades of Oatmeal, Pale Ivory, Sail and Light Chocolate. The base of the sneaker consists of mesh and the overlays are leather and some kind of plastic. The Zoom contains different patterns such as stripes and checks. Finally, parts of the outsole are coloured light blue.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Shadow 'Pistachio Frost'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Shadow 'Pistachio Frost' features a smooth all green upper with an enticing mix of materials. The sneaker dressed in 'Pistachio Frost' suede base, features smooth leather overlays in a calming beige-green hue. The collar is constructed with tumbled leather in 'Mint' green matching the white Swoosh's shadow. The thick midsole of the sneaker matches in colour the overlays, inner lining and lacing system giving unity to the design. The outsole of the silhouette comes in a third hue of green featured in the design while matching the shadow 'AIR' logo on the back of the shoe.

name: Nike Air Max 1 Corduroy 'Baltic Blue'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 Corduroy 'Baltic Blue' incorporates the iconic design of Air Max 1 in an all-corduroy upper. The vibrating colorway features 'Baltic Blue' all throughout the upper with the 'Sesame-Sail' Swoosh which matches the colour of the tongue tag. The navy inner, outsole and airbag diversify the colour palette while the Sail rubber midsole completes the design.

name: Nike ZoomX Vaporfly NEXT% 2
text_content: Designed for long-distance running and racing, the Nike ZoomX Vaporfly NEXT% 2 is a high-performance running shoe. A lightweight and breathable mesh upper in bright orange tones is used for the upper. A durable and grippy outsole gives the Nike ZoomX Vaporfly NEXT% 2 optimum traction. Rubber pods are strategically placed in high-wear areas to improve grip and durability. With an updated midsole design in shades of light orange with a gradient from red to yellow in the front, the Nike ZoomX Vaporfly NEXT% 2 features a range of innovative sole technologies that boost running performance.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'Black/Chlorophyll'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 'Black/Chlorophyll' (DQ4071-005) is predominantly black, with bright green 'Chlorophyll' accents on the outsole and branding elements. It's the shoe for everyone, offering a perfect blend of fashion, comfort, and a proven track record. The low-top design with a padded collar provides a sleek appearance and a soft, comfortable feel, while the rubber waffle sole maintains a traditional look with traction and durability. Stitched overlays and TPU accents ensure lasting durability, comfort, and that beloved '90s aesthetic. The Nike Air Max 90 is the epitome of a classic with a modern twist.

name: Nike Dunk Low GS 'Pink Velvet'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low GS 'Pink Velvet' has a fresh colorway and combines different shades of pink. The Dunk Low has become a very popular model with many people in recent years. The Dunk Low was introduced in 1985 and has kept its retro look ever since. The 'Pink Velvet' was released in 2021 and was dropped in GS sizes.The sneaker has a white leather upper. The Swoosh and mudguard are light pink. The Swoosh has a shiny finish and gives the sneaker a chic colour. The heel tab has a velvet look. On this tab the Nike logo is put in red.

name: Nike P-6000 WMNS 'White Gold Red'
text_content: From the P-6000 series comes the Nike P-6000 WMNS 'White Gold Red' in an athletic aesthetic. With a design inspired by the early 2000s tracksuits, the shoe features a mix of white mesh, grey metallic overlays and a red Swoosh with golden outlay. The cushioned sock line together with the foam midsole offers the ultimate comfort while the rubber outsole provides durability.

name: Nike Lunar Force 1 Duckboot 'Black'
text_content: This Nike Lunar Force 1 Duckboot 'Black' offers a sleek, robust look, crafted from a strong blend of rubber and synthetic materials. Originally released in 2017, this silhouette combines high-fashion streetwear aesthetics with innovative design to create superior comfort, durability, and style.The shoe boasts an all-black colorway, enhancing its durability and style. With two signature Swooshes and a pull tab at the tongue and heel, the design is further enhanced. Nike Lunar sports shoes are distinguished by their diamond-like toe box pattern, which adds a unique textural element. The shoe is more than a sneaker - it's a statement piece that alters conventional footwear.

name: Nike Air Max 1 WMNS 'Fuchsia Dream'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 WMNS 'Fuchsia Dream' (DZ2628-001) is a vibrant colorway for the Air Max 1. The OG colour blocking has been selected for this colorway. The sneaker is therefore very similar to the OG release from 1987. The sole comes in white with a grey Air bubble. The overlays come in pink like the Swoosh. The Nike Air logo can be found on the heel in pink and the top of the heel is in shiny grey.

name: Nike P-6000 WMNS 'Black Volt'
text_content: From the P-6000 range comes the Nike P-6000 WMNS 'Black Volt' in an athletic aesthetic. With a design inspired by the tracksuits of the early 2000s, the shoe has a near-black look. A mix of black mesh, grey overlays and a black Swoosh with gold outlay. The cushioned sockliner, together with the foam midsole, offers ultimate comfort, while the rubber outsole ensures durability.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Hemp' - Next Nature
text_content: Stylish and environmentally friendly, the Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Hemp' - Next Nature is a standout piece of footwear. The design, which draws its inspiration from hemp, features a special fusion of earthy browns and beige that give it a rustic and natural look. The upper is made of a robust fabric that resembles hemp while 'Sail' overlays smoothly complement the base. The shoe is an adaptable option for daily wear thanks to its low-top silhouette and comfortable fit, which includes a padded collar and cushioned insole.  In addition to making a statement with its design, the Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Hemp' - Next Nature sneaker also demonstrates a dedication to environmentally friendly fashion.

name: Nike Air Max 1 '87 WMNS 'Coconut Milk'
text_content: 2022 can be described as the year of the Nike Air Max 1, multiple collabs and great regular releases. The new Nike Air Max 1 87 WMNS 'Coconut Milk' (FD9856-100) features a clean colorway consisting of Coconut Milk, Alabaster, Saturn Gold and White.

name: Nike Dunk Low Premium 'Light Orewood Brown'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low Premium 'Light Orewood Brown' sneaker, a stylish and versatile iteration of the iconic Nike Dunk silhouette, is now available. This sneaker combines traditional design elements with a contemporary twist thanks to its gentle and neutral colour scheme. The premium leather upper and stylish overlays demonstrate sturdiness and sophistication. The low-top silhouette provides unrestricted movement and is designed for both fashion and comfort. The rubber outsole offers the best traction, while the cushioned midsole guarantees excellent support and impact absorption. The Nike Dunk Low Premium 'Light Orewood Brown' will add to your sneaker collection. With each step, enter a world of style and comfort by embracing its versatility.

name: Nike Air Max Plus 'Blue Gradient'
text_content: A new icy rendition of Nike's Air Max Plus silhouette will hold fans over until the Nike Air Max Plus 'Hyper Blue' arrives in Spring 2024. Blue tones are used throughout the blue gradient mesh upper of the new Air Max Plus 'Blue Gradient'. A black accent can be found on the plastic toe cap, inner lining, and laces, while anthracite leather covers the mudguards and heels. In addition to the gradient finish throughout the upper, the shoe retains its signature wavy TPU overlays. The Swoosh branding is highlighted in metallic silver, while the "TN" branding appears on the heels and underfoot. A black rubber outsole completes the design, providing a stylish and well-rounded aesthetic. With new colorways for the technical Air Max Plus, Nike continues to provide fans with exciting options.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 'Tiffany'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 '07 'Tiffany' (DR0155-100) has a tough look. The Air Force 1 was introduced in 1982 and was the first sneaker to bring Air technology to the midsole. Bruce Kilgore was the brains behind the iconic model and now, some forty years after its first release, the model has become a true classic. The sneaker has an off-white upper. The blue details give the pair a playful twist and colour nicely with the upper. A striking detail is the black midsole. On this, AIR is put in light blue, which contrasts nicely. The Swoosh is black and has a cut-out look.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Court Purple'
text_content: Since 2018, the Nike Dunk has became more and more popular again. In 2021, this popularity reached a high point. Many sneakerheads called this year, the year of the Dunk. The popularity of the silhouette continued after the year of the Dunk. In 2022 Nike released the famous 'Court Purple' colorway on the Dunk Low. The two-tone colour scheme was previously spotted on the Air Jordan 1 and Dunk High. The upper of this Dunk is made of leather. The toebox, side panel and collar are in white. The laces of this pair are white as well. The overlays on the upper have a recognizable purple colour. The lining, Swoosh, heeltab and outsole also feature the same colour. On the heel tab is the Nike branding in white.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Shadow 'Metallic Copper'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Shadow 'Metallic Copper' has a striking design. The model takes its inspiration from the classic Air Force 1. The Shadow adds different elements to the silhouette and comes with double overlays on the middle panel. The model also features a raised midsole. The upper of the sneaker is coloured off-white. The overlays have colours mint green and copper. On the heel, the Nike logo is placed. This one also has two elements. The Air logo on the midsole runs over the upper and gives the sneaker a unique look.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Chicago Split'
text_content: Nike brand makes an addition to their series of Nike Dunk Low with a color palette in University Red/ Black- LT/ White/ Sail inspired by Chicago Bulls. The Nike Dunk Low 'Chicago Split' features a white leather base and red overlays which set the foundation for the split Swoosh in black and sail. The 'Sail' mesh tongue and midsole offer design unity which is wrapped with a split outsole in black, white and sail. If you fell in love with the previous 'Chicago' models, Nike SB Dunk Low J-Pack 'Chicago' and Nike Dunk Low EMB 'Chicago Bulls' - NBA 75th Anniversary then this one is a 'Must Have It'!

name: Nike Air Max 90 Gore-Tex 'Anthracite'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 Gore-Tex 'Anthracite' is suitable for autumn due to both the colour composition and the use of Gore-Tex materials. Nike Air Max 90 has a leather upper in the colour 'Anthracite', which is overlaid with 'Midnight Navy' and dark grey accents. Contrast is provided by the "Pure Platinum" Swoosh, tongue and horizontally ribbed panels. The white midsole adds contrast to the dusky colourway. The GORE-TEX logo can be found on the tongue and TPU panel on the side of the shoe, which is rounded off with a rubber sole and the signature Air unit.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Clear Jade'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low 'Clear Jade' has an elegant colour and is super for Spring and Summer. The sneaker has a white base with 'Clear Jade' overlays. The 'Clear Jade' is reflected on the outsole, Swoosh and Nike logo. The name of this colorway comes from the jade gemstone which possesses cleansing and protective powers. It also provides harmony, balance, happiness and prosperity too. Maybe you can restore your Chi with this sneaker!

name: Travis Scott x Nike Air Trainer 1 SP 'Grey Haze'
text_content: It's clear that Nike and Travis Scott are easy to get along with. They have had several collaborations on the Air Jordan 1, as well as the Air Max 1. When the Air Max 1 came out in collaboration with Cactus Jack, they also released two colorways of the Air Trainer 1. The Travis Scott x Nike Air Trainer 1 SP 'Grey Haze' (DR7515-001) features a light colour scheme and is ideal for summer. The upper is mainly made of a corduroy material. There are various details around the upper. For example, there is a zip on the heel with branding underneath. We also see a lot of small press studs. When you buy this shoe, there is an extra layer that can be attached above the upper.

name: Nike Cortez WMNS 'Athletic Department'
text_content: The Nike Cortez 'Athletic Department' is the newest model in Nike's college-themed retro collection, and it perfectly combines old charm and modern design. The first Cortez in the series is covered in plush Pale Ivory suede, and the entire line embodies classic design elements and vibrant colour accents. It features striking 'Deep Royal Blue' accents on the Swoosh, heel overlay, tongue, insole branding, and heel wedge. To complete the design, the classic gum rubber outsole, a hallmark feature of heritage footwear aesthetics, adds the finishing touch.

name: Nike Dunk Low Retro Premium 'Oil Green'
text_content: With the Nike Dunk Low Retro Premium 'Oil Green', you'll experience the perfect blend of style and craftsmanship in an all-green colorway. This iconic sneaker showcases a smooth 'Olive Green' upper with a canvas base and leather overlays for a visually striking aesthetic. An additional branding element includes a woven tongue tag and an embroidered Nike logo, and the signature Swoosh in light green adds contrast while sticking to the green design. The Nike Dunk Low Retro Premium 'Oil Green' makes a statement with its timeless elegance.

name: Nike Air Max 95 LX WMNS 'Reflective Safari'
Nike Air Max 90 SE Next Nature
UNDEFEATED x Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Multi-Patent'
Nike Air Max 1 '86 OG Golf NRG 'Play To Live'
text_content: Nike has expanded its golf category to appeal to the younger demographic in the world of golf. One of their most enduring icons, the Air Max 1, has made its way onto the golf course with bold colorways. This upcoming Nike Air Max 1 Golf release is one of the most anticipated releases of the year. The Swoosh is chiseled with the message ‘Play To Live’ and the opposite side features ‘Live To Play’. Its construction combines white mesh and gray suede with neutral and vibrant elements. It is the art-covered mudguard, which features a psychedelic design, that makes the bike stand out. The white midsole and multicolored outsole balance the pattern and complete the design. In this Air Max 1 Golf edition, Nike brings a unique and vibrant aesthetic to the golf course.

name: Nike Air Max 90 SE 'Snakeskin Swoosh'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 'Snakeskin Swoosh' integrates multiple textures in an appealing design. The 'Pale Ivory' mesh base features two tones of brown suede overlays which set the perfect foundation for the snakeskin-looking-like Swoosh that is predominately brown with black details. The design is nicely complemented by the 'Picante Red' red details on the tongue tag, air bubble and the tip of the outsole. The midsole comes in white while the outsole features the same brown tones as found on the upper giving unity to the entire design.

name: Nike Air Max 90 Futura WMNS 'Cow Print'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 Futura WMNS 'Cow Print' sneaker is a striking footwear alternative that fuses classic style with a lighthearted twist.Its distinctive cow print pattern distinguishes it from other sneakers and gives it a unique and humorous appeal. The contrast is enhanced and made more visually appealing by the use of the black-and-white colour scheme. This sneaker combines elegance and comfort with fine materials and the recognizable Air Max cushioning in the heel. The Nike branding, which includes the renowned Swoosh logo, lends the design a familiar feel. The Nike Air Max 90 Futura WMNS 'Cow Print' is a striking option for people looking to stand out and express their own style.

name: SoulGoods x Nike Dunk High 'Military Green'
Nike Air Max 90 WMNS 'Pastel Leopard'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 WMNS 'Pastel Leopard', also known as the Nike Air Max 90 Easter Leopard, is a striking and trendy colorway of the classic Nike Air Max 90 model. Inspired by nature, this version features a playful design with a leopard print in pastel colours, creating a unique and stylish look. The upper of the 'Pastel Leopard' is made of a combination of white mesh, and suede overlays in different pastel colours. Jade green suede covers the toe cap and part of the centre panel, while the Swooshes on both sides of the sneaker have a sky blue hue. However, the most striking detail is the baby pink suede leopard print in the lower half of the trainer, which provides a unique finish. The colour combination of the 'Pastel Leopard' ensures that this colorway goes well with different outfits, from casual to trendy. It is a great choice for ladies looking for a fashionable and eye-catching sneaker to complement their style.

name: Nike ACG Mountain Fly 2 Low Gore-Tex 'Dark Grey'
text_content: The Nike ACG Mountain Fly 2 Low Gore-Tex 'Dark Grey' (HF6245-002) is the ultimate fusion of style and functionality for outdoor enthusiasts. In the striking 'Dark Grey/Light Grey/Orange' colourway, these sneakers are designed to conquer any terrain with confidence.Crafted with precision, the sneaker boasts a rugged Gore-Tex upper that ensures waterproof protection, keeping your feet dry and comfortable in challenging conditions. The combination of dark and light grey tones, complemented by vibrant orange accents on the laces, not only adds a pop of energy to the design but also enhances visibility on the trail.

name: Nike Air Max 1 Crepe WMNS 'Light Bone'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 Crepe 'Light Bone' has a unique design. Normally the upper of the AM1 features mesh, but with the 'Light Bone', the mesh has been replaced with premium leather, creating a striking and unique look.The upper of the 'Light Bone' colorway is made of premium leather in a light bone colour. An eye-catching detail is that the light blue mudguards are made up of different patches of canvas, giving extra character to the design. What makes this colorway truly unique is the crepe sole. Instead of the traditional rubber sole normally found on the Air Max 1, the 'Light Bone' has a crepe sole. The Nike Air Max 1 Crepe 'Light Bone' is a versatile colorway that is both comfortable and stylish. The use of premium leather and the special crepe sole give the sneaker a distinctive look, making it appealing to sneaker lovers looking for something new.

name: Nike Air Max 97 'Gold Bullet'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 97 ‘Gold Bullet’ (DM0028-700) was originally released in 1999, and last seen in 2018. The 2022 version also applies gold throughout its upper, from the laces to the leather overlays to the mesh base. The lining, pull tab and outsole add contrast in black, while the white midsole delivers a clean finish to the colorway. Small hints of red can also be seen on the miniature Swooshes and detailing on the tread.

name: Nike Air Max 1 '86 OG Golf 'Obsidian'
text_content: Among the Nike Air Max 1 lineup is the '86 OG Obsidian colorway, which is perfect for golf. There is a clean combination of ‘Obsidian’, white, and red colors, as well as typical Air Max 1 materials like mesh and suede. Swoosh and mudguard are covered in obsidian suede, while the toe box, tongue, and collar are made of white mesh. Suede vamps and midfoot panels feature cream-colored accents, while Nike tongue tags and TPU eyelets feature red accents. The insoles of the shoes are adorned with white Nike Golf logos, indicating that they are golf-ready. An obsidian and red spike-less rubber outsole accompanies the white midsole featuring the four-pillar Air unit from the original Air Max 1.

name: Nike Dunk Low SE 'Hangul Day'
text_content: In honour of Hangul Day, the Nike Dunk Low SE 'Hangul Day' is a special edition sneaker celebrating the Korean alphabet and South Korean culture. With a unique and eye-catching design, this shoe celebrates the Korean alphabet. A tonal look is achieved with the upper, which comes in an array of 'Light Orewood Brown' and 'Sail'. White elements throughout the sneaker including the Swoosh add to the pleasing aesthetic of the design. The standout feature is the decorative Hangul script embroidered on the heel tab, tongue tag and insole, adding cultural significance. The design is completed by a 'Gum Light Brown' outsole and 'Sail' laces. With its classic Dunk silhouette and comfortable cushioning, the Nike Dunk Low SE 'Hangul Day' is not only a stylish addition to your sneaker collection but also a symbol of cultural appreciation.

name: Nike Air Max 95 'Hyper Turquoise'
text_content: Nike Air Max 95 'Hyper Turquoise' the shoe's upper consists mainly of mesh netting accented in white. The overlays are accented in different shades of grey to match the nose of the Air Max 95. Notable details include the lace eyelets and the small Swoosh on the heel and tongue, which all come in the 'Hyper Turquoise' colour. The shoe is supported by a black midsole with a turquoise Air unit and rounded off with a black rubber sole, featuring the Nike logo.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 WMNS 'White Python'
text_content: The material and finish of the Air Force 1 'White Python' (DX2678-100) create a luxurious look. The base of this Nike Air Force 1 comes entirely in white tumbled leather. The tongue is made of mesh. Most striking about the sneaker are the python overlays, which add dimension to the pair. A grey lining and rubber outsole contrast with the base. The midsole has been given a Sail colour, completing the design.

name: Nike Air Penny 2 'Baroque Brown'
text_content: The Nike Air Penny 2 'Baroque Brown' has an autumnal look due to the colour combination Hemp, Baroque Brown, Sesame and Coconut Milk. The base of the shoe consists of leather in the colour 'Coconut Milk' with overlays in the dark brown colour 'Baroque Brown'. Cream shades have also been used for the tongue and midsole, which adopts a wavy shape. The Nike Air Penny 2 is rounded off with a signature Air unit, supported by a rubber sole in 'Coconut Milk' colour.

name: Off-White x Nike Air Force 1 Mid 'Pine Green'
text_content: The Off-White x Nike Air Force 1 Mid 'Pine Green' is part of a 2022 collab between Nike and world-renowned streetwear brand Off-White, set up by the beloved Virgil Abloh. The sneaker comes with an all-green leather upper with white details. On the heel of the left shoe you can see a white stitching of a candlestick, on the right heel you will find a stitching with the text 'OFF', this hints at the collaboration with Abloh's brand. An additional lacing system can be seen on the midfoot of the shoes, which you may recognise from previous collaborations between Nike and Off-White. The pair is finished off with a wavy midsole with an orange-coloured Air unit. What's most eye-catching about the Off-White x Nike Air Force 1 Mid 'Pine Green', is the spiky outsole, which provides extra grip and gives the sneaker a unique look.

name: Nike Dunk Low LX WMNS 'Light Smoke Grey'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low LX WMNS 'Light Smoke Grey' combines classic design with a modern twist with its captivating colorway that exudes refined elegance.A 'Light Smoke Grey' canvas base constructs the sneaker base while accessorized with smooth suede grey overlays. The Nike Swoosh, rendered in a contrasting white tone, adds versatility and sophistication to the design. The padded collar and cushioned insole ensure exceptional comfort for everyday wear.With its timeless design and premium craftsmanship, the Nike Dunk Low LX WMNS 'Light Smoke Grey' effortlessly transitions from casual to sporty outfits.

name: Nike Air Max 97 'Silver Bullet'
text_content: The Air Max 97's upper is inspired by water droplets falling into water. The waves that run across the sneakers represent the ripples created by the impact of water droplets. Nike has given the 'Silver Bullet' a silver mesh sole. Additionally, silver and white leather outline the muguards. Above is a wavy overlay made of 3M material, which is reflective. A red mini Swoosh is placed on the tongue and the middle panel. Underneath the white midsole is an Air unit that runs throughout the sole. A black outsole with white and red details completes the sporty design.The sneaker also comes in WMNS and GS sizing.

name: Nike Air Max 90 Jewel 'White'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 Jewel 'White' has a sporty silhouette. The Air Max 90, as the name implies, was released in 1990 and was the younger brother of the famous Air Max 1, which was introduced in 1987. The Air Max 90 features a larger Air Unit compared to its predecessor and has a chunky look. The sneaker has a white colorway. The upper is made of mesh and the overlays are made of leather. The Swoosh is placed on the middle panel. The Swoosh has been given the 'Jewel' makeover and is blue in colour. The Jewel Swoosh is slightly smaller than the traditional Swoosh and has a shiny finish. Blue details also appear on the heel and tongue.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 'Georgetown'
text_content: With a low-top design and a clean and timeless aesthetic, the Nike Air Force 1 '07 'Georgetown' is a perfect match for any outfit. It features a sleek profile with a round toe and a lace-up closure. The Nike Air Force 1 '07 incorporates Nike's Air cushioning technology in the midsole, providing lightweight, responsive cushioning for a comfortable fit. In addition to a prominent grey outline around the upper and a white leather underneath, this new colorway also features a deep navy blue heel and Nike's swoosh, which references Georgetown University's colours.

name: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 WMNS 'Plum Eclipse'
text_content: Nike arrives with a new colourway of the iconic Zoom Vomero 5 model, inspired by the “dad shoe” silhouette. The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 WMNS 'Plum Eclipse' (FV1166-200) comes dressed in a women’s exclusive colourway dominated by dark ‘Plum Eclipse’ shades.  The breathable dark purple mesh base is complimented by the suede overlays in the lighter ‘Pink Oxford’ colour, creating texture and depth to the design. The Black profile Swooshes contribute to the moody aesthetic of the shoe.  In terms of comfort, the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 is equipped with a cushioned midsole featuring the innovative Cushion and Zoom Air technology, paired with a durable rubber outsole for additional grip.

name: Nike Dunk Low Retro PRM 'Deep Jungle'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low Retro PRM 'Deep Jungle' (FB8896-300) brings a fresh and vibrant aesthetic to the iconic Dunk Low silhouette. This sneaker showcases a unique 'Deep Jungle/White/Light Silver' colourway, combining rich green hues with crisp white and light grey accents for a visually striking design. The upper features a premium textured leather base and ‘Deep Jungle’ green overlays, ensuring both durability and style. The sleek design is complemented by the classic Dunk details, including the perforated toe box and padded collar. Cushioned midsole and rubber outsole provide exceptional comfort and durable traction, making the sneaker suitable for all-day wear. With its distinctive colour combination and timeless silhouette, the Nike Dunk Low Retro PRM 'Deep Jungle' stands out as a stylish choice for sneaker enthusiasts.

name: Nike Dunk Low LX WMNS 'Black Suede'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low LX WMNS ‘Black Suede’ is a sleek and stylish sneaker that combines classic design with modern materials. A black and cream colorway makes for a bold and versatile upper made of premium leather. This shoe has a low-cut silhouette for a comfortable fit and easy movement, while the black outsole provides great traction. Last but not least, it has multicolor laces and silver embroidered branding. You can dress it up or down to suit any occasion with this sneaker.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Mini Swoosh'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low 'Mini Swoosh' sneaker, is a stylish and iconic shoe that combines classic design with a unique twist. This shoe features a low-top silhouette and the key focus, a tiny Swoosh logo close to the toe box that adds some flair to the classic Dunk look.Premium smooth and tumbled leather is used in the construction of the Nike Dunk Low 'Mini Swoosh' which provides a secure fit and long-lasting comfort. While the contrasting 'Bright Mandarin' Mini Swoosh adds a pop of visual interest, the traditional black and white colorway allows for versatile styling. This shoe provides all-day comfort and support for your feet thanks to its padded collar and cushioned insole.Step into a world of timeless style and unquestionable street aesthetic with each step by embracing the iconic Nike Dunk Low 'Mini Swoosh'.

name: Nike Air More Uptempo '96 GS 'Cobalt Bliss'
Nike Air Max Plus 3 Air Max Month
Nike ACG Mountain Fly 2 Low 'Summit White'
text_content: The debut of the Nike Acg Mountain Fly 2 series brings to the public four enticing colorways in an outdoorsy style. The second generation of Nike ACG Mountain Fly features a series of enhancements fit to increase your performance and comfort while unfolding your favourite outdoor activities. The Nike ACG Mountain Fly 2 Low 'Summit White' features a two-toned design complemented by smooth black and orange details. The breathable white mesh upper ensures the ventilation of the foot and fast drying while the navy blue cushioning around the tongue and inner lining increase comfort. The branding on the lateral of the shoe features 'acg' writing in black, matching in colour the branded tongue and heel tags as well as the toggle lacing system designed for quick adjustment. Branding elements on the tags as well as the Swoosh come in contrasting 'Bright Mandarin' hue for a pop of colour in the design. For increased durability, the shoe features an extended toe cap and rubber sidewalls all around the upper in white, complementing the design. The lightweight foam midsole increases the comfort of the model while the mountain-biking-inspired outsole ensures traction on any surface. Enjoy nature in style with the Mountain Fly 2 collection in 'Neutral Olive' and 'Laser Orange'.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'From Nike To You'
text_content: Nike has taken the classic Dunk Low silhouette and given it an exciting and colourful twist with the Nike Dunk Low 'From Nike To You'. The sneaker combines timeless style with vibrant fall colours. With its striking mix of blue, cream, and yellow colours, this sneaker is sure to draw attention.With its beige upper base, the 'Midnight Navy' overlays create a smooth yet sophisticated aesthetic. The Swoosh depicted in 'Pale Vanilla' adds a bald statement to the design while nicely containing the deep blue overlays. Exceptional comfort and durability are ensured by the sail midsole, paired with a blue outsole to mirror de upper. Elevate your outfits with the Nike Dunk Low 'From Nike To You' and make a statement this season.

name: Nike WMNS Air Force 1 Sage 'Triple White'
text_content: The Nike WMNS Air Force 1 Sage 'Triple White' is an elegant and modern version of Nike's iconic Air Force 1 trainer. Designed specifically for women, this trainer has a sleek, minimalist look that perfectly matches any outfit.The upper of the trainer is made of high-quality leather and features an all-white colour, including the sole and laces. The Nike WMNS Air Force 1 Sage 'Triple White' has a raised sole, All in all, the Nike WMNS Air Force 1 Sage 'Triple White' is a beautiful trainer that is both stylish and functional and perfect for women looking for a modern twist on a classic design.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 'Black Accents'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 '07 'Black Accents' combines timeless style with modern sophistication in this black and white colorway.With a sleek white upper and stylish black accents, this shoe exudes a versatile aesthetic. The iconic Nike Swoosh logo stands out with its black outline paired with branding elements and the outsole in the same hue.If you are a fan of the white AF-1 but want a twist to it the 'Black Accents' is the perfect one for you. Elevate your casual outfits with the Nike Air Force 1 '07 'Black Accents' and take advantage of the versatile white and black combination.

name: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 'Timeless'
text_content: The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 'Timeless' is a running shoe from the Nike Zoom series. This particular version is designed with an aesthetic that pays homage to the past while exuding timeless style.The standout feature of the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 'Timeless' is the use of materials and colour schemes that create a retro-inspired look. The trainer's upper is made of a combination of leather and mesh. The colourway consists of a white base with black overlays.In terms of technology, the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 'Timeless' offers the familiar cushioning and responsive features that the Zoom series is known for. Moreover, the trainer offers excellent support and stability thanks to its sturdy midsole.It is a versatile trainer suitable for daily workouts and casual use, and the 'Timeless' edition adds a touch of nostalgia and style to it all.

name: Nike Air Max 90 Essential
text_content: This 2022 Nike Air Max 90 Essential is a colourful edition of the well-known model. The sneaker's base is white-coloured mesh. Over this base are leather overlays that consist of an off-white colour. The details in this Air Max 90 give the sneaker a playful and colourful look. The Swoosh, branding on the tongue tag and branding on the heel tab colour light blue. The eyestays and Air Max letters on the side of the sneaker come in a bright yellow colour. A salmon pink colour can be seen around the air unit, which can also be seen in the tip of the outsole and the heeltab. Finally, the remaining parts of the outsole are coloured black.

name: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 'Light Bone'
text_content: Inspired by the “dad shoe” aesthetic, Nike arrives with a new colourway of the iconic Zoom Vomero 5 model. The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 ‘Light Bone’ (FV0397-001) is dressed in ‘Light Bone’, ‘Medium Olive’ and ‘Neutral Olive’ colours making it an ideal choice for the Fall/Winter season 2023.  The mesh base in khaki tones is complimented by the suede and TPU overlays in ‘Light Bone’ hues, creating texture and depth to the design. Striking embellishments such as the tongue construction, laces, inner lining, insoles and profile Swooshes in ‘Medium Olive’ create a refreshing contrast. The ‘Neutral Olive’ quarter panel and second half of the midsole add a vibrant finish to the look. In terms of comfort, the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 is equipped with a cushioned midsole featuring the innovative Cushion and Zoom Air technology, paired with a durable rubber outsole for additional grip.

name: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 PRM 'Chocolate Teal'
text_content: The Nike Zoom Vomero 5 PRM 'Chocolate Teal' wears the right colours for both autumn and winter. The base consists of a combination of textile and suede in the colour brown, also called 'Chocolate Teal'. The side panel and laces come in shades of blue-green, while reflective details add to the look. A striking detail is located on the insole, namely a portrait of Bill Bowerman, inventor and co-founder of Nike. The shoe is finished with a brown midsole and a beige outsole for contrast.

name: Tom Sachs x NikeCraft General Purpose Shoe 'Field Brown'
text_content: The NikeCraft General Purpose Shoe was designed by Tom Sachs. The first colorway of the General Purpose Shoe was released in early June 2022. The model is designed for general purpose use. Therefore the silhouette of the sneaker is kept as simple as possible.  Nike has given the 'Brown', as the name suggests, a brown upper. The upper is made of mesh and the overlays are made of suede which gives the shoe a chic look. The NikeCraft General Purpose Shoe has a low fit. On the tongue and heel are pull tabs placed. This makes the sneaker easy to put on. The Swoosh on the middle panel and the midsole have been given a burgundy colour. As a final detail, the outsole has a waffle pattern in black which provides extra grip.

name: Nike Dunk High WMNS 'Blue Tint'
text_content: The Nike Dunk High WMNS 'Blue Tint' is a stylish and versatile sneaker with a captivating colour scheme.This iconic shoe features a 'Blue Tint' hue that exudes a cool and refreshing vibe, making it a perfect choice for any casual or streetwear ensemble. Creating an eye-catching design, the soothing blue tone dominates the base while 'Light Smoke Grey' covers the overlays, lacing system and Swoosh. With the Nike Dunk High WMNS 'Blue Tint', you can enjoy comfort and style on a daily basis. The high-top silhouette provides ankle support, while the premium construction ensures durability. This sneaker delivers the perfect blend of fashion and functionality, whether you're strolling through the city or expressing your individuality.For effortless and captivating fashion, let the Dunk High 'Blue Tint' be your go-to shoe from the street to social gatherings.

name: Nike Air Max 90 Re-Craft 'Wolf Grey'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 Re-Craft 'Wolf Grey' is light grey from head to toe. The Air Max 90 was introduced in 1990 and has a sporty silhouette. The sneaker combines the materials mesh and leather. The nose and collar are made of mesh and let the 'Wolf Grey' breathe. On the middle panel, the Swoosh is placed. This comes in the same colour grey as the upper. The sneaker is with its all-grey colorway that's easy to style.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Team Gold'
text_content: A timeless and adaptable colorway makes the Nike Dunk Low 'Team Gold' ideal for any sneaker rotation.  The striking 'Team Gold' and white upper is made of a combination of hard-wearing leather and plush suede. The golden Swoosh on the sides creates gives unity to the design, while the rubber outsole offers superior durability and traction. In addition, the toe box and quarter panels have perforations, and the collar is padded for comfort. The Nike Dunk Low 'Team Gold' is a must-have addition to any sneaker collection and is ideal for sneaker enthusiasts and collectors alike.

name: Nike Lunar Force 1 Duckboot
text_content: The Nike Lunar Force 1 Duckboot is the appropriate shoe for cold weather. The shoe features water-repellent leather and a rugged outsole, which provides plenty of grip. The Lunar Force 1 Duckboot has rubber toe cap with small studs, which overflows into side panels of brown leather. The Swoosh also features brown leather. A striking detail is the metal lace hardware combined with the oversized tongue. The white midsole provides contrast and of course the necessary cushioning, this is supported with a grip fixed outsole.

name: Tom Sachs x Nike General Purpose Shoe WMNS 'Archive'
text_content: As a sequel to Tom Sachs’ impeccably designed NikeCraft General Purpose Shoe, the Tom Sachs x Nike General Purpose Shoe WMNS ‘Archive’ is styled in a similar way, featuring a mix of durable materials on the upper and suede reinforcements around the toe, heel, and tongue. The sneaker’s golden tone is complimented by the vibrant orange pull-tabs, light tan tongue and laces, and toned-down orange midsole. A white Swoosh cuts cleanly through the design, and a black rubber outsole rounds off the look.

name: Nike Air Max 1 '87 WMNS 'Pale Ivory'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 '87 WMNS 'Pale Ivory' is a classic and adaptable sneaker in a tonal colour scheme.The sneaker is constructed with a breathable white mesh base and 'Pale Ivory' suede overlays around the lacing system and medial and heel. The smooth ivory hue is nicely complemented by the suede 'Sandrift' mudguard for enriched durability. The eye-catching dark hue colours the Swoosh and branding elements. Satin material around the collar offers elegance while the 'Sail' midsole complements the overall design. With its patented Air Max cushioning, the shoe offers plush cushioning and responsive support, ensuring all-day comfort. The Nike Air Max 1 '87 WMNS 'Pale Ivory' is an everyday shoe with style and comfort thanks to its meticulous attention to detail.

name: Nike Dunk Low GS 'Reflective Grey'
text_content: Specifically tailored to small-footers, the Nike Dunk Low GS 'Reflective Grey' (FV0374-100) impresses with a fashion-forward design and construction.  The predominantly white leather upper is artfully paired with mesh tongues and collars, while 'Smoke Grey' smooth leather overlays, tongue labels, soft inner lining, and heel accents introduce a captivating contrast and dimension to the overall aesthetic. The inclusion of speckled laces is a subtle yet stylish touch, but the true star of the show is the 3M reflective side Swooshes. They not only catch the eye but also ensure you make a statement, especially in low-light conditions. Completing the design with finesse is a white midsole and a 'Gum Light Brown' rubber outsole, providing both support and reliable grip.
colorway: White/Light Iron Ore/Gum Light Brown/Smoke Grey

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Hemp Coconut Milk'
text_content: Featuring hemp-coloured suede overlays and a coconut milk-coloured nubuck vamp and heel tab, this Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Hemp Coconut Milk' combines texture and style in a captivating sneaker. Its harmonious blend of neutral tones is complemented by hemp-colored suede overlays. Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, the contrasting textures create a stylish and sophisticated look. Its timeless appeal has made the Air Force 1 Low a staple of sneaker culture for decades. With the Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Hemp Coconut Milk', you can add a touch of style to your everyday outfit. Elevate your sneaker game with a classic silhouette that seamlessly blends fashion and function.

name: Nike Air Max 1 'The Bay' - US Exclusive
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 'The Bay' will enhance your shoe collection. This shoe, inspired by the picturesque San Francisco Bay Area landscapes, combines iconic style with unmatched comfort.For a luxurious appearance and feel, the upper uses a special combination of high-end materials, in a soft white hue for a clean look. Nike's iconic Swoosh dressed the medial of the sneaker embroidered in the shape of a feather creating an eye-catching feature. This shoe offers superior impact protection and cushioning thanks to the visible Air Max unit in the heel. The Nike Air Max 1 'The Bay' will keep you feeling and looking good whether you're exploring the city streets or going on outdoor adventures.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX CN 'Gold Swooshes'
text_content: Nike is using understated elegance to highlight its enduring influence on upscale streetwear. These specific pairs appear to be adorned in a variety of ways, not just in terms of quality or price. The addition of colourful jewels down the tongue is the most notable example. These limited edition Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX CN 'Gold Swooshes' sneakers feature extra gold mini swooshes on an all-white palette. The metallic gold eyestay details complement the swoosh details perfectly, creating a stylish and symbolic design. Nike invites you to lace up these sneakers and evoque simple elegance and luxury in this celebration of art and culture.

name: Nike Air More Uptempo 'White'
text_content: Nike has several Air Max models. The Air Max 1 started the revolution and was followed by the Air Max 90. Not much later, the brand released the Nike Air More Uptempo for the first time. This model is very rugged and definitely an eye-catcher.The upper of the sneaker is made of leather and completely in white. On the side is 'AIR' in big letters. The letters have a black outline. The Air Unit runs underneath the entire sneaker.

name: UNDERCOVER x Nike Air Force 1 Low 'White'
NOCTA x Nike Hot Step Air Terra Snakeskin 'Light Bone'
text_content: The NOCTA x Nike Hot Step Air Terra Snakeskin 'Light Bone' is a crazy collaboration between NOCTA, Drake's clothing brand, and Nike. This special edition of the Air Terra trainer combines functionality with a contemporary design and a unique snakeskin print.The upper of the NOCTA x Nike Hot Step Air Terra Snakeskin 'Light Bone' is made of high-quality leather. The trainer has a striking 'Light Bone' colour, which gives it a neutral and versatile look. What really sets this edition apart is the addition of a snakeskin print on the entire upper. This snake print adds a touch of texture and visual interest to the design.The NOCTA x Nike Hot Step Air Terra Snakeskin 'Light Bone' is designed with an emphasis on functionality and performance. The trainer features Nike Air cushioning in the heel, providing responsive cushioning and comfortable wear. The rubber outsole with a robust profile provides excellent grip and traction, making the trainer suitable for different terrains and conditions.As a collaboration between NOCTA and Nike, the NOCTA x Nike Hot Step Air Terra Snakeskin 'Light Bone' exudes unique style and exclusivity. It combines elements of streetwear and sporty functionality, making it a versatile trainer suitable for both casual outfits and sporting activities. With its striking snakeskin print and subtle colour palette, this trainer is the perfect choice for trainer lovers looking for a unique and contemporary style.

name: Nike Air Max 90 Futura Lunar New Year (W)
Nike Dunk Low SE WMNS 'Just Do it'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low SE WMNS 'Just Do It' is a sneaker with a lot of cool detailing. The applied colours give the shoe a premium look, with a 'Sale-Muslin' base overlayed by canvas in 'Team Red' and accompanied by a Swoosh and laces in the same vibrant colour. This mix of colours not only gives the shoe a premium look, but also elegance. The heel of sneaker features the year 2023 in roman numerals with the iconic Nike slogan "Just Do It". To complete the look, the shoe has an off-white midsole and gold dubraes.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Valentine's Day'
text_content: In 2023 Nike celebrates love with couples from around the world through the release of Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Valentine's Day'. The silhouette comes in a sail, red and pink colorway. The 'Sail' leather base and midsole set the foundation of the colourful accents. The red Swoosh has a soft pink outline, matching the heart-shaped cherries hanging from its tail. The two small heart cutouts on the medial quarter follow the 'love' themed design, together with the heel tab branding which is embroidered on heart-shaped leather, and the dot above the 'I' in 'AIR' which was replaced by a heart on the midsole. The pink sock line and lace lock match the mini Swoosh found on the belly, offering a touch of 'sweetness' to the overall design.

name: Nike Air Max Plus 3 'Black Aqua'
text_content: In 2019, Nike re-released the Air Max Plus 3, a cult classic and staple of Nike's Tuned Air lineup. Sean McDowell's early 2000s design has recently undergone some somber changes. The forefoot Tuned Air logo and heel counter are both highlighted in brilliant white in the ‘Black Aqua’ colorway.This shoe's midsole, mudguard, heel, collar overlay, and tongue are all black. The sock lining and laces carry on the theme. Aqua and teal gradients contrast with the black background on the mesh top, and they also adorn the tongue and heel logo. Because of its mix of dark and bright components, the Air Max Plus 3 is a striking and summer-ready option.

name: Nike Air Max 97 SE 'Muslin'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 97 SE 'Muslin' (DQ8996-200) has a retro colorway and combines different shades of beige and brown. The sneaker was released in 2022. In this year, the model celebrated its 25th anniversary and the release of the 'Muslin' was not entirely unexpected. The combination of the earth tones with the dynamic overlays makes it a unique design. The Nike Air Max 97 SE 'Muslin' has a beige upper. The upper is made of mesh, which makes it a sporty sneaker. The overlays have a wavy design and run throughout the entire design. The Air Unit runs through the entire midsole, which gives the shoe a modern look. The gum sole completes the look.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Crater Flyknit Next Nature
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Crater Flyknit Next Nature is part of the Move To Nature project from Nike. This means that the sneaker is produced with durability in mind and that recycled materials are used. The upper of the classic silhouette is made of Flyknit which gives the model its sporty look. The sneaker is coloured black with red. The upper is decorated with different patterns. The Swoosh is black and is placed in the upper, instead of being stitched on like the traditional Swooshes. The midsole is white with a speckled look. The sole is made with durable Nike Grind. This material is made with leftover scraps from the Nike factory. In short: a good sneaker for the environment and for your closet.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Cracked Orange'
text_content: A striking and vibrant sneaker, the Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Cracked Orange' features a striking colour scheme that fuses vibrant shades of orange with a touch of boldness.Different textures are present on the premium leather upper of the silhouette. The 'Light Bone' tumbled leather base creates a smooth background for the cracked suede in the vibrant 'Cracked Orange' covering the rest of the upper. The outsole reflects the upper in the same beige and orange hues, aligning with the two-tone design.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8 Winterized 'Phantom'
text_content: The Air Force 1 ‘07 LV8, a classic shoe cherished for over 40 years, is undergoing a winterized transformation for the upcoming season, called the ‘Phantom’ edition.It boasts a bone-like upper and midsole, with Cargo Khaki accents, providing a striking contrast. Elements like a shell-like toe box and ripstop mid-panels offer warmth and water resistance. The design includes thematic laces and speckled midsoles, blending style with functionality for urban and outdoor settings.This 40-year-old shoe embodies tradition, innovation, and inclusivity, making it suitable for individuals of all ages, genders, and backgrounds in any season or setting.

name: Nike Dunk Low LX WMNS 'Pink Foam'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low LX WMNS 'Pink Foam' is a women's low-top sneaker featuring a pink foam upper and a white midsole. On a 'Sail' base, the pink overlays incorporate the iconic Nike Dunk silhouette with modern materials. The rubber outsole offers durability and grip, while the cushioned insole ensures comfort with every step. The Nike branding on the heel and tongue adds a touch of athletic style, making this sneaker a versatile and stylish addition to any wardrobe.

name: Nike Air Max 90 Gore-Tex 'Anthracite'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 Gore-Tex 'Anthracite' comes in "Black" and "Anthracite" colours, which come together with shades of "Honeydew" and "Mica Green". The construction of the Air Max 90 seems traditional, but includes water-resistant features on the TPU window. In addition, leather overlays have been used instead of the suede panels used in the original design.

name: Nike Air Max Plus 'Spider-Man'
text_content: While Jordan Brand has already crafted a collaborative Air Jordan 1 for the film, Nike has yet to join in the celebration. But the Nike Air Max Plus changes that, paying homage to the suits worn by the film's heroes. In contrast to the Air Jordan 1 collaboration, this Nike Air Max Plus omits the multiverse-inspired elements. Instead, the shoe presents a grounded design that evokes images of both Miles Morales and Miguel O'Hara, the 2099 iteration. Drawing inspiration from their suits, the shoe features a predominantly black base colour, while accents of red and blue are applied to the upper and shank. The Nike Air Max Plus tribute to Spider-Man offers a stylish tribute to the beloved characters, appealing to both fans and sneaker enthusiasts.

name: Nike P-6000 PRM 'Triple Black'
text_content: The Nike P-6000 PRM 'Triple Black' is the definition of sleek and stealthy style. A throwback design with references to both Nike Pegasus 25 and Nike Pegasus 2006, it is a perfect blend of classic aesthetics with modern comfort. Crafted from premium materials, this sneaker offers durability and luxury with every step. The all-black colorway exudes sophistication and versatility, making it a perfect choice for any occasion. A cushioned midsole provides exceptional support and comfort, while the iconic Swoosh logo adds a sporty touch. This Nike P-6000 PRM 'Triple Black' sneaker will elevate your sneaker game to the next level, whether you're walking the streets or running errands.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Red Panda'
text_content: A stylish and distinctive sneaker, the Nike Dunk Low 'Red Panda' combines terrycloth, sultry suede, and smooth leather for a visually stunning aesthetic.In a calming colour palette of brown, cream, and orange, with contrasting accents that add depth, the silhouette is set to stand out. Its 'Velvet Brown' fairy suede foundation is complemented by 'Sanddrift' smooth suede overlays. Hairy suede in stunning 'Rugged Orange' complements the back overlays, tongue tag and heel tab. The upper is adorned with branding elements in contrasting red. Take your sneaker game to the next level with the Nike Dunk Low 'Red Panda'.

name: Nike Air Max 1 '87 WMNS 'Ale Brown'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 is the favourite model of the Netherlands. Despite the fact that the sneaker was introduced in 1987, it remains a modern favourite.There were several special releases of the model such as the Concepts collabs and the 'Cobblestone' colorway. The Nike Air Max 1 '87 NBHD 'Ale Brown' comes in a brown colorway with the colours 'Ale Brown' & 'Gum Med Brown'.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Smoke Grey'
text_content: A must-have sneaker for all sneaker enthusiasts and fashion-conscious individuals, the Nike Dunk Low 'Smoke Grey' effortlessly combines stylish design with versatile wearability.Constructed with a smooth white leather base, the 'Smoke Grey' overlays add to the sneaker's minimalist and sophisticated look. Grey branding elements smoothly blend into the design while the white midsole supports the silhouette. 'Gum' rubber outsole disrupts the two-tone of the upper, adding a street-wear touch to the sneaker. Nike Dunk Low 'Smoke Grey' is designed to keep up with your active lifestyle, whether you're hitting the streets or adding a sporty touch to your casual wardrobe.

name: Nike Dunk Low SE WMNS 'Just Do It' - Iridescent
text_content: Whether on the court or on the street, Nike Dunk Low SE 'Just Do It' reminds you to push boundaries and to achieve what you want. Reminiscing the iconic 'Panda' colorway, the sneaker features a white and black colour scheme. Its white leather base is complemented by the black Shoowsh, heel tab and lacing system. Patent leather with a black base and multi-colour tint adds to the dynamic and bold statement of the design. Embrace the power of 'Just Do It' with these stylish and inspiring sneakers, designed with a classic silhouette and bold design.

name: Nike Air Max 90 SE 'Moving Company'
text_content: This Air Max 90 is part of a Nike's 'Moving Company' Pack. Like its predecessors, the sneaker features many eye-catching details. The Nike Air Max 90 SE 'Moving Company' comes in a Sail-coloured base with matching canvas overlays. The mudguards colour dark grey with conch stitching on top. It also uses various light brown and green details. The sneaker comes with special tongue label with the letters Nike and a green snail.

name: Nike Dunk High '85 'Green Denim'
text_content: The Nike Dunk High 85 ‘Green Denim’ (DV1143-300) places sage green denim overlays over a plush white leather base, adding to the look with a creamy midsole and finishing off with a green outsole. Contrasting dark green stitching and light green lining adds another dimension to the look.

name: Nike Air Max 95 Anatomy Of Air 'Spine'
Nike Air Force 1 'White' - Carabiner Pack
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 from the 'Carbiner Pack' has got a striking look. Especially the Swoosh, which draws all the attention to itself. The Swoosh is equipped with a so-called carabiner. The carabiner is often used in climbing. This striking detail also lends its name to the pack. This pack also contains another Nike Air Force 1 in a different colour version.Besides the striking Swoosh, this Nike Air Force 1 'Carbiner Pack' comes in a colour mix of white, black and red. The base is predominantly white and the tongue, insole, underlying Swoosh heel are done in black. The tongue label and carabiner are in red. The lace dubrae's have an orange metallic finish. The nice thing about this Nike Air Force 1 is that you can give the sneaker two different looks. You can also detach the carabiner from the shoe. One pair, two different looks! But that is not all, because this Nike Air Force 1 'Carbiner Pack' has a second unique detail. That is the zippered pocket in the tongue of both sneakers. Good for storing something small.

name: Nike Air Force 1 LV8 GS 'Black Phantom'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Low introduces another variation in the form of the 'Split' model, featuring a versatile colour scheme of 'Black/Light Silver-Phantom-White.' This low-top sneaker boasts a premium construction with a tumbled leather upper in Phantom and smooth black leather overlays. The distinctive split theme is evident on the tongue labels, heels, insoles, and rubber outsole. Complementing the design are white Swooshes and a matching midsole, providing a balanced and visually appealing profile.

name: Foot Locker x Nike Air Max Plus 'Marseille'
text_content: The Foot Locker x Nike Air Max Plus 'Marseille' sneaker is a collaborative creation that honors the Olympique de Marseille football club. Rooted in the heart of this French club's legacy is the iconic Stade Velodrome stadium, known to evoke intense emotions among football enthusiasts. The sneaker's elegant reflection of the club's traditional colors of white and blue, which correspond to the uniforms worn by players on the field, pays homage to this heritage. Fine details, such as TPU finishes around the lace holes and white and blue accents, are used to decorate the sneaker's upper. Drawing inspiration from the stadium's architecture, the base of the sneaker showcases a distinctive grid pattern. Notably, the tongue boasts a label showcasing the club crest and the inscription "Marseille Resplendit Par Ses Hauts Faits" (Marseille shines through its greatness), a phrase that reveres the club's remarkable achievements. Standing on a white midsole, the sneaker incorporates blue-tinted Air units at the front and contrasting yellow ones at the heel.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'Black Volt'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 'Black Volt' creates a compelling design with its contrasting, sleek and vibrant elements. The sneaker's black mesh base provides breathability while the suede overlays ensure durability. Grey rubber details enhance the aesthetic while the vibrant 'Volt' accents add energy to the black backdrop. A black sole complements the 'Volt' design paired with the visible Air Bubble. The Nike Air Max 90 'Black Volt' captures the essence of contrast and individuality.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Panda' - Next Nature
text_content: The most popular dunk of 2021 was called the Nike Dunk low 'Panda', this sneaker is basically the same except for some small details. Nike has given this Dunk a more environmentally conscious look. The difference is not visible but it is there, this 'Next Nature' version is made of more recycled materials and therefore better for the environment. Not only do you look good in this Nike Dunk Low 'Panda' Next Nature but you are also helping the environment.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'Sequoia'
text_content: In the Nike Air Max 90 'Sequoia', the upper is made of synthetic leather, mesh, and breathable textiles. Air Max 90 'Sequoia' colorway features a dominant green hue inspired by sequoia trees. Nature-inspired and earthy, these shoes have an upper made of dark green or olive. Midsoles and outsoles are accented with complementary colors, such as black and white.This sneaker does keep the signature design elements that make the Air Max 90 silhouette recognizable, like rubber eyestays, a visible Air unit in the heel, and the Nike Swoosh.

name: Nike Air Force 1 'Since 82'
text_content: Nike celebrates the beloved ‘Triple White’ with an anniversary release, the Nike Air Force 1 ‘Since 82’ (DJ3911-100). With a fully white colorway, the sneaker bears a close resemblance to the original, but the branding has been tweaked. An “Anniversary Edition” mark has been added to the tongue label, and the heel tab features a Swooshless “NIKE AIR”. The sneaker is also packed with its own toothbrush, marked with “Since 1982” in a nod to the AF1’s debut year.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'Flat Pewter Obsidian'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 'Flat Pewter Obsidian' is a stylish and trendy version of the popular Air Max 90 trainer. The trainer is made of a mix of materials and features a combination of different colours that provide retro appeal.The upper of the trainer is made of leather, suede and mesh in 'Flat Pewter' and 'Obsidian' colours. The platinum grey colour of the 'Flat Pewter' gives the trainer a subtle look, while the 'Obsidian' colour provides a striking and generous look. The Nike Swoosh logo on the side of the trainer is also made of mesh and has an off-white colour.The Nike Air Max 90 'Flat Pewter Obsidian' is a perfect trainer for those looking for a stylish and comfortable trainer that can be worn in a variety of situations and activities.

name: Nike Zoom Mercurial Vapor 15 Elite FG Blast Pack Baltic Blue
Nike Air Structure Triax 91 'Persian Violet'
text_content: The Nike Air Structure Triax 91 ‘Persian Violet’ (DC2548-100) is a padded sneaker designed to combat over-pronation when running. The breathable mesh base is overlaid with geometric panels in the titular Persian Violet colour, with black details including the leather Swoosh, eyestays and along the waffle-tread rubber outsole adding a stark contrast. Hints of red are also seen in the design on the tongue, heel, insole, eyestays and midsole, and a light grey midsole tones down the arrangement.

name: Off-White x Nike Air Force 1 Mid 'White'
text_content: Off-White and Nike have had a lot of collaborations. They started with 'The Ten' in 2017 and have now released dozens of sneakers together. In 2022, the two will release an Air Force 1 Mid. Just like the previous pairs, this one is also a real eye-catcher. This Nike Air Force 1 Mid is made with textile on the upper. The velcro strap on the top of the shoe is dark green. Across the upper are extra loops through which an extra lace can be threaded. Another striking element on this pair is the Air Unit. The Air Unit on this AF-1 is visible. Finally, the outsole. The front part of the outsole is coloured in blue, pink and black with rubber spikes. The rear part is grey.

name: Nike Air Footscape Woven 'Cow'
text_content: Based on Tory Orzeck's Air Footscape and Air Woven silhouettes created in 1996, it is a hybrid of the two. The upper features a woven stripe and sail accents, which highlight the shoe's signature asymmetrical lacing system. Throughout the tongue, heels, and midsole, branding there is a mix of tonal colors. A white midsole features debossed Nike branding, while a black outsole completes the look. This new "Cow Print" Air Footscape Woven is poised to make a statement for the upcoming autumn season. It is also available in the 'Black' colorway.

name: Nike Air Max Plus WMNS 'University Blue'
text_content: The Nike Air Max Plus WMNS 'University Blue' is a women's sneaker that combines style and performance. With its vibrant University Blue colorway, it instantly catches the eye. The shoe features a mix of synthetic and mesh materials on the upper, providing breathability and durability. The TPU overlays, known as "fingers," add a distinct design element but also offer support and structure. The standout feature of this shoe is the Air Max cushioning technology. This shoe has visible Air units in the midsole that deliver excellent impact absorption and a comfortable ride. With the iconic Nike Swoosh on the sides and the embroidered 'Tn' logo on the heel, this sneaker showcases the Nike branding we all love.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Athletic Department - Deep Jungle'
Nike Air Max 90 NRG 'Ridgerock'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 NRG 'Ridgerock' has a striking look and combines different Winter colours. The upper is turquoise and made of mesh. The overlays on the middle panel are brown and made of rough suede. The colours deep purple and yellow also make their appearance on the silhouette.The heel of the sneaker features the Nike Air emblem, which is coloured in ochre yellow. The midsole is off-white and gives the shoe a retro look. In short; the 'Ridgerock' is the perfect sneaker for anyone who is looking for a striking pair.

name: Nike Air Zoom Vomero 5 'Worn Blue'
text_content: Known for its cushioning, responsiveness, and support, the Nike Air Zoom Vomero 5 is a popular running shoe model from Nike. The shoe is designed to provide stability during runs. For sport enthusiasts, these include a supportive midfoot cage that enhances stability and a molded external heel counter.White mesh and blue synthetic materials make up the upper of the Nike Air Zoom Vomero 5 'Worn Blue', complemented by leather overlays in different shades of blue. A white swoosh with a blue border completes this new colorway.

name: Nike Air Humara QS 'Polar'
text_content: The Nike Air Humara 'Polar' comes in various shades of blue with a rugged black sole that makes the shoe suitable for winter. The base consists of light blue mesh with leather overlays in dark blue and black. The Swoosh comes in 'Buff Gold' as does the stitching on the mudguard and the logo on the tongue, heel and insole. The midsole is made of carbon fibre and has a checkered pattern in black and blue, it is rounded off with a rubber sole.

name: Nike Air Max 90 LTR GS 'Monarch'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 LTR GS 'Monarch' (CD6864-023) is a stylish and vibrant addition to the Air Max 90 lineup. Featuring a distinctive ‘Pure Platinum/Summit White/Monarch/Black’ colourway, this sneaker boasts a leather upper that combines durability with a premium aesthetic. A ‘Summit White’ leather base with ‘Pure Platinum’ overlays, and ‘Black’ accents on the Swooshes, mudguards, inner lining, tongue and heel branding, and part of the lacing system, create a striking contrast. The eye-catching 'Monarch' orange hue can be seen on the lacing system, on the TPU Air Max emblem on the mudguards, tongue and heel Nike branding, as well as on the midsole and parts of the outsole, creating a bold and energetic look. Contrasting black details on the Swoosh, laces, and heel, along with a white midsole, provide a balanced and fashionable contrast. The iconic Air Max cushioning in the midsole ensures comfort and support, making these sneakers ideal for all-day wear. With its attention to detail and a blend of bold colors, the Nike Air Max 90 LTR GS 'Monarch' stands out as a distinctive choice for sneaker enthusiasts.

name: Nike Dunk Low GS 'Deep Jungle'
text_content: The newest version of the Nike Dunk Low, designed for preschoolers, has been revealed. This design features monochromatic overlays on a smooth leather foundation, showcasing a simple and adaptable aesthetic. The iconic Swoosh is made of leather, adhering to traditional styles. A perforated toe box improves breathability, and the extreme cushioning in the midsole guarantees young wearers' comfort throughout the day, which is why is also offered in TD sizing. The woven branding adds a subtle detail and the rubber outsole offers durability and traction. The classic and cosy fit of the cotton laces adds to the allure of this Nike Dunk Low for young children.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Forest Green' - Color of the Month
text_content: A new release featuring green Swooshes makes its way into Nike's "Color of The Month" series. A White/Forest Green-Gum Yellow color combination is available for the Nike Air Force 1 Low. Featuring a white leather upper with tonal detailing on the tongues, laces, inner liner, and midsole, the shoe showcases a white leather construction throughout.A ‘Forest Green’ accent can be found on the Swooshes, insoles, tongue tags, heel tabs, toes, and midsole. An outsole made of Gum Yellow rubber completes the design. In a fresh take on the iconic Air Force 1, these sneakers combine classic style with unique color accents.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Gorge Green'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Gorge Green' features a cold colour palette in green and blue hues. The women's exclusive has a 'Phantom' leather base and 'George Green' overlays. The design of the sneaker is nicely accessorised by the 'Midnight Navy' Swoosh on the lateral. Branding elements on the tongue tag in green and heel tab in navy depict the Nike logo. To complete the design the shoe features green laces, 'Phantom' midsole and 'George Green' outsole. This versatile silhouette can easily be integrated into any seasonal outfit.

name: Nike Air Max 90 Jewel 'Black'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 Jewel 'Black' is one for those who want to stand out. The sneaker has a black upper and combines red details. The Air Max 90, as the name suggests, was released in 1990 shortly after the famous Air Max 1 (1987). Unlike its predecessor, the AM90 features a larger Air Unit which gives the silhouette a chunky look.The upper of the sneaker is made of mesh with leather overlays. On the middle panel is the Swoosh. The Jewel Swoosh is smaller than the traditional Swoosh and has a shiny look. The Air Unit is coloured red, as are the details on the tongue and heel.

name: Nike ACG Mountain Fly Low GORE-TEX 'Hazel Rush'
Nike Air Max 1 '86 OG WMNS 'University Red'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 '86 OG WMNS 'University Red' mostly known by sneakerheads by the 'Big Bubble' nickname brings back to the public the original design that made Nike the iconic brand that is today. The revolutionary design of Tinker Hatfield took over the footwear industry in a way nobody could have predicted. With an architectural background, Hatfield designed the sneaker with a visible air bubble, which was highly criticized as it was considered too innovative and eccentric. Luckily, Nike believed in innovative thinking and from there on the rest is history.The '86 OG silhouette features a white mesh base with grey suede overlays around the lacing system and heel. The guard is constructed with intense 'University Red' suede together with the Swoosh. The branding elements on the heel tab and tongue tag also come written in the same red hue as well as the insole and upper eyestays. A white midsole supports the upper while the outsole is constructed of a mix of white red and black patches. The element that makes this shoe truly authentic is the enlarged air bubble which at the time was a manufacturing mistake, thus the newer models feature a significantly smaller one.The colorway also comes in mens and GS Sizing.

name: Nike Dunk High SE 'Baroque Brown'
text_content: Nike is embracing the autumn season with a range of brown-based sneakers, including the Dunk High ‘Baroque Brown’, which stands out as a noteworthy addition.The Dunk High SE ‘Baroque Brown’ offers a blend of neutral tones, with brown and sail white taking center stage in its design. These colours create a distinct autumn-ready style. Additional design elements include red accents on the inner lining, Swoosh outline, and heel pull tab, providing the finishing touches to this autumnal-themed shoe. Gold-pigmented Nike labels on the tongue and a basketball logo on the sock liner pay homage to the shoe's basketball heritage. Completing the design, the shoe includes a sail white midsole and a brown rubber outsole, creating a well-rounded and autumnal colourway.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'Black Bronzine'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 'Black Bronzine' is made from a mix of mesh, leather, ripstop and suede materials. The upper has a black base and with 'Bronzine' accents, while dark grey contrasts to highlight the Swoosh and parts of the midsole. The 'Bronzine' details recur on the tongue the in a gridded pattern and TRP panels. The shoe is rounded off with a rubber sole that features the signature Air Max unit.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Shadow 'Pearl White Citron Tint'
Nike Air Zoom Maxfly Track and field sprinting spikes
Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX Low 'Team Gold'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX Low 'Team Gold' sneaker combines traditional design and modern refinement.With a smooth sail leather base, the sneaker features 'Team Gold' tumbled leather overlays. The tonal combination is disrupted by the iconic Swoosh that accessories the sneaker in black tumbled leather mix that also constructs the branded heel tab. Sail laces accessories on the upper of the sneaker while black writing on the tongue tag offers continuity to the design. The bottom of the sneaker sticks to the colour scheme with a sail midsole paired with 'Team Gold' rubber outsole. The Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX Low 'Team Gold' is the perfect choice for making a fashionable statement, whether hitting the streets or boosting your casual ensembles.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Anthracite'
text_content: Featuring a sophisticated colorway, the Nike Dunk Low 'Anthracite' sports a sleek and stealthy look. In a low-top silhouette, the colorway combines 'Anthracite', 'Pure Platinum' and 'Cool Grey' hues. Featuring a 'Cool Grey' base, the 'Anthracite' overlays offer a glamorous touch. The 'Pure Titanium' silver hue of the Swoosh adds a bright element to the design. The design is nicely complemented by a deep blue semi-translucent outsole. Bring casual elegance to your outfits with the Nike Dunk Low 'Anthracite'.

name: Nike Air Max 90 SE WMNS 'Asia'
