text_content: With an off-white mesh upper, double red mini-swooshes, and a large Swoosh in green embroidered with the brand name 'NIKE' in a stylized font, the Nike Air Max 90 SE WMNS 'Asia' provides the most comfort and style. A white and black sole is topped with a bright green Air unit, encapsulated within a beige plastic panel. The sneaker is finished off with leather overlays and transparent lace supports.

name: Nike Air Max Dawn Black Safari Animal (W)
Nike P-6000 WMNS 'Sea Glass'
text_content: The Nike P-6000 shoe has a more traditional and sophisticated silhouette that is similar to the running fashion from the 2000s. An engraved Swoosh with horizontal and vertical borders surrounds the shoe's top, adding unique details to its eye-catching design. The "Sea Glass" colorway has an off-white upper with black accents on the inside padding, the swoosh, the outsole, and the midsole corner. For ladies looking for a stylish and comfy sneaker option, the Nike P-6000 is a noteworthy option due to its distinctive blend of retro style and contemporary comfort.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'White' - Lucky Charms
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 'White' - Lucky Charms is a chic sneaker. The name 'Lucky Charms' alludes to the charms attached to the collar. It is not the first time Nike has attached these charms to a sneaker. The Air Force 1 and Blazer Mid also have a 'Lucky Charms' variant. The Nike Air Max 90 'White' has a white colorway. The upper is made of leather and the collar has a velvet feel. This gives the sneaker its luxurious look. The charms on the middle panel are gold and come in different shapes. A Swoosh, a shoe box and the year 1990 are attached to the model. The year 1990 refers to the year when the Nike Air Max 90 was first released. The Nike Air Max 90 'White' - Lucky Charms combines the materials mesh and leather on the upper. On the middle panel is the Swoosh and on the heel is the Nike Air logo.

name: Nike Air Ship SP 'Tech Grey'
text_content: The Nike Air Ship SP 'Tech Grey' is a brand new colourway reminiscent of the original 1985 Air Jordan 1 High OG 'Neutral Grey'. This version is dressed in a colour scheme of Summit White, Gunsmoke and Tech Grey.The Jordan Air Ship 'Tech Grey' has an upper of Summit White leather with a perforated toe cap for breathability, nylon tongues and Tech Grey suede Swooshes and heels. Gunsmoke brand labels on the tongue, an interior with Gunsmoke lining, 'Nike Air' embroidery on the heels and a rubber outsole atop a white midsole complete the sleek design.This new colourway version of the Jordan Air Ship combines a classic silhouette with contemporary details, making it an attractive choice for trainer lovers. With subtle colours and high-quality materials, the Air Ship SP 'Tech Grey' pays homage to Jordan Brand's past while offering a fresh and modern look.

name: Nike Air Max 90 Leather Triple Black (2020)
Nike Air Max 97 WMNS 'Obsidian'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 97 WMNS 'Obsidian' (DR9774-400) boasts a captivating colourway in 'Obsidian/Gorge Green-Midnight/Navy-Sail.' This blend of shades creates a unique appearance for the sneaker. The upper showcases a rich 'Obsidian'/‘Midnight Navy’ hues, accentuated by touches of 'Gorge Green' on the mini side Swoosh and on the tongue Swoosh branding, as well as 'Sail' on the outsole. These colours come together to offer a unique and eye-catching design. Crafted with a combination of high-quality mesh and synthetic materials, the shoe provides both style and durability. The Air Unit midsole and reliable rubber outsole ensure comfortable wear and excellent traction, making the Nike Air Max 97 WMNS 'Obsidian' a fantastic choice for various occasions.

name: Nike Dunk High 'Laser Blue
text_content: Nike has released several colorways for the Nike Dunk High, including the Laser Blue. 'Laser Blue' is one of the OG colours of the brand which has been used as a detail on several Air Max 90. For this Dunk High it is the complete opposite. The colour can be found all over the shoe. 'Laser Blue' can be found on the swoosh, overlays, laces and stitching. The only thing that does not come in this colour is the base, which comes in white. This makes the blue pop more. Like many Dunk High's, this sneaker is also made of leather.

name: Nike Air Force 1 LX 'United in Victory Hemp'
Nike Air Max 90 'Reflective Swoosh'
text_content: Nike is introducing a new addition to its Air Max 90 lineup for the upcoming season with the ‘Black Reflective’ colourway. Geared towards the autumn season, this classic silhouette is crafted from a mix of materials, including mesh, tumbled leather, and smooth leather. The shoe features a sleek all-black upper, extending to the tongues, laces, eyelets, and rubber sole, giving it a minimalist appearance. Notably, the design incorporates reflective mudguards that reveal Swoosh logos on the lateral panel when exposed to light, adding a touch of uniqueness. To provide a striking contrast to the predominantly black design, vibrant red accents are used on the tongue labels, heels, insoles, and Air Max heel units.

name: Nike Air Max Plus 'Light Photography'
text_content: With its captivating colour scheme, the Nike Air Max Plus 'Light Photography' is a bold sneaker. Incorporating vibrant hues to create a dynamic and electrifying look, this iconic shoe features a red, yellow and orange mix.This design has a striking combination of vibrant colours on its upper and midsole, creating a sense of motion and energy. The black and white around the midsole, Swoosh, mudguards and lacing system complement the design while toning down the fiery colour mix. Its Air Max cushioning technology ensures both responsive and plush support making it perfect for long-lasting comfort on all your adventures.The Nike Air Max Plus 'Light Photography' will elevate your sneaker game with its iconic and vibrant design.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LX 'Command Force'
Nike ZoomX Vaporfly NEXT% 3 'White'
text_content: The Nike ZoomX Vaporfly NEXT% 3 (DV4129-100) is designed for ambitious and competitive people, sharing a passion for running and speed. From experts to beginners, this shoe is perfect for the chasers, the racers and the elevated pacers who aim to catch the uncatchable.  A full-length carbon fibre flyplate provides a stiff and propulsive feel. Nike’s iconic ZoomX foam unlocks more energy return than before, and gives you a bouncy, springy feel. The midsole bulges out by the heel intentionally as it reduces weight on the inside of the foot that ultimately gives a more stable ride. The premium Flyknit yarns and engineered zones in the forefoot take the performance of the Vaporfly to another level, ensuring supreme breathability, support, flexibility, and softness complimented with a cool design. The White, Smoke Grey and Particle Grey colourway creates a simple minimalistic aesthetic, making it extremely easy to incorporate it in your activewear wardrobe. Slip into the Nike ZoomX Vaporfly sneakers and let them carry you to new heights of achievement. Every step in these shoes is a leap toward your goals, a stride closer to greatness.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Indigo Haze'
text_content: Nike Dunk Lows have made a significant cultural impact, becoming highly sought-after sneakers among sneaker enthusiasts. As a result of its retro aesthetic and popularity in the skateboarding community, it has earned the status of an iconic product.Featuring a low-top design and a classic basketball-inspired silhouette, the Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Indigo Haze' is sure to turn heads. In contrast to the white upper, this shoe features purple overlays, laces, and outsole, as well as a pink swoosh for a versatile and fashionable look.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Cool Grey'
text_content: We introduceren de Nike Dunk Low WMNS in de stijlvolle kleurstelling 'Cool Grey' (FV1167-001), met een bovenwerk van grijs nubuckleer aangevuld met contrasterende accenten van leisteen nubuck. De sneakers hebben platte veters die door een geweven gebreide tong lopen, versierd met geborduurde Nike logodetails. Onder de voeten hebben ze een middenzool van gebroken wit schuim, bovenop een doorschijnende rubberen buitenzool. Deze combinatie van materialen en ontwerpelementen zorgt niet alleen voor een trendy look, maar ook voor comfort en ondersteuning voor je voeten. De Nike Dunk Low 'Cool Grey' is een veelzijdige keuze voor elke gelegenheid, of je je nu opdoft of casual houdt.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Have a Nike Day'
text_content: Nike brings back the 'Have A Nike Day' theme in a new form with this Air Force 1 Low. With a bold yet simple design, the Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Have a Nike Day' (DM0118-100) comes in a fresh white leather finish that is contrasted with a black Swoosh, a yellow heel tab and a 'Sunflower' motif with Nike smiley logo on the side of the sneaker. Finishing off the theme is 'Have A Nike Day' embroidered on the heel and 'From Beaverton With Love' label on the tongue. A perfect sneaker for the sunny days!

name: Nike Dunk Low Retro GS 'Panda'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low 'Panda' is a classic colorway that uses the familiar dunk colour blocking in black and white leather. A clean and simple look to style, it shouldn't be missed from any sneaker collection. This GS sneaker also comes in adult sizing, and as a WMNS exclusive.

name: Nike Air Max 95 'Track Red'
text_content: Featuring a vibrant 'Track Red' colour combination that commands attention with its bold and energizing appearance, the Nike Air Max 95 'Track Red' is a distinctive shoe. An elegant gradient from black to grey covers both the midsole and upper, giving this design a unique sense of movement and flair. The details throughout the sneaker depict Nike branding elements in a contrasting red hue. Designed to offer all-day comfort and style, the Nike Air Max 95 'Track Red' features Nike's patented Air Max cushioning technology for responsive support.The Nike Air Max 95 is a daring shoe that combines the seductive allure of the 'Track Red' colour combination with the beauty of its unique design.

name: Nike Terminator Low 'Liberté'
text_content: Introducing the Nike Terminator Low 'Liberté,' a shoe that fuses classic design with a dash of liberation. The distinctive design of this iconic silhouette was drawn from the spirit of liberty and independence. This sneaker's upper is expertly crafted from a blend of high-end leather and fabric materials. The 'Liberté' colorway has a soft and patriotic appearance thanks to its varied colour palette, which includes 'Phantom', 'Wolf Grey', and 'Coconut Milk'. It is a standout option for any sneaker enthusiast thanks to the iconic Nike branding and intricate details.But there's more to the Nike Terminator Low 'Liberté' than looks. Additionally, it features cushioned midsoles and sturdy rubber outsoles that offer all-day comfort and trustworthy traction. The Nike Terminator Low 'Liberté' is a stylish way to express your love for liberty.

name: Nike Air Max 90 WMNS 'Blissful Blue'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 WMNS 'Blissful Blue' is a women's sneaker with the classic Nike silhouette. It has become an iconic sneaker known for its visible Air Max cushioning and timeless design.Featuring a predominantly blue color scheme, the Nike Air Max 90 WMNS 'Blissful Blue' features a predominantly blue color scheme. Uppers are predominantly 'Blissful Blue', which is the major color. In addition, it has complementary accents and detailing in white and grey. The iconic Nike Swoosh logo can usually be found on the shoe sides.The visible Air Max unit in the heel is a notable feature of the Air Max 90. Additionally, the shoe has a padded collar and tongue to provide support and a secure fit. A grey outsole incorporates patterned rubber that enhances traction and complements the Air Max unit.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'University Blue' - Athletic Department
text_content: From the 'Athletic Department' Pack, the Nike Dunk Low 'University Blue' pays homage to college sports with its classic silhouette. The traditional leather upper features a white base with light grey overlays at the forefoot and heel, creating a clean and timeless look. Pastel blue accents adorn the signature Swoosh and back tab, complemented by an embroidered Nike wordmark in gold lettering. Additional branding details include a woven Nike tongue tag and 'Nike Athletic Dept.' insoles, adding to the thematic appeal. The vintage off-white midsole contributes to the retro aesthetic, while underfoot support is provided by the powder blue rubber outsole. This release combines classic elements with thoughtful detailing, making it a standout addition to the 'Athletic Department' collection.

name: Nike Air Max Plus 'Reverse Grape'
text_content: Nike Air Max Plus 'Reverse Grape' combines heritage, modernity, and urban sophistication. Featuring a striking 'Reverse Grape' colorway, the Nike Air Max Plus 'Reverse Grape' is a timeless silhouette that effortlessly blends nostalgia and contemporary style. It stands out in any setting because of its rich purple tones and subtle grey accents, giving it a unique visual appeal. A fashion and comfort staple, the Nike Air Max Plus 'Reverse Grape' is crafted with meticulous attention to detail and premium materials. Incorporating the signature Air Max cushioning and a bold colour combination these sneakers are a true statement piece. The colorway is also available in GS size.

name: Fat Joe x Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Terror Squad'
text_content: The highly sought-after Fat Joe x Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Terror Squad' sneaker collaboration highlights the distinctive style and influence of the legendary rapper Fat Joe. This sneaker stands out from the competition thanks to its premium design and striking construction. A distinctive combination of black and white blocking is used on the upper, which is made of premium leather and textile materials. The iconic Nike Swoosh is prominently displayed on the sides, and Fat Joe's 'Terror Squad' branding gives the shoe a unique flair. The cushioned midsole and sturdy rubber outsole of the Air Force 1 Low silhouette are known for their classic appeal and unbeatable comfort. The Fat Joe x Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Terror Squad' is an essential addition to your collection, whether you're a fan of Fat Joe or you just enjoy unique sneaker partnerships. By wearing these iconic and fashionable shoes, you can up your sneaker game and pay homage to the rap legend.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LX 'Mica Green'
text_content: Fresh and colourful, the Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LX 'Mica Green' is the ideal sneaker for spring and summer. Constructed with a pale colour palette, the premium leather and canvas used on the upper offer comfort and style. 'Photon Dust' canvas upper ensures the sneaker's breathability while the 'Mica Green' leather overlays increase the shoe's durability. 'Sail' tumbled leather Swoosh and branded heel tab adds to the style of the sneaker and its material mix. Branding elements on the tongue tag and heel depict the renowned Nike logo. The pale green tongue, laces and outsole nicely contrast the sail midsole of the sneaker, providing unity to the design. Its colour scheme is ideal for those looking for a vibrant and fun look that is still adaptable to a variety of outfits. The colorway also comes available in the Dunk Low design.

name: Nike Air More Uptempo 'Pink Foam'
text_content: The Nike Air More Uptempo was first released in 1996. Basketball player Scottie Pippen has made the silhouette a global icon. This pair comes with details that have meaning.  This Nike Air More Uptempo has an upper with a gridded gradient. Which comes paired with white leather overlays and a mesh tongue. Other details include the 3M outlines, which are reflective. Swooshes on the outsole come in pastel pink and blue. The shoe is accented with a special date, 5 December 1983, on the tongue and a Bible quote from Philippians 2:3 on the left insole. There is a signature on the right insole.

name: Nike ACG Air Moc 'Sail Black'
text_content: A functional and adaptable shoe that combines modern style and outdoor performance is the Nike ACG Air Moc 'Sail Black'. This shoe has a clean sail and black colorway in a lightweight, breathable upper made of a mix of textile and synthetic materials. The slip-on style makes it simple to put on and take off, making it ideal for everyday wear or outdoor activities. The durability and adaptability to different terrains are indicated by the ACG (All Conditions Gear) branding. The rubber outsole offers dependable traction on various surfaces, and the Phylon midsole offers lightweight cushioning. The Nike ACG Air Moc 'Sail Black' provides comfort, style, and functionality in a stylish package, whether you're exploring the trails or simply strolling around the city. The silhouette also comes available in the 'Moss' colorway.

name: Nike Air Max 95 QS 'Skeletal'
text_content: Besides the Nike Air Max 95 'Anatomy of Air', there is also the Nike Air Max 95 QS 'Skeletal' (DV2593-100) with unique details. This sneaker is clearly inspired by the human body.The shoe has a very calm composition and consists mainly of different shades of grey. Most shades are very light, but the grey nose is a bit darker than the rest of the sneaker. On the midsole is a very light print, this is a clear reference to bones. Under the sole you can find a small image of bones.

name: Nike Cortez PRM 'Black Sail'
text_content: Introducing a new set of colourways, the classic Nike Cortez is receiving an aged treatment, with the upcoming 'Black Sail' makeup among them. This iteration maintains its timeless, clean, and sleek aesthetic, ensuring it pairs well with a variety of outfits. The shoe features a primarily premium leather construction in black, sail, and alabaster tones. It incorporates both tumbled and smooth leather for visual interest, and comfort is enhanced through the use of mesh materials. Notably, sail accents adorn the Swooshes, heel tabs, and insole branding, while black elements are found on the base, tongues, inner lining, and heel branding. Sitting atop an alabaster sole, this Cortez achieves a vintage-inspired look.

name: Off-White x Nike Air Force 1 Mid 'Black'
text_content: The legacy of Virgil Abloh lives on in this futuristic Off-White x Nike Air Force 1 Mid 'Black' (DO6290-001) collab. This is in honour of the 40th anniversary of Nike's iconic Air Force 1 model. The Nike Air Force 1 Mid is constructed of predominantly black mesh with a wood grain pattern. The lacing system combines the traditional lacing design with a second futuristic set of laces that are connected with loops to the Flywire cables. The recognisable spikes on the outsole are in line with the ISPA philosophy: 'Improvise. Scavenge. Protect. Adapt'. Of course, the sneaker also features the very recognizable 'Orange' Off-White™️ tag and label on the Swooshes.

name: Billie Eilish x Nike Air Alpha Force 88 'Fire Red'
text_content: Nike has once again joined forces with singer-songwriter Billie Eilish, this has resulted in the unique Billie Eilish x Nike Air Alpha Force 88 'Fire Red'. This trainer brings together Billie Eilish's distinctive style with the iconic Air Alpha Force 88 silhouette in red and black colorways.The 'Fire Red' colourway features a white upper, with fiery and vibrant red accents. The trainer is made of high-quality leather for durability and comfort. The Air Alpha Force 88 is known for its retro-inspired design, which includes a sturdy midsole and a supportive collar. These features offer stability and a unique aesthetic that sets the trainer apart. To complete the trainer, co-branding can be found on the insole.The Billie Eilish x Nike Air Alpha Force 88 'Fire Red' is a statement trainer and versatile in its styling. This trainer pairs perfectly with sporty outfits for a dynamic look and more casual and trendy outfits for a fashionable statement. Embrace Billie Eilish's creativity and style with the Air Alpha Force 88 silhouette in 'White Black' and 'Fire Red'.

name: Nike WMNS Air Max 1 LX 'Guava Ice'
Nike Air Max 90 Leather Triple White (2020)
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 'Triple White' is an iconic model in the most wearable colorway, making the sneaker very popular. The Air Max always stays true to its roots with the iconic waffle pattern sole, stitched overlays and classic TPU accents. Fresh details provide a modern look and Air cushioning ensures comfort.

name: NIke Air Max 90 WMNS 'Citrus Pulse' - Chenille Swoosh Pack
text_content: In the Nike Air Max 90 'Citrus Pulse' colorway, Nike aims to deliver an eye-catching design and bright colors in a unique design. The two-tone sneaker in a clear white and yellow division is ideal for anyone looking to make a statement with their footwear. The upper of the shoe comes in total white, including the tongue and overlaps, with a bright yellow swoosh embossed in the midfoot. A gradient white-to-yellow midsole and yellow outsole complete the shoe.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Chocolate' - Color of the Month
Nike Air Force 1 '07
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 '07 (DR0155-002) has a cool look and combines blue details on a black upper. The Air Force 1 was introduced in 1982 as a basketball shoe and has become an iconic sneaker on and off the basketball court. This colorway of the Nike Air Force 1 '07 is black and has a leather upper. The midsole is dark grey and gives the trainer a tough twist. On the mudguard and midsole are blue details. These contrast nicely with the upper. The cut-out Swoosh on the mid-panel is dark grey and made of textile. The pull loop on the heel completes the sneaker.

name: Nike Wmns Dunk High 'Silver Glitter Swoosh'
Nike Shox TL 'Black Grey'
text_content: Featuring space-age aesthetics the Nike Shox TL 'Black Grey' styles a futuristic look. Its visually striking design is created by pairing a black nylon base with grey accents colouring the Swoosh and various details. The upper features a web-like pattern created by glossy taped overlays, adding to its originality.Among the most distinctive features of the Shox TLs are their pillared midsoles, which combine nostalgia with forward-looking innovation. Furthermore, the sneakers feature subtle embroidered branding to indicate Nike's identity, and their rubber outsoles ensure durability and traction.

name: Nike Air Max 97 'Off Noir'
text_content: In 1997, Nike was inspired by fast Japanese trains and created the Air Max 97 with the iconic wavy design, since then it has been a versatile sneaker that can be found in many colorways. From the bright ''to the quiet '', there is an Air Max 97 for everyone.And so the Nike Air Max 97 'Off-Noir' is there for people who are looking for a revolutionary and stylish sneaker. With a full black colorway this shoe gets a clean look, the all white sole and translucent air-unit offers a nice contrast. The logo on the tongue is also white and thus immediately stands out, however, the logo on the overlays is black to maintain the clean look.

name: Ambush x Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Black'
text_content: Following successful collaborations between the Tokyo fashion house AMBUSH and iconic sportswear Nike, the design of Air Force 1 Low takes over the fashion stage through its minimalist yet eye-catching detailing. The Ambush x Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Black' features an all-black premium leather upper with mid and outsole in the same hue. The sleek black background creates the perfect setting for the signature tailpipe Swoosh that comes in contrasting white. The sneaker features cobranded elements on the heel, tongue tag and leather insole. To complete the minimalist detailing, the shoe comes accessorised with an AF1 lace lock in white, matching the Swoosh and giving unity to the design. This collaboration is an absolute must-have not only because of the clean look but also the ease of styling the shoe in any outfit. The design of AF1 collab with AMBUSH also comes available in white, blue and green.

name: Nike Air Max 97 WMNS 'Chlorine Blue'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 97 WMNS ‘Chlorine Blue’ (DQ9131-001) celebrates the model’s 25th anniversary with the perfect colorway – the metallic silver mudguard and Chlorine Blue accents beautifully capture the spirit of the Japanese Bullet Train, the original inspiration for the AM97. Navy blue stripes and a white mudguard add nice contrasts at both end of the scale. Full-length cushioning and mesh panels in the upper add superb comfort and breathability to the sneaker. The sneaker is also available in Men’s sizing.

name: Nike Air Max Plus 'Pure Platinum'
text_content: There's nothing like the Nike Air Max Plus 'Pure Platinum', a sneaker that combines style, comfort, and undeniable appeal. The 'Pure Platinum' colorway provides a fresh and contemporary aesthetic. This sleek, clean shoe can easily transition from casual outings to athletic activities. With its white mesh upper and premium suede upper, this shoe adds texture and visual interest. Nike's iconic branding on the tongue and sides completes the look. Featuring the signature Air Max cushioning, this sneaker offers exceptional comfort and support with every step. Discover a perfect fusion of style and comfort with the Nike Air Max Plus 'Pure Platinum'.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Four Horsemen'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Four Horsemen' is a unique trainer honouring LeBron James' close circle of business partners and friends, including Maverick Carter, Ernie Ramos and Rich Paul. Previously made available only to a select group of friends and family members, these exclusive trainers are now being released publicly for the first time.The upcoming models are inspired by LeBron James' early career and are designed in St Vincent-St Mary High School colours. Made of high-quality leather, the trainer's upper features a modest white base with striking green Swooshes outlined in silver.Embroidered on the heel cap of the trainers are chess pieces with the number "4", symbolising James' inner circle. In addition, the initials "LR" and "MR" are engraved on the heel tabs, as a tribute to the friends involved. The trainers feature metallic silver and unique insole graphics.With the release of the Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Four Horsemen', trainer lovers and fans of LeBron James can be part of the story behind this special trainer and get their hands on a piece of the history of this legendary basketball player.

name: Serena Williams Design Crew x Nike Air Max 1 'Golden Yellow'
text_content: Tennis legend Serena Williams is collaborating with Nike to create a new version of the enduring Air Max 1. This dynamic collaboration appeals to streetwear fans by incorporating a vibrant color into the classic Air Max 1 design. In keeping with Nike's emphasis on the Air Max 1 model this year, the Serena Williams Design Team updated it. The sole is white with a small green swoosh on the toebox, and the upper is mostly orange with textures. Finally, the visible air unit on the heel is matched by the Swoosh. The Serena Williams collaboration gives a dynamic twist to the traditional sneaker, reflecting Nike's commitment to innovation.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Enamel Green' - Certified Fresh
Nike Air Max Furyosa ' Rattan'
text_content: After the success of the Air Max 1, Nike released a lot of different Air Max silhouettes. With the Air Max, the Air Unit is visible. The Air Max Furyosa even has two visible Air elements. The upper of the Air Max Furyosa 'Rattan' is very striking. The base of the upper is in white. The leather overlay is in beige and has a little overlap. The toe cap, heel tab and other overlays are in dark blue. Around the white upper is a yellow lace. The sole is also very unique. The upper is very rough, but so is the sole. It consists of two parts. The front part is completely white. The back part is divided in two, the lower part is white and the upper part is green. In both colours there is an Air Unit.

name: Billie Eilish x Nike Air Force 1 High ’07 SP
text_content: Singer Billie Eilish has taken on the iconic Air Force 1 High. For this Air Force 1 collab between Billie Eilish x Nike, Billie has remixed the classic by using eco-friendly materials on the model, among other things. The sneaker is constructed from recycled synthetic nubuck material that looks and feels super soft and comes in a 'Mushroom' colorway. The Nike Grind midsole perfectly matches the monotonous 'Mushroom' colourway upper. The sneaker is completely composed with durability in mind. The five chunky straps on top of the shoe represent Billie's signature oversized style. These straps are based on the strabs of the Air Trainer 3 and cover the laces, giving this unique sneaker a striking look.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Midnight Navy'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low 'Midnight Navy' sneaker combines a timeless design with an alluring deep blue colorway to create a stylish and functional footwear option. The upper's premium white leather base and 'Midnight Navy' overlays contribute to its simple, streamlined design. The 'University Blue' Swoosh adds a sophisticated touch to the ensemble. This sneaker offers a snug and comfortable fit for all-day wear with a lace-up closure, padded collar, and cushioned insole. Branding elements on the tongue tag in 'Midnight Navy' complement the upper while the gold writing on the heel tab creates an astonishing contrast. The sleek and robust design of the shoe is completed by the white midsole paired with a firm rubber dark blue outsole.The Nike Dunk Low 'Midnight Navy' is a stylish shoe that easily elevates both more informal and formal looks with a deep blue sense of refinement and elegance.

name: Nike Dunk Low Premium 'Sesame'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low Premium 'Sesame' pays homage to the culinary scene in Montreal. These sneakers pay tribute to the traditional bagel design with their university gold base, sand drift, and coated sesame seeds. The shoes' insoles are decorated with an image of a wood print. The Dunk Low Premium 'Sesame' blue swooshes and heel tabs counteract the dominant color scheme. Gum brown translucent outsole. This limited edition Dunk will be appreciated by sneakerheads and city people alike.

name: Nike Air Max Plus WMNS 'Mica Green'
Nike Dunk Low 'Celtics'
text_content: In the past few years, Nike has released many different colour and pattern options for the Dunk Low, making it a highly customizable shoe. Therefore, it is highly anticipated to see the Nike Dunk Low 'Celtics' released in 2023 as part of Nike's collaboration with the Boston Celtics. In keeping with the Boston Celtics team's colours, the Nike Dunk Low 'Celtics' upper features premium leather and suede materials and a classic green and white colour scheme. Also featured on the shoe are Celtics branding and a Nike Swoosh logo in black with Nike's letters embroidered in green on the tongue and pull tab.

name: Nike Air Max 90 Next Nature 'White Black'
Mimi Plange x Nike LeBron 20 Premium 'Ceremony'
Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8 'Split Light Silver'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8 'Split Light Silver' is a sneaker that fuses traditional design with modern accents. Its dominant colour scheme of 'Mint' draws attention and produces a stunning aesthetic.The upper's white leather base creates a smooth background for the pale green overlays. This sneaker's unique colour-blocking design, where the split Swoosh changes from mint green to black makes the sneaker truly distinctive. The contrast gives it depth and dimension.The sneaker features a functional lace-up closure, padded collar, and cushioned insole for maximum comfort and support. Durability and excellent traction are both guaranteed by the rubber outsole. Nike's attention to detail is demonstrated by discrete branding elements on the sides and the Nike Air branding on the tongue and heel tab.The versatile Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8 'Split Light Silver' adds a splash of colour and style to any look.

name: Nike Dunk High 'Psychic Purple'
text_content: The Nike Dunk High 'Psychic Purple' comes in a two-toned colour scheme ready to impress. On a black smooth leather base, the silhouette features intense purple leather overlays. The same 'Psychic Purple' is used in the construction of the Swoosh. With black interior cushioning, the purple sole is highlighted with the white Nike logo. The upper sits atop a white midsole which matches the branded tongue tag. The rubber outsole in purple completes the design together with the laces.

name: Nike Dunk Low 85 'Athletic Department'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low 85 'Athletic Department' is part of the classic Nike Dunk Low trainer model from the 1980s. This Dunk Low trainer has a vintage look and is made from high-quality materials. The upper is made of a white canvas base, providing a fresh and clean look. The grey suede overlays add texture and depth to the design, while the red leather Swooshes and heels offer a striking and contrasting colour.Another striking feature of this trainer is the aged yellow laces and midsoles, which create a vintage look and complete the design. The graphic insoles are also a nice detail and add a personal touch to the trainer.This trainer has a classic and timeless look and is suitable for everyday wear and casual occasions. Paying homage to Nike's rich history and the iconic Dunk Low trainer, the Nike Dunk Low 85 'Athletic Department' is a must-have for trainer lovers looking for a stylish and comfortable trainer with a retro look.

name: Nike Mac Attack QS SP 'Black and White'
text_content: In this sneaker, Nike seamlessly combines timeless style with modern design elements with the Mac Attack QS SP 'Black and White'. As part of Nike's Quickstrike collection, these sneakers showcase an elegant black-and-white colour scheme that oozes sophistication. The upper is crafted from premium materials, providing durability and comfort. The iconic Nike Swoosh logo is prominently displayed on the side, giving it a sporty feel. The shoe features a cushioned midsole that enhances comfort and support, making it ideal for athletic activities as well as everyday wear. The Nike Mac Attack QS SP 'Black and White' is sure to make a statement, whether you're on the streets or in the gym.

name: Nike Air Max CB 94 'Light Iron Ore'
text_content: With its eye-catching airbrushed detailing that skillfully combines orange, black, and gray tones throughout the upper, the Nike Air Max2 CB 94 ‘Light IRon Ore’ steals the show. The canvas of the upper is made of white bone leather, providing a clean backdrop for the striking design elements. Notably, overlays are skillfully created using black spray effects, which contrast sharply with the spotless base. This pair of sneakers features bootie sockliners, heel tabs, large eyelets with painstakingly woven laces, and other thoughtful design elements. A variety of branding components, such as mini Swooshes, Nike embroidery, rubberized tongue badges, Nike Air heel plates, and intricately printed insoles, elevate the shoe's aesthetic. Black air-assisted midsoles and contrasting rubber outsoles beautifully complete the design's harmonious ensemble, highlighting the meticulous attention to detail that distinguishes this iteration. In essence, the Nike Air Max2 CB 94 iteration represents an artistic fusion of hues, materials, and branding that was painstakingly planned out to produce a striking and cohesive whole.

name: Nike Air More Uptempo 'White Chrome'
text_content: The Nike Air More Uptempo 'White Chrome' is a stylish sneaker with a bold design and exceptional performance. With a sleek white leather upper and chrome accents, the silhouette is designed to give you the ultimate comfort. The iconic "AIR" branding on the side of the shoe adds signature style and pays homage to the '90s era of basketball. This athletic shoe features Nike's innovative Air-Sole technology, which provides cushioning and support for a comfortable and responsive ride. The semi-translucent rubber sole provides excellent traction and durability.  Whether you're a serious athlete or a casual sneaker enthusiast, the Nike Air More Uptempo 'White Chrome' is a must-have addition to your collection. Its sleek design, exceptional performance and iconic branding make it an outstanding choice for anyone looking to up their sneaker game.

name: Nike Air Max Plus 1 GS 'Black Bright Crimson'
Nike Air Force 1 Retro QS 'Chocolate'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Retro QS 'Chocolate' (FD7039-200) is a nostalgic and stylish reinterpretation of the iconic Air Force 1 silhouette. This sneaker showcases a rich ‘Chocolate/White Chocolate’ colourway, paying homage to the classic aesthetic. The upper features a chocolate brown hue, creating a timeless and versatile appearance. The premium leather used on the upper ensures durability and style. The ‘White Chocolate’ elements, including the side Swoosh, laces, tongue and heel branding, as well as the cushioned midsole add a clean and contrasting touch, enhancing the overall design. With its blend of heritage and contemporary elements, the Nike Air Force 1 Retro QS 'Chocolate' stands as a distinctive choice for sneaker enthusiasts.

name: Nike Air Max Plus 'Kiss My Airs'
Nike Air Force 1 Low Retro 'Pink' - Anniversary Edition
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Low Retro 'Pink' - Anniversary Edition is a special edition of the iconic Air Force 1 trainer in honour of the model's 40th anniversary. It features a white colour with striking pink accents and a retro-inspired design.The trainer's upper is made of premium leather in white colour and features a pink Swoosh logo on the side. The trainer's midsole is white and has pink lettering, while the gum midsole provides good grip and flexibility.The trainer features special details that reference the origins and history of the Nike Air Force 1. For example, a retro trainer box is included, reminiscent of the original boxes from the 80s and 90s. Also embroidered on the heel of the trainer is "NIKE AIR" in a classic font, reminiscent of the earliest Air Force 1 models. Another unique addition to the Anniversary Edition is a festive toothbrush. This toothbrush has the text "Since 1982" printed on it, highlighting the introduction of the Air Force 1 as a milestone in the history of Nike and trainers in general.Originally released in 1982 as a basketball trainer, the Nike Air Force 1 has since become a cultural icon and a versatile trainer suitable for all kinds of occasions. The pink colour of the Anniversary Edition gives the trainer a playful, feminine look and is a great addition to the collection of anyone who loves colour.Overall, the Nike Air Force 1 Low Retro 'Pink' - Anniversary Edition is a great choice for trainer lovers looking for an eye-catching, comfortable and durable trainer with a unique design.

name: Nike Shox TL 'Silver'
text_content: Nike's revival of the Shox TL sneakers combines space-age aesthetics with a strong sporting heritage. These sneakers feature silver and white, with a gentle hue of blue on the 'Silver' colourway, creating a futuristic and visually striking design. Crafted with durable nylon uppers, the shoes also incorporate glossy taped overlays that form a web-like pattern on the upper, adding to their unique look.One of the most distinctive features of the Shox TLs is the pillared midsoles, offering a fusion of '90s nostalgia and forward-looking innovation. Additionally, you'll find subtle embroidered branding to signify Nike's identity, and to ensure durability and traction, the sneakers are equipped with a rubber outsole.

name: Nike Air Max 97 WMNS 'Silver Bullet'
text_content: Nike has given the Air Max 97 'Silver Bullet' (DQ9131-002) a silver mesh sole. Additionally, silver and white leather outline the muguards. Above is a wavy overlay made of reflective 3M material, and a red mini Swoosh is placed on the tongue and the middle panel. Underneath the white midsole is an Air unit that runs throughout the sole. A black outsole with white and red details completes the sporty design.The sneaker also comes in men's and GS sizing.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Shadow WMNS 'Blue Whisper'
text_content: There is no doubt that the Nike Air Force 1 Shadow is one of the most popular shoes among women, offering a fashion-forward update to Bruce Kilgore's iconic design from 1983. Over the years, it has gained popularity and is known for its experimental designs. The latest iteration features a white and ‘Blue Whisper’ color scheme, perfect for the warm weather of summer. Swooshes and other branded components alternate between two shades of blue on the upper, adding a touch of contrast. There is a blue flair around the heel and the sole units match the color scheme. The pair is summer-ready with an oft-imitated off-white outsole.

name: Nike ACG Moc 'Moss'
text_content: A functional and adaptable shoe that combines modern style and outdoor performance is the Nike ACG Air Moc 'Moss'. This shoe has a clean green and grey colorway in a lightweight, breathable upper made of a mix of textile and synthetic materials. The slip-on style makes it simple to put on and take off, making it ideal for everyday wear or outdoor activities. The durability and adaptability to different terrains are indicated by the ACG (All Conditions Gear) branding. The rubber outsole offers dependable traction on various surfaces, and the Phylon midsole offers lightweight cushioning. The Nike ACG Air Moc 'Moss'  provides comfort, style, and functionality in a stylish package, whether you're exploring the trails or simply strolling around the city. The silhouette also comes available in the 'Sail Black' colorway.

name: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 'Black'
text_content: This Nike Zoom Vomero 5 comes in a ‘Black’ colorway that offers a sleek and understated look. With an open mesh base and leather overlays, the Zoom Vomero 5 showcases the signature plastic material on the panel and heel counter. These sneakers feature Zoom Air insoles for enhanced cushioning. A stealthy aesthetic is completed by reflective accents with 3M technology, as well as black on the entire shoe.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Blue' - Since 82
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Since 82' - Toothbrush (DJ3911-101) is part of the 40th anniversary year of the Nike Air Force 1. This Nike Air Force 1 Low features a white leather base and a white midsole for a fresh look. The Swooshes, Nike branding on the tongue, heel and midsole feature a nice 'Game Royal' blue hue.  The sneaker sits on a Gum outsole which gives the shoe a cool vintage look. Each pair also comes with a special toothbrush.

name: Nike Air More Uptempo WMNS 'Rosewood'
text_content: The Nike Air More Uptempo WMNS 'Rosewood' brings the enticing design of Air More Uptempo to new interpretations. The sneaker features a smooth leather base, creating a neutral background for the grey overlays. The leather overlays depicting 'AIR' continue in the same grey hue onto the black outsole, sectioning it. The visible Air Bubbles are also incorporated into the design while being the only disruptor of the elongated overlays. Branding elements throughout the shoe come in 'Rosewood' hue, offering the tonal silhouette a sparkle of colour. Nike's iconic Swoosh on the heel of the sneaker comes in an Air Bubble form with a translucent top and 'Rosewood' background. The design is completed by white laces and inner lining.

name: Nike Mac Attack 'Red Crush'
text_content: The Nike Mac Attack, a tennis shoe originally released in 1984, is receiving its first-ever retro release this year. Crafted for tennis legend John McEnroe, the Nike Mac Attack is generating excitement as collaborations with Social Status have been revealed and Travis Scott was seen wearing a remixed version featuring Cactus Jack branding and a reversed Swoosh. Now, a brand new colour scheme called "Red Crush" is bringing the silhouette back into the spotlight. The upper combines breathable mesh and smooth leather, with the mesh providing structure to the side panels and the leather used for overlays. A pure white colour dominates most of the shoe, allowing the "Red Crush" accents to stand out on the Swooshes, collars, checkered tongue branding, heels, and outsoles. Nike branding is present on the tongues and heels, while the shoe's size and style code are printed on the interior medials.

name: Nike Air Max Plus 'Diamond'
text_content: Drawing inspiration from the serene beauty of rolling palm tree waves, the Nike Air Max Plus emerges as the ultimate representation of the Tuned Air line. Dressed in a White/Blue colourway, the Nike Air Max Plus ‘Diamond’ (FV0394-300) features a lightweight mesh base with a captivating tie-dye blue pattern, and the upper is skillfully secured by a TPU cage that pays homage to the elegant palm trees. Enhancing its distinctive style, jewel logos grace the tongue and sides, while a vibrant volt-yellow Tn Air emblem adorns the heel. Complementing this oceanic design, accents of aqua leather frame the upper, creating a harmonious flow. The tongue is adorned with striking strips of 3M material that adds a dash of brilliance to the look. Underneath, the shoe boasts a white phylon midsole, equipped with Air units strategically placed for exceptional cushioning and comfort, allowing you to stride with both style and ease.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'Spray Paint Swoosh'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 'Spray Paint Swoosh' has an all-black upper made of a mix of mesh and tumbled leather. An eye-catching detail are the Swooshes in the colours orange and yellow; it gives the impression that these have been applied with a spray can. There are also yellow details in the form of branding elements on the tongue and heel. The shoe is rounded off with a white midsole, which features the signature Air unit, this time in grey sheathing.

name: Nike Air Max 95 'Triple Black'
text_content: Nike is giving the Air Max 95 a nice and sleek makeover with the release of the ‘Triple Black’ edition of the sneaker. The classic silhouette sees the shoe dressed in black, metallic silver and anthracite colors. The sneaker is constructed with a mixture of materials, featuring mesh and leather among the upper. The laces are made in black to match the sleek look. The all-black design is joined by subtle branding details like a mini jewel Swoosh.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'Multi Swoosh Grey'
text_content: Nike's lifestyle brand has released a multitude of general sneaker releases recently, with nearly every silhouette in their lineup featuring the iconic swooshes. Air Max 90, a popular model, has now joined this trend with a Halloween-themed version. In addition to jet-black accents on the quarters and heel tab, the shoe's upper is predominantly covered in a dark shadow grey colour. With an array of Swooshes on the mid-foot area, the sole unit matches the dark aesthetic perfectly. Orange highlights the main swoosh, adding vibrant colour to the design. The two-tone sneaker combines Halloween elements with Nike's signature style, which is also available on the Air Max GS.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Shadow WMNS 'Pink Oxford'
Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX Low 'Command Force'
Nike Air Max 95 'Safari Viotech'
text_content: Nike has a number of recognizable models and the Air Max 95 is definitely one of them. The special surface design makes it a versatile sneaker.The 'Safari' colorway is very similar to the Atmos x Nike Air Max 1 B 'Viotech'. The brown colours on the upper go from light to dark, for example the upper panel is very light beige while the panel near the sole is very dark. The classic Viotech colour can be found on the tongue, heel and Swoosh branding on the heel of the shoe.

name: Nike Dunk Low WMNS 'Oxygen Purple'
text_content: This new Dunk Low WMNS is making waves this spring. On the panel swoosh, tongue tag, and insoles, hits of "Oxygen Purple" light and stunning purple tones complement the neutral leather uppers and overlays. In addition to a cream-colored outsole and midsole, matching white laces provide a polished touch that lifts the shoe's overall appearance. This Dunk Low WMNS 'Oxygen Purple' is sure to be a hit this season. Its subtle and sophisticated style combines the right amount of color and neutrality to make a chic and stylish statement.

name: Nike Zoom Vomero 5 'Velvet Brown'
text_content: From the Nike Zoom Vomero design comes the Nike Zoom Vomero 5 'Velvet Brown' in a predominately dark colorway with red details. The mesh upper dressed in 'Velvet Brown' features various brown and black leather overlays. The medial of the shoe has a 'University Red' background on which the classic zoom overlays for enhanced stability come in brown. Atop the medial, the Swoosh featured in brown has a thin red outline. The branded tongue tag of the sneaker uses red and white to depict Nike's logo while matching the red sparkled laces. The midsole of the trainer comes in 'Velvet Brown' while the white chunky outsole completes the design.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Red' - Since 82
text_content: The Air Force 1 Low 'Red' - Since 82 (DJ3911-102) falls under Nike's 'Colour of the Month' series. This shoe series pays tribute to the Baltimore sneaker shops that kept the AF1 popular.The upper is made almost entirely of high-quality leather that is white in colour. The Swoosh is covered in 'University Red' leather. The branding on the midsole, tongue label, heel tab are also in this colour. The classic design is finished off with a white midsole with a gum outsole underneath.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX WMNS 'Coconut Milk'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX WMNS 'Coconut Milk' (DO9456-100) is a sneaker exclusively for women. The Air Force 1 silhouette has become a true classic since its release in 1982 and has many variations. The '07 LX version has a 'Jewel' Swoosh on the middle panel that gives the shoe a chic and unique look. The sneaker is beige and has a leather upper. The pre-yellowed midsole matches the upper well and gives the shoe a retro look. The 'Jewel' Swoosh is beige and has a glossy finish. The tongue features the Nike logo.

name: Nike Air Force 1 GS 'Brown Yellow'
text_content: Nike Air Force 1 BG 'Brown Yellow' is a true autumn trainer due to its colour composition. Indeed, the AF1 comes with pastel shades of green and blue on the upper and side, which overflows into a brown heel. The Swoosh is yellow, as is the sole. The entire shoe is leather this makes the AF1 autumn-proof.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 WMNS 'Tie-dye Jewel Swoosh'
text_content: In 2023, Nike is paying homage to its iconic "Just Do It" slogan with a vibrant and innovative twist. This tribute encompasses several of their archival models, and the creative concept comes from the design of Bruce Kilgore.The focal point of this tribute is the classic Air Force 1, typically recognized for its ‘Triple-White’ colour scheme. The transformation extends from the flat leather panels to the fuzzy collar lining and ballistic mesh tongue construction, giving it a fresh and lively appearance.Notably, the tie-dye treatment is not limited to the surface. It also decorates the Jewel mid-foot Swooshes and the heel tab logo, both of which appear upside-down for a unique and eye-catching effect.

name: Nike Wmns Internationalist PRM (Pale Ivory / Pale Ivory - Summit White
Nike Air Force 1 07 SE 'Sanddrift'
text_content: The Air Force 1 '07 SE' has everything to get you through the Winter. A stylish and neutral colour palette of Phantom, Sanddrift, Black and White, Nike transforms the silhouette with contrasting fabrics. A suede upper, teddy fleece lining and the iconic swoosh made of down. Both the heel and tongue also feature Nike branding in a unique style. All and all, definitely a sneaker that belongs in your rotation during colder weather.

name: Nike Air Max Plus 'Rainbow'
text_content: The Nike Air Max Plus 'Rainbow' is a colourful version of the popular Nike Air Max Plus model. The sneaker's upper is made of breathable mesh and has overlapping TPU details. The 'Rainbow' version has an upper that consists of colourful rainbow transitions.The shoe is designed with Nike's famous Air-Sole unit, which provides cushioning and comfort during wear. This makes the Nike Air Max Plus 'Rainbow' an ideal choice for those looking for both style and comfort. The sneaker's outsole is made of durable rubber and offers good grip on different surfaces.The Nike Air Max Plus 'Rainbow' has an iconic look with an advanced design that is still popular among sneaker lovers. The rainbow transition gives the shoe a striking and cheerful look that matches different styles and outfits. Whether you go for a casual or sporty look, the Nike Air Max Plus 'Rainbow' is a versatile sneaker that offers comfort and style.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 'White Icy Blue'
text_content: In honour of its 40-year legacy, the Nike Air Force 1 Low emerges in a sleek all-white design with icy blue accents for the winter season. This iconic silhouette combines traditional leather panels with tactical nylon mid-foot components, ensuring both style and breathability. Reflective rope laces add a touch of visibility and flair. The sneakers feature clean midsoles with a colourless look, while the standout element is the semi-translucent icy blue outsoles that complete the cool and distinctive outfit up top.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Premium WMNS 'Velvet Brown'
Nike Dunk High 1985 'Yellow' - Acid Wash
text_content: The Nike Dunk High came out in 1985 as a basketball shoe. The Dunks are no longer used for basketball, but the skateboard scene has kept the Dunk alive. With the Acid Pack, Nike pays homage to the old silhouette of the Dunk High. The sneaker is built from a light yellow outsole. The midsole has a yellowed look, which is darker than the outsole. It tends to be more orange. The base of the upper is made of black leather and the overlay panels have a black and yellow Acid Wash. The upper is yellow and contrasts well with the black.

name: Nike Air Max 90 LTR GS 'White Action Grape'
Nike Air Max Pulse 'Cobblestone'
text_content: The Nike Air Max Pulse 'Cobblestone' is a trainer with a modern design and the iconic Air Max cushioning. The trainer has an upper of mesh with leather and synthetic overlays, making it breathable and durable. The 'Cobblestone' colour scheme has a neutral and versatile look, consisting of 'Cobblestone', 'Light Orewood Brown', 'Black' and 'Reflect Silver'.A unique feature of the Air Max Pulse is the visible Air Max unit in the heel, which provides responsive cushioning and comfort with every step. In addition, the trainer has a rubber outsole for good grip on different surfaces.All in all, the Nike Air Max Pulse 'Cobblestone'is a cool and comfortable trainer that can be worn both casually and during sports.This trainer is also available in a women's size and a 'Black' version.

name: Nike SB Pogo White Black Skate
Nike Air Force 1 Wild WMNS 'Mahogany'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Wild WMNS 'Mahogany' (FB2348-800) is a striking addition to the Air Force 1 lineup. With a 'Mahogany/Black' colourway, this sneaker offers a distinctive and bold appearance. The upper combines premium materials in a mix of textures and patterns for a unique design. It features a rich blend of ‘Mahogany’ mesh base and suede overlays which adds some depth to the monochromatic design.  Additionally, the added padding at the heel and the reinforced outsole enhances the functionality and comfort you will feel when wearing this pair. This Air Force 1 in rugged orange also incorporates midsole cushioning making the sneakers suitable for everyday wear, whether you will use them on the trail or you want to incorporate them in your gorpcore street style wardrobe.

name: Nike Air Max 90 Terrascape Black Lime Ice
text_content: This is a new colorway of the Air Max 90 called Nike Air Max 90 'Terrascape Black Lime Ice' first came out in early 2022. This sneaker is made with 20% recycled material, so besides the fact that they are super comfortable they are also environmentally conscious. The base of this sneaker is black with some mesh on the toe. The midsole is made of Crater foam with a transparent layer around it.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low 'White Snakeskin' - Color of the Month
text_content: In an attempt to breathe new life into the Air Force 1 silhouette, Nike came up with the idea of the 'Colour of the Month'. This was a huge success and years later, the Air Force 1 has become a true icon for the sneaker community. So it is no surprise that the concept has been brought back in 2023 on the 40th anniversary of the silhouette. The 'White Snakeskin' features an all-white colour palette with different textures. Snakeskin leather overlays extend from the swoosh to the heel. Nike Air branding can be found on the tongue and heel, and the signature metal AF1 branding can be found at the bottom of the laces.

name: Nike Blazer Mid '77 SE GS 'Split White Spruce'
Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX Low 'Brown' - Plaid Pack
Nike ACG Mountain Fly 2 Low 'Neutral Olive'
text_content: The debut of the Nike Acg Mountain Fly 2 series brings to the public four enticing colorways in an outdoorsy style. The second generation of Nike ACG Mountain Fly features a series of enhancements fit to increase your performance and comfort while unfolding your favourite outdoor activities. The Nike ACG Mountain Fly 2 Low 'Neutral Olive' features a two-toned design complemented by smooth white and purple details. The breathable 'Neutral Olive' mesh upper ensures the ventilation of the foot and fast drying while the black cushioning around the tongue and inner lining increase comfort. The branding on the lateral of the shoe features 'acg' writing in black, matching in colour the branded tongue and heel tags. The toggle lacing system designed for quick adjustment comes in 'Mountain Grape' purple hue for a pop of colour. The Swoosh featured on the lateral of the shoe comes dressed in white, matching sections of the reinforcing rubber sidewall. For increased durability, the shoe is equipped with a grey extended toe cap. The lightweight foam midsole increases the comfort of the model while the mountain-biking-inspired outsole ensures traction on any surface. Enjoy nature in style with the Mountain Fly 2 collection in 'Summit White' and 'Laser Orange'.

name: Nike Air Max 1 Slide 'Sport Red'
text_content: The Air Max 1 Slide 'Sport Red' is the transformation of the popular Air Max 1 design into its slide version, perfect for hot summer days. The red silhouette features a thick strap composed of a white mesh base with grey and red suede overlays. Because there is no tongue, the 'Air Max' tag sits in the middle of the strap, centred away from the red lateral Swoosh bellies. The red insole and white midsole are separated by the classic air bubble of the AM-1. An alternation of red and white patches constructs the outsole while giving unity to the design. This slide also comes in a black colorway.

name: LeBron James X Nike Air Force 1 'Strive For Greatness'
text_content: LeBron James and Nike have teamed up once again to produce the Air Force 1 'Strive For Greatness'. This pair comes in a beige colour scheme. Black is also used on the Swooshes on the mid panel, heel tab and tongue.  The back panel of the Air Force 1 features a checkered print that matches the colour scheme used. In addition, the model has a white midsole that is supported by the outsole in the same colour. On the sneaker, a few striking details can be found. There is a blue lion illustrated on the heel tab. The lion wears a crown and is surrounded by trees and water, which refers to LeBron's nickname, 'King James'.

name: Nike Dunk Low Twist WMNS 'Panda'
text_content: The well-liked 'Panda' colorway of the Nike sneakers is now available for the Dunk Low Twist for ladies. The 'Panda' mentality that sneakerheads like is embodied by its white base with black overlays. The shoe has a strong backtab, a detachable Swoosh evocative of Ambush's previous Nike partnerships, and bumpers at the toe and heel. A white midsole sits above a black rubber outsole to complete the look, giving the whole thing a sleek, contrasting element. Fans of the classic Dunk style will love the Nike Dunk Low Twist in Panda for its striking colors and distinctive design.

name: Nike Air More Uptempo Red Toe
Nike Air Max 1 Slide 'Obsidian'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 1 Slide 'Obsidian' is a slipper inspired by the iconic Nike Air Max 1 trainer. The slipper has a sleek design and is available in different colour combinations.The 'Obsidian' colourway features a dark blue colour, with white accents on different areas of the sandal. The sandal's upper is made of white mesh with overlays of grey and obsidian suede, and the sandal is finished with the iconic Air bubble.The Nike Air Max 1 Slide 'Obsidian' is a striking, stylish flip-flop that perfectly matches casual outfits. Its iconic design and high-quality materials make it a durable and comfortable choice for everyday wear.

name: Nike Air Max Scorpion Flyknit WMNS 'White Football Grey'
Nike Air Force 1 Shadow WMNS 'Pink Glaze'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Shadow 'Pink Glaze' gives a playful twist to a classic basketball design. The sneaker is mostly off-white with a variety of pastel-coloured overlays on the back. The layered approach gives the Nike Air Force 1 twice the branding details and a larger midsole that accentuates the iconic Air Force 1 design with a striking new look.

name: Nike Air Force 1 LV8 PS 'Light Silver Deep Royal'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 LV8 PS 'Light Silver Deep Royal' (FB9501-001) in the ‘Light Silver/Deep Royal/White’ colourway is a stylish and eye-catching iteration of the classic Air Force 1. The leather upper predominantly features light silver and white tones, creating a clean and modern aesthetic. The deep royal blue accents on the iconic Swoosh and heel branding add a pop of colour, making the design stand out. Equipped with Nike Air cushioning in the midsole, these sneakers provide not only a fashionable look but also the comfort and support that Air Force 1 enthusiasts appreciate. This combination of style and functionality makes the Air Force 1 LV8 PS 'Light Silver Deep Royal' a versatile choice for various occasions.

name: Nike Air Max 90 'Pressure'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 'Pressure' is a great tribute to Frank Rudy. In 1997, Rudy designed the pioneering concept of Nike Air Technology. Through his previous work at NASA, he was inspired and thus the story of Nike Air Technology began.  The base of the sneaker consists of mesh. The overlays come in a nubuck and suede material and are light brown in colour. The Swoosh is coloured orange while the eyestays in turn colour yellow. The transparent Air Unit features the year 1990, which is a reference to the year the Nike Air Max 90 came out.  The insoles of the Nike Air Max 90 'Pressure' contain a motif of a blue print which is believed to be a copy of the blueprints used by Frank Rudy himself.  This is not the first sneaker that is an ode to the well known Frank Rudy, for instance, the Nike Air Max 97 'M. Frank Rudy' was released.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8 'Medium Ash'
text_content: Nike continues to expand its Air Force 1 Low collection with the introduction of the ‘Medium Ash’ colourway, designed to transition from summer to winter seamlessly. The high-quality leather construction of the sneakers ensures their durability and readiness for more severe weather. Ripstop mid panels that are seam-taped for added water resistance and insulation improve their winter suitability. The unique colour palette combines medium ash tones on the upper with bronzine accents on the tongues and the rubber soles. Throughout the shoe, Nike branding is prominently featured on tongue labels, insoles, and heels. The AF1 is finished with a speckled midsole and a bronzine rubber outsole, providing both style and functionality for the upcoming season.

name: Nike Air Max 95 'Triple White'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 95 'Triple White' is a rendition of the classic Air Max 95 model, known for its iconic layered design and visible Air cushioning in the sole. As the name suggests, the sneaker is coloured all-white, with a white leather and leather upper and a white sole.The 'Triple White' colorway is a great choice for sneaker lovers looking for a fresh and minimalist look that can be easily combined with different outfits. Whether you go for a casual look or something more formal, the Nike Air Max 95 'Triple White' offers a versatile and timeless option.

name: Nike Cortez '23 WMNS 'Orewood Brown'
text_content: The Nike Cortez '23 WMNS 'Orewood Brown' is a women's shoe that combines the classic style of the original Nike Cortez with modern updates. The shoe has an upper of premium leather and suede in a beautiful Orewood Brown colour.The Nike Cortez '23 WMNS 'Orewood Brown' has rubber outsole with herringbone pattern for grip and orange detail on the midsole. The signature design with the Swoosh on the sides and Nike branding on the tongue and heel round off the sneaker's look.

name: Nike Dunk Low 'Washed Denim'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low 'Washed Denim' consists mainly of white leather. The tongue of the shoe is made of vintage nylon, unlike the inner lining, for this it uses mesh for comfort. The Nike Dunk Low catches the eye because of the texture of the Swoosh and heel collar, namely 'Washed Denim'. This matches the sail laces and midsole. Rounding out the Nike Dunk Low 'Washed Denim' is the gum rubber outsole.

name: Nike Dunk Low PS 'Hyper Pink'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low GS 'Hyper Pink' (DH9765-600) has a cute colorway. The upper is light pink and made of leather. The midsole has been given the same colour as the upper, which gives the sneaker a striking look. The overlays have been given a slightly darker pink hue, but match the upper well.The shoe has a bright pink Swoosh on the middle panel. This contrasts nicely with the pink upper and does justice to the name of the colorway. On the heel and nose the Nike logos are stitched. These also come in the striking pink colour. In short; the ideal sneaker for those who love pink and are not afraid to make a statement.

name: Nike Air Max 90 GS 'Phantom'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 is an unprecedented classic. The sneaker is loved by almost every sneaker lover and not without reason.That the 'Phantom' colorway is also available in children's sizes is a nice bonus. The quiet, grey base is enhanced by playful colours like yellow, blue and pink. Next to these colours, different materials like leather and canvas complete the look.

name: Nike Zoom Mercurial Superfly 9 Academy MG 'Luminous Pack'
Nike Air Force 1 '07 'Quilted Swooshes'
text_content: As summers worldwide face rainy days, Nike has responded by enhancing this presidential model with water-resistant uppers to keep wearers dry. In this iteration, the shoe adopts a clean Sail and Black colour scheme, with a pristine upper that prominently features ‘Quilted Swooshes’ on the sides.The traditional sole unit maintains its timeless off-white appearance, aligning with the classic Air Force 1 style, making it a versatile choice for various weather conditions and fashion preferences.

name: Nike Air Max 1 GS 'Tropical Twist'
text_content: With its vibrant and stylish design, the Nike Air Max 1 GS 'Tropical Twist' adds an element of freshness to the iconic Air Max 1 silhouette. This grade school-exclusive release combines crisp white mesh panels with light grey leather overlays and jet-black nubuck mudguards for a dynamic colour scheme. Teal accents are found on the Swoosh, tongue tabs, and collar lining, adding a tropical touch. Inspired by the Air Max 90 Essential, subtle purple highlights elevate the design and add a unique touch. With Air Max cushioning, the 'Tropical Twist' colorway offers both comfort and style.

name: Nike LeBron 21 'Akoya'
text_content: The Nike LeBron 21 'Akoya' is designed to protect the modern basketball player. The shoe is inspired by oyster shells, so the upper is cloaked in "Light Bone" with vents that resemble the veining of a shell. The Swoosh is underlined by the colour "Campfire Orange", which also returns on the tongue and heel. The Nike LeBron 21 is equipped with a Cushlon 2.0 foam sole that is supported by a semi-transparent outsole in milky white.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low 'West Indies'
text_content: Twenty years after its original release, the Nike Air Force 1 Low 'West Indies' (DX1156-100) is being re-released. The sneaker was originally released in celebration of the West Indian Day Parade Carnival, an annual celebration in Brooklyn, New York. This AF1 has a white leather base with green details at the lining, outsole and heel tab. The heel features 'West Indies' stitched on with a palm tree graphic. The pair also features various yellow accents on the tongue and heel tab.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Mid QS 'Independence Day'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Mid QS 'Independence Day' celebrates the 40th anniversary of the AF-1 with a retro edition from 1997. From the metallic Midnight Blue leather overlays, the Jewel Swoosh, the University Red details on this Air Force 1 Mid, to the transparent outsole. Everything about this sneaker reaches back to the great days of yore!

name: Nike Air Max 90 Social F.C. 'Light Bone'
Nike LeBron 21 GS 'Tahitian'
text_content: The Nike LeBron 21 'Tahitian' colourway draws inspiration from the captivating glow of Tahitian pearls. LeBron's 21st signature sneaker with Nike features iridescent detailing on the heel counter and midsole, reminiscent of the rare pearl's luminosity. Dressed in a Black, Particle Grey, Wolf Grey, and Pink Rose colour scheme, the sneaker boasts a suede finish on the base and tongue tabs. Mesh detailing in matching colours adorns the lower portion of the tongues, while Black lining and laces contribute to a cohesive aesthetic. A Black midsole and semi-translucent green outsole complete the main features, creating a visually striking and thematically cohesive design.

name: Nike Dunk Low Premium 'Sequoia'
text_content: As part of Nike's classic Dunk Low silhouette releases, the Dunk Low Premium 'Sequoia' arrives. It has a canvas base and tongues with tumbled leather overlays. Inside, the shoe is lined with terry cloth for added comfort. The tongue labels, insoles, and heel embroidery feature white branding accents alongside the sequoia-colored upper. Finished with a light rubber outsole and midsole, the design is complete.

name: Nike Dunk Low PRM WMNS 'Team Red'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low PRM WMNS 'Team Red'  is a premium sneaker model designed for women by Nike. This shoe is based on the classic basketball silhouette of the original Nike Dunk. With red and white being the dominant colours of this colorway, the low-top silhouette features a padded collar for comfort and flexibility.A combination of premium leather is used to construct the upper of the shoe. White leather covers the toe box, the midsole, the base, as well as the laces, while a powerful red covers the overlays, the heel counter, the outsole, and the classic swoosh, giving the shoe a stylish and upscale look.

name: Nike Dunk Low GS 'Cool Grey Blue'
Nike Air Max 90 WMNS 'Teal Nebula'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 'Fresh Water' colorway features white, black, and vibrant aqua accents. Durable and breathable materials compose the upper. In terms of the upper, the toebox is mainly white while the overlay and the swoosh are gray. In this new colorway, the mudguard, eyelets, branding details, and visible Air Max unit all feature a 'Fresh Water' hue.

name: Serena Williams Design Crew x Nike Air More Uptempo 'Dark Obsidian'
Nike Air Force 1 Low Retro 'West Indies Yellow'
text_content: The Nike Air Force 1 Low Retro 'West Indies Yellow' sneaker is a vibrant and daring homage to the West Indian region's rich cultural history. This classic shape comes in a vibrant yellow colorway that radiates style and energy. This sneaker offers both style and ventilation thanks to its perforated toe box and smooth leather upper.The 'West Indies Yellow' which embodies the spirit of the area and exudes joy and warmth, pays homage to the beaches and tropical settings that are bathed in sunlight. The Air Force 1 Low Retro is made with Nike's renowned craftsmanship, which guarantees exceptional comfort and durability. This sneaker is a must-have for those looking for a bold and expressive style that makes a statement with every step thanks to its recognizable Air-Sole unit and durable traction.With this vibrant and iconic sneaker, which captures the essence of the area's heritage while ensuring exceptional comfort and performance, you can step out with confidence and flaunt your individual style.

name: Nike Air Max 90 Futura WMNS 'Triple White'
Nike Tiempo Legend 9 Elite FG 'Black Metallic Gold'
Stüssy x Nike Air Max Penny 2 'Rattan'
Nike Air Max 90 LTR PS 'Light Thistle'
Nike Sportswear NIKE ZOOM AIR FIRE
Nike Dunk Low 'Mystic Red Cargo Khaki'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low 'Mystic Red Cargo Khaki' is a stylish and versatile sneaker in a contrasting colorway. On the 'Mystic Red' leather base, the 'Cargo Khaki' overlays create a bold look. A white midsole disrupts the two-toned design of the upper, while a rubber outsole provides stability and traction. The iconic Nike logo is embossed on the heel tab and tongue tag in khaki.The Nike Dunk Low 'Mystic Red Cargo Khaki' is sure to turn heads whether you're hitting the streets or making a fashion statement.

name: Nike Air Max 90 GORE-TEX 'Black'
text_content: The Nike Air Max 90 GORE-TEX 'Black' is completely enveloped in a black silhouette. In collaboration with GORE-TEX, almost the entire shoe is covered in leather to make it waterproof. The GORE-TEX logo can be found on both the tongue and the side panel. Eye-catching details include the orange TPU grille and the rubber mudguard on the heel, which features Nike-Air logo. Rounding off the Air Max 90 is the well-known sole, which features cushioning.

name: Nike Dunk Low PS 'Two-Toned Grey'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low PS 'Two-Toned Grey' is a stylish trainer with a signature design that combines classic and contemporary elements. Designed for the younger generation, this trainer is specially made for children.The 'Two-Toned Grey' colourway of the Nike Dunk Low PS features a striking two-part grey colour scheme. The upper is made of high-quality leather and features different shades of grey that blend in nicely. These subtle colours give the trainer a sophisticated and versatile look.The Nike Dunk Low PS 'Two-Toned Grey' is not only a trendy trainer but also a durable choice for kids. Its timeless design and high-quality materials make this trainer suitable for both everyday use and sporting activities. With its modern look and comfortable fit, the Nike Dunk Low PS 'Two-Toned Grey' is a great choice for young trainer lovers who want to combine style and functionality.

name: Nike Tiempo Legend 9 Elite MI FG Montebelluna Leather White Game Royal
Nike Cortez WMNS 'Black and White'
text_content: The iconic and adaptable Nike Cortez WMNS 'Black and White' sneaker features a classic black and white colour scheme. The low-top silhouette is made with premium synthetic material accessorised with sections of suede and smooth leather. A bold and modern aesthetic that effortlessly goes with a variety of outfits is created by the black upper that contrasts with white accents on the Swoosh logo, laces, and midsole. This sneaker's cushioned insole and safe lace-up closure make it comfortable to wear all day. The Nike Cortez logos on the tongue and heel add a vintage touch, and the robust rubber outsole offers durable traction.Stylish and classic, the Nike Cortez WMNS 'Black and White' a versatile option for a variety of settings.

name: Nike Air Max 95 X 'Make Your Mark'
Nike SB Dunk Low 'Mystic Red'
text_content: The Nike SB Dunk Low 'Mystic Red' is one of the more notable models in the SB Dunk Low inline lineup. The shoe, which has a full suede upper and a mostly monochromatic design, is inspired by the classic animated film Akira. The paneling, laces, and lining of the shoe are all dyed in 'Mystic Red', which unifies and draws attention to the design. The branding and Swoosh are light blue in contrast to the monochromatic design, and the midsole is a deep burgundy color.

name: Nike Dunk Low PS 'Deep Jungle'
text_content: The Nike Dunk Low PS 'Deep Jungle' has an autumnal look due to the green hue in the colour combination. The shoe is composed of a very light shade of green, with overlays in the dark green colour 'Deep Jungle'. The Swoosh in the colour 'Light Silver' adds a fresh twist to the Nike Dunk Low. Notable are the laces, half of which are a light shade of green and half of which are coloured white. The shoe is finished with a white midsole supported by an outsole in grey, light green and 'Deep Jungle' colours.

name: UNDERCOVER x Nike Air Force 1 Low 'Grey Fog'
Nike Air Force 1 '50 Years of Hip-Hop'
text_content: With a design that combines iconic elements and vibrant colours, the Nike Air Force 1 '50 Years of Hip-Hop' pays homage to the influential genre. This sneaker's upper is made of a variety of high-quality materials, providing strength and a plush feel.With a clean look, the sneaker features a white leather base. The calm vibe of the upper is disrupted by the 'Smoke Grey' glitter Swoosh hue that continues onto the branded heel tab. The tongue tag features a special design referring to the anniversary of the musical genre. 'Beach' midsole diversifies the colour pallet while the whole silhouette sits atop a grey outsole. This sneaker offers both style and comfort, whether you're hitting the streets or making a statement. With this enduring sneaker that captures the spirit of hip-hop, take part in the celebration of 50 years of influential music and culture.

name: Nike Air Force 1 '07 'Triple Swoosh White'
text_content: The Air Force 1 '07 'Triple Swoosh White' is a variation of the iconic sneaker, known for its clean and timeless design. In 2007, the original Air Force 1 was remastered and released, thus the '07 designation.'Triple Swoosh White' features a predominantly white color scheme. Each side panel of the shoe features three Nike Swoosh logos, creating a distinctive and eye-catching design. A red, metallic silver and gray Swoosh logo stands out against the all-white shoe. Cushioning and traction are provided by a chunky rubber outsole, and the collar is padded for comfort and ankle support. It is often equipped with Nike Air cushioning in its midsole to provide responsiveness and impact absorption.

name: Nike Air Max 90 Leather 'White Game Royal'
Billie Eilish x Nike Air Force 1 High 'Sequoia'
text_content: Superstar Billie Eilish and Nike are back with a new shoe. This sneaker is the sequel to the Billie Eilish x Nike Air Force 1 High '07 SP that came out in April 2022.The Billie Eilish x Nike Air Force 1 High 'Sequoia' (DM7926-300) has the same special details as its predecessor. For instance, the sneaker comes in a colour scheme of only one colour and that is in this case 'Sequoia'. What cannot be missed are the 5 Velcro straps that run over the laces.

name: Nike Air More Uptempo
text_content: This colorway of the Nike Air More Uptempo (DM8155-100) is only available in kids sizes and came out as part of the 'Peace, Love, Swoosh' three-pack, along with another Air Force 1 and an Air Huarache. The sneaker has a clean white leather upper with perforation holes.
